\id JHN
\h SAN JUAN
\toc1 A JE'RA' U JACH TSOYIR U T'ɅN C'UJ TU TS'IBTA JUAN
\toc2 SAN JUAN
\toc3 Jn.
\mt1 A JE'RA' U JACH TSOYIR U T'ɅN C'UJ TU TS'IBTA JUAN
\c 1
\s1 A jera' cu tsicbar ti' to'onex a mac a cu tar ich C'uj soc u tsicbʌtic to'onex bicyʌra' C'uj
\p 
\v 1 Mʌ' toy betac ru'um mʌ' toy betac ca'anan xan. Rajra' ti' yʌn a mac a cu bin tar u tsicbar to'onex bicyʌra' C'uj. Raji' ti' yʌn yejer ic Tet C'uj quire' raji' C'uj a cu bin tar.
\v 2 Rajra' ti' yʌn a mac a cu bin tar ich ic Tet C'uj cax mʌ' toy betac ru'um yejer ca'anan xan.
\v 3 Tu cotor a ba' ti' yʌn, raji' u beyaj C'uj. Mʌna' mac u jer tu betaj. Raji' tu junan caj u betaj.
\v 4 Raji' tu junan cu ts'ic ij cuxtarex. Raji' tu ts'aj ic najtiquex ij cuxtarex munt q'uin. Quire' a ba' caj u betaj rajen raji' u sasirir to'onex a mac a cu manob ich yoc'ocab a mac a cu manob ich yac'birir quire' yʌn u si'pirob.
\v 5 Raji' quib a cu ye'c'ac'tic tu yʌn ac'bir. A ac'biro' mʌ' c'ucha'an yor u tupic u sasirir. Baxuc arayo' yejer Jesús xan, cax mʌ' u c'atob Jesús mac. Raji' tan u ts'ic to'onex ij cuxtarex munt q'uin.
\s1 A jera' cu tsicbar bic tabar u parar C'uj tu ch'aj u winquirir
\p 
\v 6 A ucho' ti' yʌn mac u c'aba' Juan. Raji' ts'a'b u beyaj ten C'uj.
\v 7 A Juano' caj u tsec'taj u sasirir a cu tar ich C'uj a cu sasiquintic mac. Mʌ' ja wirej, wa quij cacsiquex ij corex u sasirir ic pixamex, mʌ' ac'bir ic pixamexi'. Juan caj u tsec'taj soc u yacsic tu yor tu cotor mac a ba' cu yubic ya'aric Juan.
\v 8 A Juano' mʌ' ra' cu sasiquintic mac, u sasirir a cu tar ich C'uj, cu chen tsec'tic a cu sasiquintic mac. Quire' ara'b ti' ca' u tsec'tej.
\v 9 Wa ber a Juano' tan u tsec'tic ti' uch. Toc ts'oc u c'uchur tera' ich yoc'ocab, raji' a cu ts'ic ij cuxtarex soc u sasiquintic ic pixamex. Quire' ra' u beyaj.
\p 
\v 10 Raji' c'uchij ich yoc'ocab a caj u betaj yoc'ocab. Chen mʌ' c'ʌ'ota'b ten a mac ti' yʌn ich yoc'ocabo'.
\v 11 Caj c'uchij ich yoc'ocab soc u yet manob u winiquirob judío a mac teta'b ten C'uj uch. Chen mʌ' tu sʌjtajobi'.
\v 12 Chen yʌn mʌ' ya'ab mac a tu sʌjtajo', a tu yacsaj tu yor a ti'o'. Raji'ob yer ts'a'b u beyaj ten C'uj soc u to'car ti'ob. Ara'b ti'ob ten C'uj, raji'ob u parar C'uj a cu yacsicob tu yor ti'.
\v 13 Mʌ' ja wirej, a maque' u parar C'uj quire' caj u yacsaj tu yor. Raji' mʌ' baxuc a mac jach pararinta'b ten u tet quire' raji' quir a cuxtar techex yoc'ocab. Raji' mʌ' baxuc u pararinta'b ten u nʌ' quire' baxuc cu pachtic u pararʌncʌr a xquico'. Chen a mac a ju parar C'uj munt q'uin u cuxtar.
\p 
\v 14 Chen a mac a tar tsicbʌta to'onex bicyʌra' C'uj tu ch'aj u winquirir an ten bic to'onex. Tarij soc ij quet man a mac a ju winiquirob judío. Tij quiraj jach manan u muc'. Quire' raji' u parar C'uj, rajen baxuc jach manan u ne'er ba'. Ic Tet C'uj jari' turiri' u parar. Raji' quet cu yajquinto'onex. Raji' quet taj cu tsicbar.
\v 15 A Juano' caj u tsec'taj ti' a cu bin tar. Caj u ya'araj ti':
\p ―A jeroj, bin, a mac a tin wa'araj techex uch. A pachir cu tar, raji' jach no'j beyaj caj in wa'araj. Chen in beyaj a teno', mʌ' neno'jeni'. Cax mʌ' toy u rochen in nʌ', u toc beri' a ti'o' quire' rajra' ti' yʌn.
\p 
\v 16 Quire' jach tsoy yor a cu tar ich C'uj, rajen u jach tsoyirir C'uj caj ij c'ʌmaj. Rajra' tan u ts'ic to'on a ba' tsoy tu t'ʌn C'uj.
\v 17 Mʌ' ja wirej, u winiquirob judío caj u c'ʌmajob u nunquirob u t'ʌn C'uj a ts'ab ten Moisés uch. Chen a Jesucristojo' caj u yesaj bic C'uj caj u yajquintaj to'onex quire' otsir to'onex yirico'onex. Quire' a Jesucristojo' xan tij cu'yajex u t'ʌn C'uj a ba' taj.
\v 18 Mʌna' mac yirmʌn C'uj. Chen u parar C'uj tu yiraj u Tet. Jari' u parar turiri' raji' jach yajbir ten u Tet. Raji' caj u yesaj to'onex bicyira' C'uj.
\s1 Juan a cu yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac caj u tsec'taj ti' Jesucristo
\r (Mt. 3.11‑12; Mr. 1.7‑8; Lc. 3.15‑17)
\p 
\v 19 U winiquirob judío a ti' cʌja'anob ich u cajar Jerusalén. Raji'ob caj u tuchi'tajob sacerdote yejer a mac a cu beyajob ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob u winiquirob judío. Levitas u c'aba'ob. Tuchi'ta'b quir u c'ata' ti' Juan:
\p ―Maquechi'?
\p 
\v 20 A Juano' mʌ' ju mucraj caj u ya'araj:
\p ―Mʌ' Cristojeni', mʌ' yʌjtaquiren maqui', a cu bin tar.
\p 
\v 21 Caj u ca' c'atob ti' Juan:
\p ―Arej to'on maquechi'? A techo' wa Elíasech soc in wa'aricob ti' in rac'ob a tu tuchi'tenob?
\p Juan caj ya'araj:
\p ―Mʌ' Elíaseni'.
\p Caj u ca' c'atob ti':
\p ―Mʌ' wa tech yʌjtseq'uirech u t'ʌn C'uj a tan in pajicob u tar?
\p Juan caj u nuncaj, tan ya'aric ti'ob:
\p ―Mʌ' teni'.
\p 
\v 22 A tuchi'ta'b caj u ya'arob ti' Juan:
\p ―Arej tenob maquechi' soc in wa'aricob ti' a macob a tu tuchi'tenob ba' a beyaj tech, arej tenob.
\p 
\v 23 A Juano' caj u nuncaj caj u ya'araj:
\p ―Isaías caj u tsec'taj ti' ten uch. Baxuc a jera' caj u tsec'taj Isaías uch tan ya'aric: “Ti' cu bin tar mac ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin quir u c'am tsec'tic ich tʌcay ru'um.” C'am cu bin ya'aric: “Tajquintex a worex soc c'ucha'an a worex a qui' acsiquex Jaj Ts'urir irex ca jariquex u ber soc u tar rey.” Baxuc caj ya'araj Isaías uch.
\p 
\v 24 A mac tuchi'ta'b ten u winiquirob judío a fariseojo' caj c'uchob ich Juan.
\v 25 Caj c'uchob caj u c'atajob ti' Juan:
\p ―Biquinin ca wacsic ja' tu jo'r mac wa mʌ' tech Cristojech? Quire' mʌ' Elíasech xan, baxuc mʌ' yʌjtseq'uirech u t'ʌn C'uj xan?
\p 
\v 26 Juan caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―A teno' ra' in beyaj quir in wacsic ja' tu jo'r mac. Chen a mac jach no'j beyaj ti' yʌn tu yʌnechex baje'rer. Chen a techex mʌ' a c'ʌ'omʌnexi'.
\v 27 Raji' a cu tar pachir raji' jach no'j u beyaj chen a teno' mʌ' jach no'jen beyaj. Mʌ' pataren a teno' cax in chen pitic u c'anin pech' u xʌnʌb.
\p 
\v 28 Caj tarob u c'atej ti' Juan tu yʌn cu ya'aricob Betábara, raji' pichir ya'arir Jordán tu cu tar ic yum. Ti taro' Juan tan yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac.
\s1 Juan caj u ya'araj: Raji' irej u tʌmʌn yuc C'uj
\p 
\v 29 U jer u q'uinin Juan caj yiraj Jesús Juan. A Jesúso' tan u juts'ic u bʌj ich yicnʌn Juan. Caj ya'araj Juan:
\p ―Ir a wirex a je' cu taro' ts'a'b u beyaj ten C'uj. Raji' irej u tʌmʌn yuc C'uj quire' cu bin u quinsa'r soc u rʌc ruc'sic ic si'pirex. Baxuc tu cotor mac a ti' yʌn ich yoc'ocab.
\v 30 A jera' a tin yʌn bat'an araj tech uch caj in wa'araj techex: “A pachir cu taro', rajra' ti' yʌn a pachir cu tar cax mʌ' toy u rochen in nʌ' uch a ti'o'. Toc beri' ucho'.”
\p 
\v 31 Juan caj ya'araj:
\p ―A teno' xan mʌ' tin c'ʌ'otaj wa raji' ij cʌjtaquirex. Mʌ' ja wirej, taren in wacsic ja' tu jo'r u winiquirob judío soc u c'ʌ'oticob a cu tar ich C'ujo'.
\p 
\v 32 Juan caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―A teno' caj in wiraj u yeman u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj ich ca'anan, irej susuy caj c'uchij tu yʌni'. Ti' p'atij tu yʌni'.
\v 33 A teno' uch mʌ' tin c'ʌ'otaj. Chen a C'ujo' a tu ts'aj in beyaj quir in wacsic ja' tu jo'r mac caj ya'araj ten C'uj: “Ca' bin a wirej, quij C'uj, u yeman u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj. Ca wiric tu cu p'atʌr yejer. Raji' cu bin u ts'ic tech u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj.” Baxuc caj ya'araj C'uj ti' ten ―quij Juan―.
\v 34 Baxuc caj in wiraj, rajen quin wac techex raji' u parar C'uj.
\s1 U camsʌwinicob Jesús a tu yʌn pʌyaje'
\p 
\v 35 U jer u q'uinin a Juano' tiri' yʌn tu yʌn jo'raj. Ti' yʌn Juan yejer ca'tur u camsʌwinicob.
\v 36 Juan caj yiraj u man Jesús, caj u ya'araj ti' u camsʌwinicob:
\p ―Iriquex a jera', raji' irej u tʌmʌn yuc C'uj, quir u ruc'sic u si'pir tu cotor mac ich yoc'ocab.
\p 
\v 37 Caj yubob ya'aric Juan a ca'tur u camsʌwinicob Juan caj sayob tu pach Jesús.
\v 38 Jesús caj u sut u bʌj u pʌctej tu pach. Caj yiraj tan u tar tu pach, caj ara'b ti'ob:
\p ―Ba' ca cʌxtiquex? ―quij.
\p Robob caj ya'arob ti':
\p ―In wʌjcamsʌyʌjirechob, tu cʌja'anech?
\p 
\v 39 Jesús caj u nucaj ti'ob, tan ya'aric:
\p ―Cuxex a wirej.
\p Caj c'uchob tu yirajob tu cʌja'an. Jesús caj u yacsaj ti'ob quire' tabar u bin q'uin. Ti' wenob.
\p 
\v 40 Turiri' a tu yuba ya'aric Juan, a ca'tur u camsʌwinic, caj say tu pach Jesús, raji' u c'aba' Andrés. Raji' u sucu'un Simón Pedro.
\v 41 Seb caj bin u cʌxtej u sucu'un Simón. Caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Tin wiraj a cu ya'ara' Mesías ―raji' u c'at ya'aric Cristo a tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj.
\p 
\v 42 Andrés caj bin yejer u sucu'un tub yʌn Jesús. Caj irir Simón ten Jesús, caj u ya'araj ti':
\p ―A techo' ―quij Jesús―, Simónech, u pararech Jonás. Chen yʌn in pʌchic a c'aba' Cefas, aro' Pedro a c'aba' ―a Cefaso' ich u t'ʌn u winiquirob judío, quet ich u t'ʌn griego cu ya'aric Pedro.
\s1 Jesús cu pʌyic Felipe yejer Natanael
\p 
\v 43 Caj sasij Jesús u c'at u bin ich u ru'umin Galilea. Mʌ' toy xiqui' caj u nup'a Felipe caj ya'ara ti':
\p ―Sayen ―quij Jesús―, tin pach quir a cʌnic in t'ʌn.
\p 
\v 44 A je' Felipeja' ti' cʌja'an ich u cajar Betsaida. Tu cʌja'anob Andrés xan yejer Pedro.
\v 45 Felipe caj bin u cʌxtej Natanael, caj u yiraj caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Tij quiraj ―quij Felipe―, a mac ts'ibta'b ten ic nunquir Moisés uch ich u t'ʌnob. Baxuc raji'ob tu ts'ibtajob ic nunquir yʌjtseq'uirob u t'ʌn C'uj uch. Baxuc raji' u parar José a ti' cʌja'an ich u cajar Nazaret.
\p 
\v 46 Natanael caj c'ataj ti' Felipe tan ya'aric:
\p ―Mʌ' ij cu'wimʌn a mac jach tsoy a cu tar ich u cajar Nazaret.
\p Felipe caj u nuncaj:
\p ―Cojen irej ―quij ya'araj ti'.
\p 
\v 47 Jesús caj u yiraj tan u c'ʌs juts'ic u bʌj Natanael ich Jesús. Jesús caj ya'araj:
\p ―A je' cu tara' a mac taj u yor ich u winiquirob judío. Mʌ' yer bic tabar u tus aric mac.
\p 
\v 48 Natanael caj u c'ataj ti':
\p ―Bic a c'ʌ'otiquen?
\p Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―A teno' ―quij Jesús―, caj in wirech yaran u che'er higuera cax mʌ' toy u t'ʌnech Felipe.
\p 
\v 49 Caj ara'b ti' ten Natanael:
\p ―In wʌjcamsʌyʌjirech ―quij Natanael―, a techo' u pararech C'uj. Baxuc je' a wocar a reyintic u winiquirob judío.
\p 
\v 50 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti', tan ya'aric:
\p ―Quire' ―quij Jesús―, caj in wa'araj tech caj in wirech yaran u che'er higuera, rajen caj a wacsa ta wor ten? Jach tsoy baxuc, quire' ta wacsaj ta wor. Ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin je' in wesic tech jach manan in ne'er ba'.
\p 
\v 51 Baxuc xan Jesús caj u ya'araj ti' u camsʌwinicob.
\p ―Taj a ba' quin wac techex. A techexo' je' a wiriquex u q'ue'pʌjʌr ca'anan soc a wiriquex u yeman yʌjmasirob u t'ʌn C'uj tu yʌnen. Je' a wiriquex u nacar ich ca'anan yʌjmasirob u t'ʌn C'uj. Quire' a teno' baxuquenechexo'.
\c 2
\s1 Jesús caj bin yirej u ch'ic u rac' mac
\p 
\v 1 Caj manij mʌna' u nup u q'uinin caj ts'oc yiric Natanael yejer Felipe. Yʌn mac cu bin u ch'ic u rac' ich u cajar Caná ra' u wa'an u ru'umin Galilea. Ti' yʌn xan u nʌ' Jesús, tar yiric u ch'ic u rac' mac.
\v 2 Caj pay u camsʌwinicob Jesús caj yirajob u ch'ic u rac' mac. Yet payac Jesús.
\v 3 Ti' toy yʌn Jesús tu cu bin u ch'ic u rac' mac caj xup u c'ab uva. Caj ara'b ti' Jesús ten u nʌ':
\p ―Xup u c'ab uva. Biquinin mʌ' a yamtic ti'ob?
\p 
\v 4 Jesús caj ya'araj:
\p ―In nʌ'ech ―quij Jesús―, biquinin ca wa'aric ten xup? Mʌ' toy jach c'uchuc tu q'uinin soc in wesic in muc'.
\p 
\v 5 U nʌ' Jesús caj u ya'araj ti' u c'urewob a mac cu bin u ch'ic u rac':
\p ―Quibex a ba' cu ya'aric techex.
\p 
\v 6 Ti' t'ana'ani' u yajaw p'urir yoch ja', u cuchir tu cu t'ajic yoch ja' soc ti' cu p'o'icob u c'ʌb. Baxuc ti' cu p'o'icob yoc. Quire' baxuc u p'urir cu ch'ic ochenta litros yoch ja'.
\v 7 Jesús caj ya'araj ti' u c'urewob a mac a cu bin u ch'ic u rac':
\p ―Toc chupex ya'arir a je' t'ana'an u p'urir yoch ja'.
\p Tu toc chupaj u ya'arir u jor u p'urir.
\v 8 Jesús caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Jopex ca' xiquex a purex ti' yirej yʌjt'ʌjir a wo'ochex.
\p Caj binob u purej ti'.
\v 9 Yʌjt'ʌjir yoch caj u tumtaj ja' a waysa'b u c'ab uva. Chen mʌ' yer tub u tar ya'arir u c'ab uva. Chen u c'urewob yerob chen ja' ca'ch caj u jopajob. Rajen u yʌjt'ʌjir yo'och caj u t'ʌnaj a mac a cu ch'ic u rac'.
\v 10 Yʌjt'ʌjir yo'och caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―A rac'ob ―quij―, raji' cu bat'an ts'ic a jach tsoy u c'ab uva. Cu ts'ocar u yuq'uicob ya'ab u c'ab uva, cu ts'ic ti' u rac'ob u c'ab uva, a mʌ' quet yejer a tsoyo'. Chen tech ta ric'saj u c'ab uva a jach tsoyo' hasta baje'rer.
\p 
\v 11 Baxuc caj u betaj Jesús ich u cajar Caná, ra' u wa'an u ru'umin Galilea. Raji' u yʌnxchun u carem beyaj soc yesic ti' u rac'ob u winiquirob judío jach yʌn u muc' C'uj. Rajen u camsʌwinicob caj u yacsob tu yorob ti' quire' yerob u parar C'uj.
\p 
\v 12 Caj ts'oc aro' caj binob ich u cajar Capernaum. Jesús yejer u nʌ' yejer yits'inob yejer u camsʌwinicob. Chen mʌ' ya'ab u q'uinin ti' p'atob ich u cajar Capernaum.
\s1 Jesús cu joc'sic mac a cu canicob ba' ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob judío
\r (Mt. 21.12‑13; Mr. 11.15‑18; Lc. 19.45‑46)
\p 
\v 13 Tabar u c'uchur tu q'uinin u qui'qui' janʌnob u q'uinin pascua. Ra' u q'uinin u winiquirob judío quire' na'nij u c'ʌ'oticob quire' baxuc caj potmasta'b u winiquirob judío ich u ru'umin Egipto ten yʌjmasir u t'ʌn C'uj uch. Caj bin Jesús yejer u camsʌwinicob ich u cajar Jerusalén.
\v 14 Caj bin Jesús tu re'a'an carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob judío. Ti' tu yiraj mac ich carem naj. A mac cu canicob yʌrʌc' wacʌx a tono' yejer tʌmʌn yuc yejer susuj. Rʌc ti' yʌnob tu re'a'an carem naj. Caj irir xan ti' cura'an yʌjc'axir u taq'uin soc u c'oxar u taq'uin a mac a cu tar nach.
\v 15 Rajen caj u cʌxtaj sum soc u jit'ic quir u jats'ʌr u pachob. Caj u rʌc joc'saj ich carem naj tu cotor a mac a cu canicob yʌrʌc' tʌmʌn yuc yejer yʌrʌc' wacʌx a tono'. Baxuc a mac cu c'axicob u taq'uinob mac caj u rʌc wec u taq'uinob yejer u pojche'irob u taq'uinob.
\v 16 Jesús caj u ya'araj ti' a mac a cu canic susuj:
\p ―Toc rʌc joc'sex a wʌrʌc' susuj. Quire' raji' yatoch in Tet, mʌ' a c'axiquex irej tu cu naj co'nan ba'.
\p 
\v 17 Caj u yirob ba' tu betaj Jesús, rajen c'aj ti' u camsʌwinicob Jesús a ba' ts'iba'an ich u t'ʌn C'uj uch: “Quire' q'uex in wor ti' yatoch C'uj rajen cu bin u p'actiquen mac.” Baxuc ara'b ich u t'ʌn C'uj uch.
\p 
\v 18 U jach ts'urirob sacerdote caj u c'atob ti' Jesús tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Mac caj u ts'aj a beyaj quir a joc'sic mac a cu canicob ba' ich carem naj? Ese tenob carem beyaj soc in werob mac caj u ts'aj a beyaj.
\p 
\v 19 Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Jubse a je' carem naja' ca' bin c'uchuc mʌna' u nup u q'uinin, quin bin in ca' ric'sej u jer ric'ben.
\p 
\v 20 U jach ts'urirob sacerdote caj ya'arob:
\p ―Yʌn cuarenta y seis yaxq'uin caj ts'oc u ts'ʌpquintic u tunichir quir u ts'ocsicob a je' carem naja'. Bic tabar tech ca' bin a ric'sic mʌna' u nup u q'uinin?
\p 
\v 21 Jesús tan u tsicbar ti' u winquirir, mʌ' cu ya'aric jach carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob judío.
\v 22 Rajen caj riq'uij Jesús ich u quimirir. U camsʌwinicob c'aj ti'ob a ba' ara'b ti' u jach ts'urirob sacerdote ten Jesús. Ra'iri' u q'uinin caj u quibob u t'ʌn C'uj tu ts'iba'an tan ya'aric: “Je' u ca' riq'uir tu quimirir.” Rajen yerob taj u camsʌwinicob a ba' ara'b ti' u jach ts'urirob sacerdote ten Jesús.
\s1 Jesús yer ba' cu tucricob tu cotor mac
\p 
\v 23 Ti' p'at Jesús yejer u camsʌwinicob ich u cajar Jerusalén hasta caj ts'oc u man u q'uinin pascua. Ya'ab mac caj u yacsaj tu yor quire' yerob yʌjtaquirob quire' yirob u carem beyajob Jesús.
\v 24 Quire' Jesús yer ba' cu tucric tu cotor mac rajen yer mac mʌ' quet yor yejeri'.
\v 25 A Jesúso' mʌ' ba'wir cu tar ya'aric ti' bicyʌra' mac quire' Jesús u toc er bicyʌra'.
\c 3
\s1 Nicodemo cu tar u tsicbar yejer Jesús
\p 
\v 1 A ucho' ti' yʌn u winiquir judío a fariseojo' a ucho', raji'o' u c'aba' Nicodemo. Raji' turiri' u ts'urir ich u winiquirob judío. A fariseojo' cu quibicob a ba' ara'b ten u nunquir u winiquirob judío.
\v 2 Oq'uin caj bin Nicodemo tu yʌn Jesús quir u tsicbar yejer. Caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―In wʌjcamsʌyʌjirech. In wer C'uj tu tuchi'tech quir a camsico'on. Wa mʌ' C'uj tu tuchi'tech, mʌ' c'ucha'an a wor a wesic carem beyaj an ten bic ca betic.
\p 
\v 3 Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Taj quin wa'aric tech. A mac u c'at u yocar tu cu reyintic C'uj, u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj yʌn u ts'ic u cuxtar a cu tar ich ca'anan. Irej wa ju ca' rocha'r ten u nʌ'.
\p 
\v 4 Nicodemo caj ya'araj ti' Jesús:
\p ―Bic tabar u ca' rochar ten u nʌ' quire' uch ch'ijic? Mʌ' c'ucha'an yor u ca' ocar ich u nʌc' winic soc u ca' rocha' ten u nʌ'.
\p 
\v 5 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti', tan ya'aric ti':
\p ―Taj a ba' quin wac tech. Mʌ' chen jari' ja' cu yacsa' ta jo'r, ca' a c'ʌmej u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj quire' baxuc toc ara'b ten C'uj. A baywo' c'ucha'an a wor a wocar tu cu reyintic C'uj.
\v 6 Tu q'uinin caj u rochech a nʌ', raji' quir a chen cuxtar ich yoc'ocab. Tu q'uinin cu ts'ic tech a cuxtar u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj, ra' cu tar ich ca'anan, raji' quir a cuxtar munt q'uin. Aro' irej wa tu ca' rochech a nʌ'.
\v 7 Mʌ' ju jac'ʌr a wor Nicodemo quire' tin wa'araj tech aro'. Mʌ' ja wirej, u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj je' u ts'ic a cuxtar a cu tar ich ca'anan soc c'ucha'an a wor a bin ca'anan.
\v 8 A ic'o' cu rʌc man tu cotor. Ca wu'yic u jum, chen mʌ' a wer tub u tar, mʌ' ja wer, tu cu bin. Baxuc aro' tu cotor mac a ts'ab u cuxtar a cu tar ich ca'anan ten u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj. Cu chen beyaj ti' techex chen mʌ' a werex bic tabar.
\p 
\v 9 Nicodemo, mʌ' toy u jach qui' najti' caj u ca' nuncaj, tan ya'aric:
\p ―Bic tabar cu betic a baxuc aro'?
\p 
\v 10 Jesús caj a nuncaj ti' tan ya'aric:
\p ―A techo' a ne'er a camsic, ca chen camsic u winiquirob judío. Mʌ' wa ja najtej a tin wa'araj tech?
\v 11 Jach taj quin wa'aric tech Nicodemo. A tenob in wa'aricob tech a ba' in werob, baxuc a ba' tin wirob. Chen techex mʌ' ja quibex a ba' quin wa'aricob.
\v 12 Wa mʌ' ja quibiquex a ba' quin tsicbar techex, a ba' yʌn ich yoc'ocab an ten bic caj in wa'araj yʌn u ca' rochiquech a nʌ'. Je' wa ja quibic a ba' quin wa'aric techex, a ba' yʌn ich ca'anan?
\p 
\v 13 Jesús caj ya'araj:
\p ―Mʌna' mac binij ich ca'anan caj wʌc'ʌs ur tera' quir ya'aric bicyʌra' ca'anan. Chen a teno' c'ucha'an in wor in wa'aric bicyʌra' quire' ti' in tar ich ca'anan quire' a teno' irenechex. Ti' quin wʌc'ʌs bin xan.
\v 14 An ten bic ic nunquir Moisés caj u nacsaj can a beta'b ti' mascab, caj u nacsa yejer che' ich tacay ru'um. Soc raji' quir u jawʌr a mac chi'bir ten can wa cu pʌctic. An ten bic a cano' caj nacsa'b ich che' baxuc ten ca' bin u bʌjen ich cruz soc u nacsiquen soc in jawsic u si'pir mac quire' a teno' irenechex.
\v 15 Wa mac cu yacsic tu yor ten quire' bin u ca' bʌjbiren ich cruz soc in taquic ti'ob, je' u cuxtar munt q'uin.
\s1 Ic Tet C'uj cu yajquintic tu cotor mac
\p 
\v 16 ’Mʌ' ja wirej, a C'ujo' jach manan cu yajquintic tu cotor mac ich yoc'ocab. Rajen tu tuchi'taj u parar turiri'. Rajen tu cotor mac a cu yacsic tu yor ti' cu bin tacbir soc mʌ' u bin erar ich c'ac'. Chen cu bin ts'abʌr u cuxtar munt q'uin.
\v 17 Ic Tet C'uj tu tuchi'taj u parar tera' ich yoc'ocab. Mʌ' tarij quir u ts'ic u muc'yaj a ti' yʌn ich yoc'ocab quire' yʌn u si'pirob. Mʌ' ja wirej, tarij quir u yamtic tu cotor mac.
\p 
\v 18 ’A mac cu yacsic tu yor ti' cu bin tacbir ten u parar C'uj, mʌ' ju bin u bo'otic u bo'orir u si'pir. Chen a mac a mʌ' u c'at u to'car ten u parar C'uj. A C'ujo' caj u toc tetaj tub u wich u bin, quire' mʌ' tu quibaj u t'ʌn u parar a turiri', raji' ij cʌj taquir.
\v 19 Mʌ' ja wirej, tarij u parar C'uj ich yoc'ocab quire' tu toc tucraj a C'ujo' bic cu bin u ruc'sic u si'pir mac. Mʌ' ja wirej, ca' bin tac u sasirir a a'ac'biro' chʌca'an a wiric ba' u ber wa c'as. Baxuc xan caj tar u parar C'uj chʌca'an yiric wa yʌn u si'pir tu cotor mac. Chen a winiquiro' mʌ' u c'at u tar tu yʌn u parar C'uj quire' cu manob tu c'asir quire' raji'ob cu jach pachticob u si'pirob.
\v 20 Quire' tu cotor mac a na'nij cu betic a c'aso' mʌ' u c'at ca' iric a ba' cu betic. Rajen mʌ' u c'at u tar tu yʌn u parar C'uj.
\v 21 Chen a mac a rajra' cu betic a ba' u c'at C'uj, mʌ' ju ch'a'ej sajquir u tar yicnʌn u parar C'uj. Mʌ' ja wirej, irir raji'ob yamta'b ten C'uj.
\s1 Juan a cu yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac, cu tsicbʌtic Jesús
\p 
\v 22 Pachir caj binij Jesús yejer u camsʌwinicob ich u ru'umin Judea. Ti' p'at yejer u camsʌwinicob ya'ab u q'uinin. Jesús tu ts'aj u beyaj quir u yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac wa tu quib u t'ʌn.
\v 23 Baxuc Juan xan tan yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac ich u cajar Enón. A Enóno' c'ʌs bʌytʌc u cajar Salim. Quire' ti' yʌn ya'ab yic' ja'. A mac c'uchob ich Juan caj ac'sa'b ja' tu jo'r wa tu quib u t'ʌn xan.
\v 24 Quire' a Juano', mʌ' toy chucuc quir u ma'cʌr, tan yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac ich u cajar Enón.
\p 
\v 25 Yʌn u camsʌwinicob Juan mʌ' qui' yorob quire' u winiquirob judío tan u binob ich Jesús ca' acsac ja' tu jo'rob. Rajen u camsʌwinicob Juan quet tan u chich aricob turiri' u winiquir judío.
\v 26 U camsʌwinicob Juan caj binob ya'arej ti' Juan tan ya'aricob ti':
\p ―In wʌjcamsʌyʌjirech a mac tarij tub yʌnech uch ich pʌchir ya'arir Jordán a mac a ta wa'araj uch yʌn u tar. A baje'rer ti' yʌn tan yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac, tu cotor mac tan u rʌc bin yicnʌn.
\p 
\v 27 Juan caj u nuncaj tan ya'aric ti'ob:
\p ―Mʌ' ja wirej, u bʌjiri' C'uj cu ts'ic u beyaj ti' mac a ba' yʌn u betej.
\v 28 A techexo' caj a wu'yajex mʌ' jin mucraj tin toc araj: Mʌ' Cristojen. Mʌ' taren in taquechex. A C'ujo', tu ts'aj in beyaj quir in chen pʌyic u ber ij cʌjtaquirex.
\v 29 A mac a caj u raq'uintaj a je' xquica' raji' u mam. A mac u jach yajo' cu yiric tan u ch'ic u rac'. Cu yubic u tsicbar cu qui' tar yor yubic tan u ch'ic u rac'. Aro' baxuc ten, jach qui' in wor in wiric u bin a pimo' ich Jesús.
\p 
\v 30 Juan caj ya'araj:
\p ―Mʌ' u neman u jumin ten, chen a Jesúso', ra' cu jach jumintejob, quire' baxuc u c'at C'uj.
\s1 A mac a cu tar ich ca'anano'
\p 
\v 31 Juan caj ya'araj ti' u camsʌwinicob:
\p ―A Jesúso' tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj tera' ich yoc'ocab, raji' u ts'urir tu cotor ba'. A teno' ―quij Juan―, te' toc yʌnena' ich yoc'ocab, quin chen beyaj a tera'. A teno', quin chen aric techex a ba' quin wiric ich yoc'ocab. A Jesúso' tar u tar ich ca'anan, rajen u ne'er tu cotor ba'. Rajen neyʌn u muc'.
\v 32 A Jesúso' cu ya'aric a ba' caj u yiraj tu yʌn a C'ujo'. Baxuc a ba' caj u yubaj, raji' cu ya'aric. Chen mʌ' ya'abi' cu quibic a ba' cu yac.
\v 33 Chen a mac a cu quibic u t'an Jesús quire' tarij ich ca'anan tan u quibic a ba' ara'b ti' Jesús ten C'uj.
\v 34 A Jesúso' tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj, rajen cu ya'aric u t'ʌn C'uj. A C'ujo' mʌ' ju p'isej mun cu ts'abʌr ti' Jesús u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj. mʌ' ja wirej, rajra' yʌn u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj ti'.
\v 35 Ic Tet C'uj cu yajquintic u parar rajen caj u ts'aj ti' tu cotor a ba' yʌn ti', C'uj ca' u cʌnantej u parar.
\v 36 Tu cotor mac a cu yacsic tu yor ti' u parar cu bin tacbir ten u parar C'uj. Munt q'uin cu bin cuxtar. Tu cotor mac a mʌ' u c'at u yacsic tu yor ti', mʌ' u bin tacbir ten u parar C'uj. Mʌ' u bin cuxtar munt q'uin, tar cu bin ich c'ac'. Yʌn u ts'abʌr u muc'yaj ten C'uj.
\c 4
\s1 Jesús cu tsicbar yejer xquic a ti' cʌja'ano' tu cajar Samaria
\p 
\v 1 Jesús tu najtaj ti' a ba' ara'b ten mac ti' a fariseojo'. U camsʌwinicob Jesús tan u pimtar quire' tan u jach pimtar a mac acsa'b ja' tu jo'rob. Tan u jach osar u camsʌwinicob Juan. Baxuc ara'b ti' a fariseojo' ten mac.
\v 2 Baxuc caj juminta'b ti' Jesús. Chen u bʌjiri' Jesús mʌ' ju yacsaj ja' tu jo'rob mac. Chen u camsʌwinicob raji'ob cu yacsic ja' tu jo'rob mac.
\v 3 Quire' Jesús yer ba' cu ya'aricob a fariseojo' quire' mʌ' u c'atob yiricob u pimtar u yacsicob tu yorob ti' Jesús. Rajen ruq'uij ich u ru'umin Judea soc u wʌc'ʌs bin ich u ru'umin Galilea.
\p 
\v 4 Ra' u berir tu cu bin uch, ti' cu ch'ʌctic u ru'umin u c'aba' Samaria.
\v 5 Ti' c'uchob Jesús yejer u camsʌwinicob ich u cajar Sicar. Ra' u cajar ich u ru'umin Samaria. Aro' jach bʌytʌc ti' u ru'umin a ti' ts'ab ti' José uch ten u tet Jacob.
\v 6 Ti' yʌn yic' ja' ich ru'um chen tam yʌn ya'arir. Raji' u nunquir u winiquirob judío caj u panaj uch, Jacob u c'aba'. Quire' Jesús ca'anij tu cu tar ich bej. Tan u jesic u bʌj bʌytʌc tu yʌn yic' ja'. Bʌytʌc c'ac'chunq'uin.
\v 7 Caj tarij xquic a ti' cʌja'an ich u ru'umin Samaria. Quir u paytic yoch ja' quire' tam. Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Chan chuquej ―quij Jesús―, ten ja' quir in wuq'uic.
\p 
\v 8 Mʌ' ja wirej, u camsʌwinicob Jesús, binob ich u cajar Sicar quir u mʌnicob yo'och.
\v 9 A xquico' a ti' cʌja'an tu ru'umin Samaria caj u ya'araj ti' Jesús:
\p ―Biquinin ca c'atic ten ja' quire mʌ' u winiquir judíojen? U xquiquiren u ru'umin Samaria.
\p Baxuc caj ya'araj a xquico' quire' p'acta'b u winiquirob samaria ten u winiquirob judío.
\v 10 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti', tan ya'aric:
\p ―Wa ja chen er C'uj u c'at u sijic tech ba', wa ta c'ʌ'otajen a mac a tu ya'araj tech: “Chan chuquej ten ja' quir in wuq'uic”, a techo' jach jaj ta yʌn bat'an c'ata ten sam ja' ca' in ts'a tech ja' soc raji' quir a cuxtar munt q'uin.
\p 
\v 11 A xquico' caj ya'araj:
\p ―Jaj Ts'urir ―quij―. A techo' mʌna' quir a paytic ja' quire' tam yic' ya'arir. Bic tabar ca bin a ts'ic ja' ten, a ray ja'o' an ten bic caj a wa'araj ten?
\v 12 Ic nunquir Jacob caj u p'ʌta to'on a je' yic' ja'a'. Quire' u bʌjiri' ti' tu yuc'aj xan uch. Baxuc ti' caj u yuc'ob u pararob xan, baxuc ti' caj u yuc'ob u yʌrʌc'. Jach manan wa no'jech ta beyaj a techo', c'ucha'an waj a wor a ts'ic ten ja' an ten bic ta wa'araj?
\p 
\v 13 Jesús caj u nuncaj, caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Tu cotor mac a cu yuq'uic a je' ja'a', je' u ca' uc'chʌjʌre' cax a wuq'uej.
\v 14 A mac a cu yuq'uic ja' a quin ts'ic a ti'o', mʌ' ju bin yʌnyʌn uc'chʌjʌr. Quire' a ja'o' a quin ts'ic ti', cu wayʌr yic' ja' irej u bosirʌncʌr ja' tu pixam soc u cuxtar munt q'uin.
\p 
\v 15 Mʌ' toy u najti', wa tan u tsicbar ti' u cuxtar munt q'uin, rajen a xquico' caj ya'araj:
\p ―Jaj Ts'urir ―quij―, chan chuquej a je' ja'a' a caj a wa'araj ca' in wuq'uej soc mʌ' in yʌnyʌn uc'chʌjʌr baxuc soc mʌ' in ca' tar in t'uyic in woch ja' yejer sum.
\p 
\v 16 Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Joq'uen pʌyej a mam soc a tar yejer.
\p 
\v 17 A xquico' caj u nuncaj caj u ya'araj:
\p ―Mʌna' in mam ―quij ya'araj ti' Jesús.
\p Rajen Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Taj caj a wa'araj ten mʌna' a mam
\v 18 quire' yʌn tech cinco a mam jach jaj uch. Rajra' tan a tuchi'tic ca' xic a mac jach raji' a mam. Rajen a ba' ta wa'araj sam taj quire' mʌ' jach a mami', cax ti' cʌja'anech yejer.
\p 
\v 19 A xquico', caj ts'oc yubic a ba' ara'b ti' ten Jesús, caj ya'araj:
\p ―Jaj Ts'urir ―quij―, quin wiric irech yʌjtseq'uirech u t'ʌn C'uj.
\v 20 Quire' in nunquirob uch tu c'ujinticob C'uj uch ich a je' u jo'r u witsira'. Chen techex ca wa'ariquex ca' xiquenob ich u cajar Jerusalén quir in c'ujinticob C'uj.
\p 
\v 21 Jesús caj ya'araj:
\p ―Quibej a ba' quin wa'aric tech, xquic. Ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin, mʌ' ju bin ya'aricob ca' in c'ujintejob C'uj ich a je' jo'r witsira'. Mʌ' ju bin u ya'aricob: “Ca' ij c'ujintej C'uj ich u cajar Jerusalén.”
\v 22 A techexo' u winiquirechex samaria mʌ' a werex C'uj, a mac a ca c'ujintiquex. Chen u winiquirob judío yerob in Tet C'ujob, a mac in c'ujinticob quire' ara'b ti'ob ten C'uj: “Bin in ca' in tar quir in taquicob quire' p'eri'en yejer u winiquirob judío.”
\v 23 Baje'rer c'uchij tu q'uinin tu cotor mac a cu qui' acsic tu yorob, taj cu bin u c'ujinticob ic Tet C'uj tu pixam. Quire' baxuc u c'at ic Tet C'uj, taj ca' u c'ujintejob ten mac tu pixamob.
\v 24 Ic Tet C'uj mʌ' c'ucha'an a worex a wiric quire' mʌna' u winquirir. Rajen mʌ' ja wirej. Baxuco' mʌ' c'ucha'an a wor a wiric a mac a taj cu c'ujintic C'uj tu pixam. Quire' tu pixamob taj cu c'ujinticob C'uj. Baxuc C'uj u c'at taj ca' ij c'ujintej ―baxuc caj u ya'araj Jesús.
\p 
\v 25 A xquico' caj ya'araj:
\p ―In wer mac cu bin tar cu ya'ara' Mesías ―raji' u c'at ya'aric Cristo cu bin ts'abir u beyaj ten C'uj quir u taquic mac tu cotor ca' bin tac―. Raji' cu bin u camsico'on tu cotor ba'.
\p 
\v 26 Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Raji'en a tan in tsicbar yejerech.
\p 
\v 27 Ra'iri' u q'uinin caj urob u camsʌwinicob tu bin u mʌnejob yo'och. Caj jac'ob yorob caj yirob Jesús tan u tsicbar yejer xquic. Mʌ' ja wirej, a mac a cu camsic u t'ʌn C'uj mʌ' ju tsicbar yejer xquic ich tan bej, baxuc na'nij cu betic u winiquirob judío. U camsʌwinicob surac u c'atob: “Biquinin ca tsicbar yejer xquic baxuc aro'?”
\v 28 Rajen a xquico' caj u p'ʌta u p'urir yoch ja' tu chi' u jorir ya'arir caj bin ich u cajar Sicar. Caj c'uchij caj ya'araj ti' u rac'ob:
\p 
\v 29 ―Cojenex ―quij―, ca' a wirex a mac a tu ya'araj tu cotor ba' a tin betaj. Jaj ix tʌco wa raji' ti' Cristo a cu bin tuchi'bir ten C'uj.
\p 
\v 30 Rajen seb caj tarob ich Jesús caj joc'ob tu cajar.
\v 31 Caj bin a xquico' ca'ch, u camsʌwinicob tan u chich a'aricob ti' Jesús:
\p ―In wʌjcamsʌyʌjirech chan janen.
\p 
\v 32 Jesús caj u nunca tan ya'aric ti'ob:
\p ―Yʌn ten quir in janʌn. A ba' yʌn ten mʌ' a werex wa yʌn ten.
\p 
\v 33 U camsʌwinicob caj pacran tsicbanʌjob tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Yʌn wa mac tar u puric yo'och quir u janʌn?
\p 
\v 34 Jesús caj ya'araj ti' u camsʌwinicob:
\p ―Ra' in woch a teno' ca' in betej a ba' u c'at C'uj quire' raji' tu tuchi'tajen. Ca' in ts'ocsej a tu ts'aj in beyaj.
\p 
\v 35 Jesús caj ya'araj ti' u camsʌwinicob:
\p ―Baxuc ca waquex tech yʌn cuatro ic nʌ' quir ic wʌtic ij co'och trigo. U'yex ba' quin wac techex. Pʌctex a wirex a ra' cu tar winiquirob tub yʌno'on. Raji'ob irob trigo a cu tijire' ich cor quir u wʌtic.
\v 36 Jeroj c'uchij tu q'uinin a yamtic mac u yacsic tu yor ten. Irechex a mac tan a wʌtiquex trigo ich cor a tiquino'. A mac a cu yamtic mac ca' u yacsej tu yor, irob a mac a cu maric yoch trigo a tiquine'. Je' u qui' acsa'rob ten C'uj. A mun cu bin yambir ca' u yacsej tu yor cu bin cuxtar munt q'uin. Rajen p'eri' qui' yorob a mac a cu ts'abʌr ti' u t'ʌn C'uj tu pixam mac yejer a mac a cu yamtic ca' u yacsej tu yor.
\v 37 Quire' taj a cu ya'aric mac: “Turiri' yʌjpʌq'uir turiri' yʌjwʌtir.”
\v 38 A teno' caj in ts'aj a beyajex techex quir a mariquex a mac a tu yacsaj tu yor ten. Quin tuchi'tiquechex tub mʌ' beyajnʌja'anechex. Mʌ' ja wirej, u jer mac tu pʌc'aj u t'ʌn C'uj tu pixamob. Quire' ra' a beyaj a techexo' quir a qui' camsic ti'ob ti' u t'ʌn C'uj soc u qui' acsicob tu yorob.
\p 
\v 39 Ya'ab u winiquirob samaria a cʌja'anob ich u cajar Sicar tu yacsob tu yorob ti' Jesús quire' a ba' tu tsicbʌtaj a xquico' ti'ob quire' tu yubob ya'aric: “Raji' tu ya'araj ten tu cotor ba' caj in betaj uch.”
\v 40 Caj tarob u winiquirob samaria ich Jesús. Caj u chich arob ca' p'atʌc yejerob. Ti' p'atij Jesús ca'tur u q'uinin.
\v 41 Ya'ab u winiquirob samaria caj u yacsajob tu yorob a ba' caj u yubob ya'aric Jesús xan.
\v 42 Rajen ya'ab u winiquirob samaria caj u ya'arajob ti' a xquico':
\p ―Baje'rer tij cacsaj tij cor, mʌ' chen tij cu'yaj a wa'aric. Quire' tij cu'yaj u t'ʌn Jesús, rajen ij quer raji' Cristo a tar u taquic tu cotor mac ich yoc'ocab.
\s1 Jesús cu jawsic u parar a mac a cu beyajo' ti' rey
\p 
\v 43 Caj ts'oc u man ca'tur u q'uinin. Caj ruc' Jesús ich u ru'umin Samaria quir u bin ich u ru'umin Galilea.
\v 44 Caj binob ich u ru'umin Galilea quire' yerob mʌna' mac cu bin u p'actic Jesús ca'ch quire' mʌ' sʌjta'b ten u rac'ob. Quire' Jesús caj u ya'araj: “A mac a cu tsec'tic u t'ʌn C'uj mʌ' u bin sʌjta'bir tu ch'ijir.”
\v 45 Caj c'uchij Jesús ich u ru'umin Galilea, mac ti' cʌja'anob qui' yorob yiricob Jesús. Mʌ' ja wirej, tu yirob tu cotor a ba' caj u betaj Jesús u q'uinin pascua ich u cajar Jerusalén quire' binob xan.
\p 
\v 46 Jesús caj wʌc'ʌs bin ich u cajar Caná ra' u wa'an u ru'umin Galilea tu' tu waysaj ja' u c'ab uva. Ti' yʌn mac a cu tar ti' u cajar Capernaum. Raji' cu beyaj ti' rey. Raji' u parar yaj.
\v 47 A cu beyaj ti' rey caj yuba ya'aric c'uchij Jesús tar u tar ich u ru'umin Judea baje'rer c'uchij ich u ru'umin Galilea. Caj bin yirej quir u chich pʌyic ca' xic ich yatoch quir u jawsa' u parar quire' tabar u quimin.
\v 48 Caj c'uchij ich Jesús caj ara'b ti' ten Jesús:
\p ―A techexo' mʌ' ja quibiquex cax jach manan in muc' hasta ca wiriquex carem in beyaj.
\p 
\v 49 Chen a mac a cu beyaj ti' rey caj ya'araj ti' Jesús:
\p ―In Jaj Ts'urir ―quij―, sepquintej a tar, mʌ' toy quimic in parar.
\p 
\v 50 Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Ca' xiquech ta watoch je' u jawʌr a parar.
\p A xibo' tu quibaj u t'ʌn a ba' ara'b ti' ten Jesús. Caj wʌc'ʌs sutnʌj tu yatoch
\v 51 Tabar u c'uchur tu yatoch caj bin nupbir ten u c'urew ich bej. Tar u tar ich yatoch caj ara'b ti':
\p ―A parar jawij.
\p 
\v 52 A xibo' caj u c'ataj ti' u c'urew:
\p ―Tu' q'uin caj jawij?
\p U c'urew caj ya'araj:
\p ―Jo'raj c'ʌs sarpʌj u q'uinin caj jawij u chʌcwirir u jo'r.
\p 
\v 53 U tet u parar caj u c'ʌ'otaj ra'iri' u q'uinin caj ara'b ti' ten Jesús jo'raj: “Je' u jawʌr a parare'”; rajen a xibo' yejer tu cotor mac ti' yʌn tu yatoch caj u yacsob tu yorob ti' Jesús.
\p 
\v 54 A jera' u carem beyaj tu ca' esaj Jesús soc yesic yʌn u muc' C'uj. Raji' tu betaj caj urij ich u ru'umin Judea caj c'uchij ich u ru'umin Galilea.
\c 5
\s1 Jesús cu jawsic a mecho', a mac a characbar tu cuch yacʌr ya'arir, u c'aba' ya'arir Betesda
\p 
\v 1 Pachir caj c'uchij tu q'uinin u qui'qui' janʌn u winiquirob judío. Ra' u q'uinin pascua, ca'ten binob Jesús yejer u camsʌwinicob ich u cajar Jerusalén.
\v 2 Ti' yʌn ich u cajar Jerusalén tu cuch yacʌr ya'arir. Ti' yʌn tu cu yocar yʌrʌc' tʌmʌn yuc ich u jor u pa'te'ir tunich. Tar cu binob ich carem naj a tʌmʌn yuco'. Yʌn u c'aba' tu cu yacʌr ya'arir u c'aba' Betesda. Baxuc cu ya'aric ich u t'ʌn hebreo Betesda. Ti' c'ʌxa'an cinco yatoch tu nʌc' tu cuch u yacʌr ya'arir. Chen yatochob mʌ' pa'te'ta'an.
\v 3 Ti' much'a'anob ya'ab u yajirir yejer ch'op u wich yejer a mac mech yoc yejer a mac a mʌ' ju riq'uir. Rʌc ti' yʌnob ich yatochob tu cuch yacʌr ya'arir characbarob ich ru'um. Quire' tan u pajicob u pecsa'r ya'arir.
\v 4 Mʌ' ja wirej, tar cu yeman yʌjmasir u t'ʌn C'uj tu cuch yacʌr ya'arir. Tenten cu yeman yʌjmasir u t'ʌn C'uj quir u pecsic ya'arir. Caj ts'oc u pecsa' ya'arir, a mac yʌn pʌybej em ich ya'arir caj jawij u yajir cax ba' yajirir.
\v 5 Ti' yʌn turi' u winiquir judío jach uch tu cʌnaj u yajir. Yʌn treinta y ocho yaxq'uin ti'.
\v 6 Jesús caj u yiraj ti' chara'an. Yer uch yajac rajen caj u ya'araj ti':
\p ―A c'at wa ja jawʌr?
\p 
\v 7 A yajo' caj u nunca tan ya'aric:
\p ―In Jaj Ts'urir ―quij―, mʌna' mac cu bin u yacsiquen tu cuch u yacʌr ya'arir, cu ts'ocar u pecsa'r ya'arir. Cax in c'at in wocar, u jer cu tar, raji' cu bat'an ocar.
\p 
\v 8 Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Riq'uen cats'e yor xa'an ca' ximbanʌquech.
\p 
\v 9 Seb caj jawij caj u cats'a yor xa'an caj u yʌnxchun u ximbar. Chen ra' u q'uinin cu jesic u bʌj u winiquirob judío caj jawsa'b ten Jesús.
\v 10 Rajen u winiquirob judío caj ya'arob ti' a mac jawsa'b:
\p ―Ti' toy u q'uinin quir ic jesic ic bʌjex, tech tan a cʌrʌxbetic u t'ʌn Moisés quire' tan a cuchic yor xa'an.
\p 
\v 11 A xibo' caj u nuncaj tan ya'aric ti'ob:
\p ―A mac a tu jawsajen. Raji' caj u ya'araj ten: “Cats'ej yor xa'an ca' ximbanʌquech” ―quij.
\p 
\v 12 Robob caj u c'atob ti':
\p ―Mac caj u ya'araj tech cats'ej yor xa'an ca' ximbanʌquech?
\p 
\v 13 A jawsa'b u yajirir mʌ' yer mac jawsej quire' seb caj binij Jesús quire' pim winicob caj u much'quintajob u bʌj.
\v 14 Pachir Jesús caj u nup'aj tu jap'nin carem naj. Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Jawech baje'rer. Mʌ' toy jawac a si'pir wa ca p'atʌr ich a si'pir, jach manan ca bin a muc'yaj.
\p 
\v 15 A xibo' caj bin ich u jach ts'urirob sacerdote caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―A mac a tu jawseni', raji' Jesús.
\p 
\v 16 Quire' Jesús caj u jawsaj a xibo' u q'uinin u jesic u bʌj u winiquirob judío rajen u jach ts'urirob sacerdote cu p'acticob Jesús. U c'atob u quinsicob Jesús.
\v 17 Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―In Teto' ti' toy cu beyaj. Baxuc aro' ti' toy quin beyaj xan.
\p 
\v 18 Rajen u jach ts'urirob sacerdote u c'atob u jach quinsicob Jesús. Cu tucricob mʌ' ju cʌnantaj u q'uinin tu cu jesicob u bʌj u winiquirob judío. Bayiri' quire' caj ya'araj: “Raji' in Tet C'uj.” Baxuc tu p'eri'quintaj u bʌj yejer C'uj.
\s1 U parar C'uj, raji' ts'a'b u beyaj ten C'uj
\p 
\v 19 Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Taj a ba' quin wac techex, a teno' u pararen C'uj. In bʌjiri' mʌ' c'ucha'an in wor ti' ba'. Quin chen betic a ba' quin wiric u betic in Tet. A ba' cu betic in Tet, baxuc a teno' quin betic quire' u pararen.
\v 20 In Tet cu yajquintiquen quire' u pararen. Cu yesic ten tu cotor ba' cu betic. Techex baje'rer ta wirex chichin a ba' caj in betaj. Je' u cha'ic in betic C'uj jach manan carem in beyaj. Ca' bin ts'ocac in betic, jach manan cu bin jac'ʌr a worex.
\v 21 An ten bic in Tet cu ric'sic a quimeno' soc u ts'ic u cuxtar. Baxuc a teno' quin ts'ic u ca' cuxtar a mac in c'at u ca' cuxtarob.
\v 22 In Teto' mʌ' ju bin u jʌsic a mac yʌn u si'pirob. Chen tu ya'araj ten, quire' u pararen, soc in jʌsic a mac yʌn u si'pirob.
\v 23 Rajen tu cotor mac je' u sʌjtiquen an ten bic cu sʌjticob in Tet. A mac a mʌ' ju sʌjtiquen cax u pararen C'uj, baxuc mʌ' ju sʌjta' in Tet a mac a tu tuchi'tajen.
\p 
\v 24 Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Taj quin wa'aric techex: C'uchij tu q'uinin a mac a cu yubic in t'ʌn a teno' u pararen C'uj, a mac a cu yubic in t'ʌn wa cu yacsic tu yor ti' a mac a tu tuchi'tajen, je' u cuxtar munt q'uin. Mʌ' ju bin ts'abir u muc'yaj. Baxuc mʌ' ju bin satʌr chen cu bin ts'abir u cuxtar ric'ben quir u cuxtar munt q'uin.
\v 25 Taj quin wa'aric techex. C'uchij tu q'uinin a mac a cu yubic in t'ʌn a teno' u pararen C'uj. A techexo' irechex wa quimrechex ʌcʌtan ten. A mac a cu yacsic tu yor in t'ʌn je' u cuxtar munt q'uine'.
\v 26 An ten bic in Tet C'uj yʌn u muc' quir u ts'ic u cuxtar munt q'uin ti' mac. Baxuc caj u ts'aj ten u muc' quir in ts'ic u cuxtar munt q'uin ti' mac, quire' u pararen.
\v 27 Baxuc caj u ts'aj ten u muc' quir in jʌsic mac a yʌn u si'pirob quire' a teno' bajeneno' winic ich yoc'ocab.
\v 28 Mʌ' u jac'ʌrex a worex quire' caj in wa'araj techex aro'. Mʌ' ja wirej, je' u c'uchur tu q'uinin tu cotor mac a quimeno' cu bin u yubic in t'ʌn quire' u pararen C'uj.
\v 29 Tu cotor mac cu bin riq'uir tu mucnaj. A mac a tu betaj tsoy cu bin cuxtar munt q'uin ich ca'anan. A mac a tu betaj c'aso' cu bin ts'abir u muc'yaj quire' ra' u bo'orir u si'pirob.
\s1 A mac a cu ya'arico' taj ti' Jesús
\p 
\v 30 Jesús caj ya'araj:
\p ―A teno' ―quij―, in bʌjiri' mʌ' c'ucha'an in wor ti' ba'. An ten bic caj u ya'araj in Tet baxuc quin bin in jʌsic a mac a yʌn u si'pirob. Taj quin bin in jʌsic mac. A teno' mʌ' in bin in jʌsej an ten bic in c'at. A teno' quin betic an ten bic u c'at in Tet a tu tuchi'tajen.
\v 31 Quire' techex ca tucriquex in bʌjiri' quin tsicbar tin junan. Rajen ca tus tucriquex mʌ' c'ucha'an a worex a wacsiquex ta worex ten.
\v 32 Yʌn ten mac cu tsicbar ti' ten. Taj a ba' cu tsicbar ti' ten.
\v 33 A techexo' ta tuchi'tajex mac quir u c'ata' ti' Juan a cu yacsic ja' caj u jo'r mac. Taj a ba' tu ya'araj techex Juan ten.
\v 34 Mʌ' ba'wir Juan quir u tsicbar ten. Quin chen aric techex aro' quir in c'asictechex soc c'ucha'an a worex a wacsiquex ta worex.
\v 35 A Juano' irej quib, cu ye'c'ac'tic a berex soc chʌca'an a berex tu ca binex. Cax tabar u q'uinin, Juan caj u camsaj techex soc a werex ten. Qui'ex a worex caj u tsec'taj techex Juan.
\v 36 A Juano', tu chen tsicbʌtajen. Chen in beyaj cu cha'ic C'uj in betic jach carem. Aro' cu yesic techex C'uj tu tuchi'tajen.
\v 37 In Tet C'uj a mac tu tuchi'tajen, raji' cu tsicbʌtic ten. A techexo' mʌ' ja wu'yʌmʌnex chichin u tsicbar, mʌ' ja wiramʌnex bicyʌra' C'uj.
\v 38 Quire' mʌ' ti' yʌn u t'ʌn ta pixamex. Rajen mʌ' ja wacsiquex ta worex ti' ten a mac tu tuchi'tajen C'uj.
\v 39 Mʌ' ja wirej, rajra' ca qui' xaquiquex u t'ʌn C'uj tu ts'iba'an quire' ca tus tucriquex baxuco' ca bin a cuxtarex munt q'uin. Chen u t'ʌn C'uj mʌ' ju ya'aric aro'. Cu tsicbar ti' ten a ts'iba'an u t'ʌn C'uj quir in ts'ic a cuxtarex munt q'uin.
\v 40 Chen a techexo' mʌ' ja c'at a wacsiquex ta wor ti' ten quir in ts'ic a cuxtarex munt q'uin.
\p 
\v 41 ’Cax mʌ' a sʌjtiquenex mʌ' jin pʌq'uiquechex.
\v 42 Quire' in werechex, mʌ' ja yajquintiquex C'uj ta pixamex.
\v 43 A techexo' mʌ' a c'at a wacsiquex ta wor ti' ten cax ti' in tar ich in Tet. Chen a mac mʌ' tuchi'ta'b ten in Tet ca sʌjtiquex.
\v 44 Mʌ' c'ucha'an a worex a wacsiquex ta worex quire' ca pachtiquex ca' u tus yirechex a rac'ob jach tsoyechex. Mʌ' ja wirej, mʌ' tan a cʌxtiquex soc chen C'uj cu yiriquechex jach tsoyechex.
\v 45 Mʌ' a chen tucriquex wa chen ten quin bin in ta'quiquex a jo'rex ʌcʌtan ti' in Tet. Quire' ca tus tucriquex a qui' cʌnantiquex tu cotor a ba' ts'ibta'b ich u t'ʌn Moisés. Ta pʌyex a si'pirex quire' mʌ' ta quibex an ten bic caj u ya'araj Moisés uch.
\v 46 Wa ta quibex a ba' caj u ts'ibtaj Moisés baxuc je' a quibiquex in t'ʌn quire' Moisés tu ts'ibtaj ten uch.
\v 47 Quire' wa mʌ' a quibiquex a ba' caj u ts'ibtaj Moisés uch, baxuc xan mʌ' ja bin a quibex a ba' quin wac techex xan ―baxuc caj ya'araj Jesús ti' u jach ts'urirob sacerdote.
\c 6
\s1 Jesús cu jansic cinco mil xib
\r (Mt. 14.13‑21; Mr. 6.30‑44; Lc. 9.10‑17)
\p 
\v 1 Pachir Jesús caj binij pichij c'ac'nab Galilea. U jer u c'aba' u c'ac'nabir Tiberias.
\v 2 Ya'ab mac tan u binob tu pach Jesús quire' tu yirob carem u beyaj. Baxuc caj yirob u jawsa'rob a mac yʌn u yajirir.
\v 3 Rajen Jesús naquij ich u jo'r chan p'uc wits yejer u camsʌwinicob Jesús caj curʌj quir u camsic ti'ob.
\v 4 Tabar u c'uchur tu q'uinin u qui'qui' janʌnob u winiquirob judío ra' u q'uinin pascua.
\v 5 Jesús caj u yiraj a pimo' tan u tarob cʌxta'bir. Rajen caj u ya'araj ti' Felipe:
\p ―Tu quic bin ic mʌnic yoch pan quir ic jansic a pimo' a cu tarob.
\p 
\v 6 Baxuc caj u ya'araj Jesús quire' cu tumtic Felipe yubej ba' cu ya'aric quire' a Jesúso' yer ba' cu bin u betej.
\v 7 Felipe caj u nuncaj ti' tan ya'aric:
\p ―Cax wa yʌn u taq'uin a mun cu jaric mac turiri' yaxq'uin, quir a mʌnic yoch pan ti' a pimo', mʌ' ju bin nup'ur cax ca'ca' xet'.
\p 
\v 8 Andrés, ra'iri' u camsʌwinic Jesús xan. Andrés, u yits'in Simón Pedro, caj ya'araj ti':
\p 
\v 9 ―Ti' yʌn chan chichan tera' yʌn ti' cinco yo'och pan beta'b ti' u pʌc'ar cebada ra' yoch u winiquirob judío. Yejer ca'tur cʌy. Je' wa ju rʌc nup'ur ti' a pimo' quire' jach pim?
\p 
\v 10 Jesús caj ya'araj ti' u camsʌwinicob:
\p ―Arex ti'ob ca' curacob ich su'uc.
\p Quire' ti' yʌn ya'ab su'uc tub yʌnob. Caj curʌjob, yʌn cinco mil xib. Mʌ' tu xacajob mun xquic yejer chichan.
\p 
\v 11 Jesús caj u chucaj pan a cincojo' caj u ya'araj ti':
\p ―Bayo' C'uj.
\p Caj ts'oqui' caj u ts'aja ti' u camsʌwinicob quir u jʌsicob ti' a pimo', a ti' cura'anob. Baxuc caj u betaj xan yejer yoch cʌy, tan u rʌc jʌsic ti'ob a mun u c'at.
\v 12 Caj nachʌjob. Jesús caj ya'araj ti' u camsʌwinicob:
\p ―Marex u xet'er tu' mʌ' ju rʌc jantob soc mʌ' u sa'atʌr.
\p 
\v 13 Rajen tu rʌc marob u xet'er. Caj u but'ob ich xac, rʌc chupij doce xac a mun yʌn samo' cinco yoch pan a beta'b ti' yoch cebada.
\v 14 A pimo' caj u yirob ba' caj u betaj Jesús quire' yerob carem u beyaj. A pimo' cu pacran aricob:
\p ―Mʌ' wa raji' jach jaj yʌjtseq'uir u t'ʌn C'uj a ara'b bin u ca' tar tera' ich yoc'ocab?
\p 
\v 15 Chen Jesús caj u najtaj a pimo' u c'at u ts'ʌricob u pach u yocar rey ten u piman. Rajen Jesús caj bin tu junan ich u jo'r p'uc wits.
\s1 Jesús cu ximbar ich yoc'o ja'
\r (Mt. 14.22‑27; Mr. 6.45‑52)
\p 
\v 16 U camsʌwinicob Jesús tan yiricob tan yac'birchʌjʌr caj bin ich chi' c'ac'nab.
\v 17 Caj ruc'ocob ich chem quir u ch'ʌcticob c'ac'nab quir u c'uchurob ich u cajar Capernaum. Jach ac'birchʌjij tan u binob ich chem. A Jesúso', mʌ' toy uruqui'.
\v 18 Caj u yʌnxchun u tar yic'ar. Jach c'am caj jach nuquij u tar u yamin xan.
\v 19 Caj nachijob tan u binob yejer chem. Yʌn cinco kilómetros caj yirob Jesús. Tan u ximbar ich yoc'o ja', tan u c'ʌs nats'ʌr ich chem caj u ch'aj sajquirob u camsʌwinicob caj yirob u tar Jesús.
\v 20 Chen Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Ten ca wiriquenex ―quij―, mʌ' a ch'iquex sajquir.
\p 
\v 21 Caj qui'jij yorob caj acsa'b Jesús ich chem. Rajen seb caj c'uchob pichij c'ac'nab tu cu binob ca'ch.
\s1 A pimo' tan u cʌxticob Jesús
\p 
\v 22 Caj sasij a pimo' a p'atob pichir c'ac'nab caj u najtob binob u camsʌwinicob tu junanob ich chem. Quire' ti' yʌn turiri' u chem ich chi' c'ac'nab ca'ch. Caj u najtob xan mʌ' binij Jesús yejer u camsʌwinicob.
\v 23 Tarob u jer chemob ti' u tar ich u cajar Tiberias ti' manob tu' jansa'b a pimo' ten u Jaj Ts'urir caj ts'oc ya'aric:
\p ―Bayo' C'uj ―quij.
\p 
\v 24 Quire' tu yirob mʌ' ti' yʌn Jesús mʌ' ti' yʌn u camsʌwinicob xan. Caj ocob ich chem. Caj binob ich u cajar Capernaum quir u cʌxta'ob Jesús.
\s1 A Jesúso' raji' irej yoch waj soc u ts'ic u cuxtar munt q'uin ti' mac
\p 
\v 25 Caj c'uchob a pimob ich pichi c'ac'nab caj u nup'ob Jesús caj u c'atob ti', tan ya'aricob:
\p ―In wʌjcamsʌyʌjirech, tu' q'uin c'uchuquech tera'?
\p 
\v 26 Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Taj quin wa'aric techex. Tarechex a cʌxtiquenex quire' ta wu'yajex najchʌjechex ti' a woch pan. Mʌ' tarechex a cʌxtiquenex quire' ta wacsajex ta wor ten a carem beyaj tin betaj.
\v 27 Mʌ' rajra' ca tucriquex a wochex quire' cu xupur aro'. Ca' a cʌxtex a wochex ti' a pixamex quire' munt q'uin ti' yʌn a pixamex. Je' in ts'ic techex a teno' a mac tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj. Quire' baxuc caj u ts'aj in beyaj in Tet C'uj.
\p 
\v 28 A pimob caj u nuncob tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Bic tabar ic betic u beyaj C'uj?
\p 
\v 29 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti'ob tan ya'aric:
\p ―Ra' u beyaj C'uj quir a wacsiquex ta worex ten quire' tu tuchi'ten C'uj.
\p 
\v 30 A pimob caj ya'arob:
\p ―Ba' carem beyaj ca wesic tenob soc c'ucha'an in worob in wacsicob tin worob ti' a t'ʌn? Ba' beyaj ca wesic tenob?
\v 31 Ic nunquir caj u jantob yoch mana a irej waj uch ich tacay ru'um. Baxuc cu ya'aric tu ts'iba'an u t'ʌn C'uj: “A tu ts'aj ti'ob yoch waj a manajo' a cu tar ich ca'anan. Baxuc tech yʌn a ts'ic tenob.”
\p 
\v 32 Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Taj quin wac techex. Mʌ' Moisés caj u ts'aja ti' a nunquirex yoch pan a manajo' ich tacay ru'um. C'ub u beyaj Moisés ten C'uj. Chen C'uj tu ts'aj ti'ob quir u janticob. A tu jantajob a nunquirex uch chen quir u cuxtar a tera' ich yoc'ocab. Chen baje'rer in Tet cu bin u ts'ic techex a wochex quir a cuxtar munt q'uin.
\v 33 A C'ujo' cu ts'ic yo'och a jach jaj cu tar ti' ca'anan. A je' ocha' quir a cuxtarex munt q'uin a mac a ti' yʌnob ich yoc'ocab.
\p 
\v 34 A pimob caj u ya'araj ti' Jesús:
\p ―In Jaj Ts'urob rajra' ca ts'ic tenob in woch panob a ca tsicbʌtic tenob baje'rer.
\p 
\v 35 Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―An ten bic cu cuxriquechex ti' a wo'och wajex. Baxuc a teno' iren waj quir a cuxtarex munt q'uin. A mac a cu tar tin wicnʌn tan yacsic tu yor ten. Aro' irej wa mʌ' u yuc'chʌjʌr baxuc irej wa mʌ' ju wi'chʌjʌr xan.
\v 36 Chen a teno' caj in wa'araj techex cax ta wirenex mʌ' a c'atex a wacsex ta worex ten.
\v 37 Tu cotor mac a cu ts'abʌr ti' ten C'uj. Je' u tar tin wicnʌn. A mac a cu tar tin wicnʌn ten qui' in wor in ts'ic ti'ob u cuxtar munt q'uin. Mʌ' biq'uin quin bin in joc'sic.
\v 38 In Tet caj u tuchi'tajen mʌ' quir in betic a ba' in c'at a teno'. A teno' taren quir in betic a ba' u c'at in Tet quire' raji' tu tuchi'ten.
\v 39 In Tet a mac a tu tuchi'ten, u c'at u yiric tu cotor mac a tu ts'ajten mʌ' u sa'tʌr mʌ' turiri'. Wa cu quimin je' in ric'sic ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin u xur t'ʌne'.
\v 40 Baxuc u c'at in Tet xan tu cotor mac a cu ya'aric: “U pararech C'uj” ti' ten. A mac a cu quibic in t'ʌn je' in taquic soc u cuxtar munt q'uin. Wa cu quimin je' in ric'sic ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin u xur t'ʌne'.
\p 
\v 41 U winiquirob judío caj u yʌnxchun u choctar yorob ti' Jesús quire' a ba' caj u yubob ya'aric quire' Jesús caj u ya'araj: “A teno' iren a woch wajex a cu tar ich ca'anan quir a cuxtarex munt q'uin.”
\v 42 U winiquirob judío caj ya'arob; tan u pacran aricob:
\p ―Mʌ' wa raji' Jesús, u parar José? Ij quiramʌn u tet yejer u nʌ'. Chen cu ya'aric ti' u tar ich ca'anan. Bic tabar aro'?
\p 
\v 43 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti'ob tan ya'aric:
\p ―Mʌ' u choctar a worex ten.
\v 44 Mʌna' mac cu bin tar tin wicnʌn quir u yacsic tu yor wa mʌ' teta'b ten C'uj a mac tu tuchi'tajen. A mac cu tar tin wicnʌn quir u yacsic tu yor wa cu quimin je' in ca' ric'sique' ca' binin c'uchuc u q'uinin cu xur t'ʌne'.
\v 45 Mʌ' ja wirej, baxuc tu ts'ibtajob yʌjtseq'uirob u t'ʌn C'uj uch, tan ya'aricob: “Tu cotor mac cu bin camsabir ten C'uj.” Baxuc caj u ya'arajob yʌjtseq'uirob u t'ʌn C'uj. Rajen tu cotor mac tu yubob a ba' caj u ya'araj Juan a mac Jesúso', quij Juan. Raji'ob camsa'b ten C'uj, rajen cu tar tin wicnʌn quir u cʌnicob in t'ʌn.
\p 
\v 46 ’Mʌna' mac yiramʌn u wich C'uj. Caj ya'araj Jesús. Chen ten tin junan caj in wiraj u wich C'uj quire' ti' in tar a teno' ―quij Jesús―.
\v 47 Taj a ba' quin wac techex ―quij Jesús―, a mac a cu yacsic tu yor tene' yʌn u cuxtar munt q'uin.
\v 48 A teno' iren a woch wajenex ―quij Jesús―, quir in ts'ic a cuxtarex munt q'uin.
\v 49 A nunquirex a ucho' caj u jantob yoch mana irej a woch panex ich tacay ru'um. Chen mʌ' ju yirob u cuxtar munt q'uin cax tu jantajob a manajo', chen quimob.
\v 50 A woch panex a quin tsicbar techex, toc tarij ti' ca'anano' soc a mac a cu jantic ti' je' u cuxtar munt q'uine'.
\v 51 A teno' taren ich ca'anan, iren a woch wajenex quir a cutarex munt q'uin. Tu cotor mac a cu jantic yoch waj a quin tsicbar ti' techex, je' u cuxtar munt q'uine'. A woch wajex a quin ts'ic techex raji' in winquirir. Je' in ts'ic ti' soc tu cotor mac cu bin u cuxtar munt q'uin.
\p 
\v 52 Rajen u winiquirob judío caj u chich arob tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Bic tabar cu bin u ts'ic to'on u winquirir quir ic chi'ic?
\p 
\v 53 Jesús caj ya'arj ti'ob:
\p ―Taj quin wa'aric techex wa mʌ' a jantiquex in winquirir a teno' iren techex mʌ' ja bin a cuxtarex munt q'uin. Wa mʌ' ja wuq'uiquex in q'uiq'uer mʌ' ja bin a cuxtarex munt q'uin.
\v 54 A mac a cu jantic in winquirir yejer in q'uiq'uer cu yuq'uic, munt q'uin cu bin cuxtar wa cu quimin. A teno' je' in ric'sic ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin u xur t'ʌne'.
\v 55 Mʌ' ja wirej, in winquirir irej a jach ochex a ca jantiquex. In q'uiq'uer xano' irej a jach uc'urex a ca wuq'uiquex. Rajen a mac a cu jantic je' u cuxtar munt q'uine'. Baxuc a mac a cu yuq'uic in q'uiq'uer je' u cuxtar munt q'uine'.
\v 56 A mac a cu jantic in winquirir baxuc cu yuq'uic in q'uiq'uer p'eri'en yejer quire' ti' yʌnen tu pixam.
\v 57 In Teto' a mac tu tuchi'tajen raji' yʌn u cuxtar munt q'uin quire' a C'ujo' toc berer uch. Rajen yʌn in cuxtar a teno' quire' in Tet C'uj. Baxuco' a mac a cu jantic in winquirir cu bin u cuxtar munt q'uin quire' ten quin ts'ic u cuxtar.
\v 58 A woch wajex a quin tsicbʌtechex ts'oc u tar ich ca'anan. Raji' mʌ' quet yejer yoch mana a tu jantob a nunquirex uch. Quire' mʌ' tu yirob u cuxtarob munt q'uini' cax tu jantob a manajo' toc rʌc quimob uch. Chen a mac cu jantic a wajo' a quin tsicbʌtechex baje'rer munt q'uin cu bin cuxtar.
\p 
\v 59 Jesús ti' tu camsajob a jera' ich u chan najir tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob judío ich u cajar Capernaum.
\s1 Jesús cu camsic bic u cuxtarob munt q'uin
\p 
\v 60 Ya'ab u q'uinin tan u tar ya'ab mac tu pach Jesús quir u cʌnicob u t'ʌn. Caj u yubob a ba' caj u ya'araj Jesús caj ya'arob:
\p ―Jach yaj ij cʌnic aro' mʌ' ij c'at ij cu'yic aro'.
\p 
\v 61 Chen Jesús tu najtaj tu yor tan u choctar yorob u camsʌwinicob. Rajen tu c'ataj ti'ob:
\p ―Cu joc'siquex wa ja worex a tin wa'araj techex?
\v 62 Ba' ca bin a wa'ariquex wa ca' bin a wirex in bin tub in wʌc'ʌs tar uch a teno' a mac tuchi'ta'ben ten C'uj?
\v 63 Quire' a pixamex je' u cuxtarex munt q'uin quire' a winquirirex mʌ' neno'ji'. Mʌ' ja wirej, in t'ʌn a tin wa'araj techex, raji' ti' a pixamex quir u cuxtarex munt q'uin.
\v 64 Ti' toj yʌnechex jun yarechex, mʌ' toy a wacsex a worex.
\p Quire' Jesús u toc er tu yʌnxchun u beyaj mac cu quibic u t'ʌn, baxuc a mac a cu bin u c'ubur Jesús.
\v 65 Caj ara'b ti'ob ten Jesús:
\p ―Rajen caj in wa'araj techex uch mʌna' mac cu tar tu yʌnen quir u cʌnic in t'ʌn wa mʌ' teta'b ten C'uj.
\p 
\v 66 Rajen ya'ab mac a cu sayʌr tu pach Jesús caj u p'ʌtob u binob tu pach Jesús caj wʌc'ʌs binob tu yatoch.
\v 67 Jesús caj u c'ataj ti' u camsʌwinicob a docejo':
\p ―Ba' ca tucriquex? Je' wa ja wʌc'ʌs binex ta watochex?
\p 
\v 68 Simón Pedro caj u nuncaj ti' Jesús tan ya'aric:
\p ―Mʌna' mac quir ic bin ic tsicbar ti' u t'ʌn C'uj. Chen a techo' yʌn a t'ʌn quir ij cuxtarex munt q'uin.
\v 69 Quire' a tenobo' tin toc wacsob tin worob tech. Quire' a techo' in werob Cristojech raji' tu ts'aj a beyaj C'uj quir a yamtiquenob quire' u pararech C'uj a cuxa'ano'.
\p 
\v 70 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti'ob tan ya'aric:
\p ―A teno' tin tetajechex doce chen ti' yʌn turiri' ich techex a mac aca'an quisin ti'.
\p 
\v 71 Jesús tan u tsicbar, ti' Judas u parar Simón Iscariote quire' raji' cu bin u c'ubic Jesús. Quire' raji' turiri' ich a doce u camsʌwinicob.
\c 7
\s1 U yits'inob Jesús mʌ' ju yacsob tu yorob ti'
\p 
\v 1 Pachir caj bin Jesús ich u ru'umin Galilea quire' mʌ' u c'at u bin ich u ru'umin Judea quire' u ts'urirob u winiquirob judío u c'at u quinsicob Jesús.
\v 2 Tabar u c'uchur tu q'uinin u qui' janʌnob u winiquirob judío ra' u q'uinin cu c'ʌxicob paser an ten bic ara'b ten C'uj uch.
\v 3 Rajen ara'b ti' Jesús ten u yits'inob:
\p ―Mʌ' a p'atʌr tera' ca' xico'on ich u ru'umin Judea. Soc a camsʌwinicob ca' bin u yirob a carem beyaj tu q'uinin u qui'qui' janʌnob u winiquirob judío soc yerob C'uj tu ts'aj a beyaj tech.
\v 4 Quire' mʌna' mac cu muc u beyaj wa ju c'at u yeticob tu cotor mac u beyaj. Joq'uen es a bʌj ti' a pimob wa ca beyaj ti' C'uj.
\p 
\v 5 Cax raji' yʌjtaquirob mʌ' ju yacsob tu yorob u yits'inob Jesús.
\v 6 Jesús caj ya'araj ti' u yits'inob:
\p ―Mʌ' c'uchuc tu q'uinin ten quir in bin ich u cajar Jerusalén quir in qui'qui'janʌn. Chen techex xenex wa ja c'at a binex.
\v 7 Rajen, mʌ' ja wirej, a mac ti' yʌn ich yoc'ocab mʌ' ju p'actiquechex a techexo', chen a teno' cu p'actiquenob quire' quin wa'aric ti'ob c'as cu beticob.
\v 8 Xenex ta qui'qui' janʌnex ich u cajar Jerusalén. Quire' a teno' mʌ' c'uchuc tu q'uinin in bin hasta cu c'uchur tu q'uinin jeroj quin bin.
\p 
\v 9 Caj ts'oc ya'aric mʌ' ju bin, ti' p'at Jesús ich Galilea yejer u camsʌwinicob.
\s1 Jesús cu bin ich u cajar Jerusalén u q'uinin cu c'ʌxicob paser quir u qui'qui' janʌnob
\p 
\v 10 Caj ts'oc u binob u yits'inob Jesús ich u cajar Jerusalén quir u qui'qui' janʌnob caj bin Jesús yejer u camsʌwinicob. Mʌ' bin yejer u rac'ob chen tu junan yejer u camsʌwinicob caj bin, quire' mʌ' u c'at u yesic u bʌj ti' a pimob.
\v 11 U ts'urirob sacerdote tan u cʌxticob Jesús u q'uinin cu qui'qui' janʌnob u winiquirob judío. Tan u c'aticob:
\p ―Tu' yʌn? ―quijob.
\p 
\v 12 Mʌ' ja wirej, a pimob rajra' cu tsicbarob ti' Jesús. Yʌn mac tan ya'aricob: “Jach tsoy a Jesúso'.” Chen yʌn u jerob cu ya'aricob: “Bic tabar jach tsoy. Quire' cu tusaric ti' mac.”
\p 
\v 13 Quire' cu sʌjticob u ts'urirob sacerdote. Rajen cu manob u muc u aricob Jesús.
\p 
\v 14 Caj c'uchij chumuc u q'uinin u qui'qui' janʌnob Jesús caj bin ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob judío caj u yʌnxchun u camsic.
\v 15 Caj jaq'uij yorob a pimob, rajen tu ya'arob:
\p ―Bic tabar ij quet winquirir caj u cʌnaj quire' mʌna' mac tu camsaj chen u ne'er u camsa'?
\p 
\v 16 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti'ob tan ya'aric:
\p ―Mʌ' ra' in t'ʌn a quin camsic techex. Raji' u t'ʌn in Tet a mac tu tuchi'ten.
\v 17 Wa mac u c'at ca' u betej a ba' C'uj u c'at. Cu bin ts'abir u najtic ich u t'ʌn C'uj tu' quin camsic wa raji' cu tar ich C'uj wa chen in bʌjiri' in t'ʌn quin camsic.
\v 18 A mac a cu camsic u bʌjiri' u t'ʌn tan u cʌxtic soc sʌjta' ten mac. A teno' tan in cʌxtic ca' a sʌjtex a mac a tu tuchi'tajen. Rajen mʌ' tan in tusariquex, taj a ba' quin wac techex.
\p 
\v 19 ’Moisés caj u tsec'taj techex uch a ba' tu toc araj C'uj uch. Chen techex mʌ' turiri' tan a quibiquex a ba' caj u ya'araj Moisés uch quire' wa ta quibajex, mʌ' ja tsicbʌtiquex a c'atex a quinsiquenex.
\p 
\v 20 A pimob caj u nuncob tan ya'aric:
\p ―Aca'an quisin tech, mac u c'at u quinsiquech?
\p 
\v 21 Jesús caj ya'araj:
\p ―A teno' tin jawsa mac turiri', u q'uinin ca jesiquex a bʌjex, raji' tu jac'saj a worex.
\v 22 Moisés caj u ts'aj u t'ʌnin quir a ts'iriquex a pararex xib tu cu wix. Mʌ' Moisés tu yʌn a'raji', chen a nunquirex, raji' tu yʌn a'raj. Rajen cax u q'uinin ca jesiquex a bʌjex ca ts'iriquex a chan pararex xib.
\v 23 Tsoy ca' quibiquex u t'ʌn Moisés tu cu ya'aric: “Ts'irej a chan pararex xib.” Cax tu q'uinin ca jesiquex a bʌjex ca' ts'iric. Rajen biquinin ca p'actiquenex ca wiric in jawsic mac u q'uinin ca jesiquex a bʌjex.
\v 24 Mʌ' tsoy wa sep ca ta'quiquex u jo'r mac. Ca' a qui' tucrex wa taj tan u betic c'as mac.
\s1 Jesús cu tsicbar tu cu tar
\p 
\v 25 A mac a ti' cʌja'anob ich u cajar Jerusalén caj ya'arob:
\p ―A je' xiba' mʌ' wa raji' tu cʌxticob u quinsej.
\v 26 Iric ti' yʌn. Mʌ' tu mucra'r tu ya'araj ich tu cotor mac. U jach ts'urirob sacerdote mʌna' ba' caj u ya'arob ti'. Jaj ix tʌco' tan u quibicob raji' Cristo a cu taro'.
\v 27 A to'onexo' ij querex tub u tar a ra xibo'. Chen ca' bin tac a Cristojo' ij cʌjtaquirex mʌna' mac yer tub u tar ―baxuc caj ya'araj a mac cʌja'anob ich u cajar Jerusalén.
\p 
\v 28 Rajen Jesús caj u c'am araj tu cu camsic ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob judío. Caj u ya'araj ti' a pimob:
\p ―Ca tucriquex a werenex. Ca tucriquex a werex tub in tar. In wʌc'ʌs bʌjiri' mʌ' taren chen a mac jach tajo', raji' tu tuchi'tajen. Chen a techexo', mʌ' a werex maqui' a tu tuchi'tajen.
\v 29 A teno' ―quij Jesús―, in wer quire' ti' in tar tub yʌni'. Quire' raji' tu tuchi'tajen.
\p 
\v 30 Rajen u c'atob u chuquicob Jesús quir u bin u mʌquicob tu cu ma'cʌr winic. Mʌ' c'ucha'an yorob u chuquejob Jesús quire' mʌ' c'uchuc tu q'uinin cu chuquicob quir u mʌquicob.
\v 31 Yʌn ya'ab mac tu yacsob tu yorob ti' quire' yerob yʌjtaquirob. Caj ya'arob:
\p ―A je' xibo' jach manan carem u beyaj caj u yesaj to'onex an ten bic cu ya'aric cu bin u betej Cristo ca' bin tac. Rajen ij querex raji' Cristo.
\s1 A fariseosjo' caj u tuchi'tajob policía quir u chuquicob Jesús
\p 
\v 32 A fariseojo' caj yubob ya'aric a mac tu yacsob tu yor ti' Jesús. Tu yubob ya'aricob a Jesúso':
\p ―Raji' Cristo a cu bin tar.
\p Rajen a fariseojo' yejer u jach ts'urirob sacerdote caj u tuchi'tajob u policía a cu beyajob ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob judío quir u chuquicob Jesús quir u mʌquicob.
\v 33 Jesús caj ya'araj ti' a pimob:
\p ―Mʌ' ya'ab u q'uinin quin p'atʌr tub yʌnechex quire' bin in ca' tub yʌn a mac a tu tuchi'tajen.
\v 34 Quire' a techexo' ca bin a cʌxtiquenex chen mʌ' ja bin a wirenexi'. Quire' a tu quin bino' mʌ' c'ucha'an a worex a tarex.
\p 
\v 35 U winiquirob judío tan u pacran tsicbarob tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Tub u wich u bin cu ya'aric mʌ' ic yʌnyʌn iric? Ti' wa cu bin ich ij quet winquirirob judío a tar yʌnob tantanxer ich u ru'umin u winiquirob griego? U tiri' cu bin u camsic u winiquirob griego.
\p 
\v 36 Caj ya'arob:
\p ―Ba' u c'at ya'aric to'onex a tu ya'araj to'onex: “Ca bin a cʌxtenex chen mʌ' ja bin a wiriquenex quire' a tu quin bino' mʌ' c'ucha'an a worex a tarex”? ―baxuc cu pacran tsicbarob u winiquirob judío.
\s1 A cu yacsic tu yor u t'ʌn C'uj rajra' cu bin joc'ar tsoy tu pixam
\p 
\v 37 U q'uinin a jach no'jo' ra' u q'uinin quir u ts'ocsic u qui'qui' janʌnob u winiquirob judío. Ra'iri' u q'uinin caj riq'uij caj ch'icrʌj Jesús caj u c'am araj ti' a pimob, tan ya'aric:
\p ―Wa mac cu yuc'chʌjʌr, arej ca' tac ten quir u yuc'ur.
\v 38 Mʌ' ja wirej, a mac a cu yacsic tu yor ten, je' u yʌn tar tu pixam an ten bic yic' ja' cu bosirancʌr a cu ts'ic u cuxtar a ricbeno' quire' baxuc cu ya'aric ich u t'ʌn C'uj ―baxuc cu tsicbar Jesús.
\p 
\v 39 Mʌ' ja wirej, cu tsicbar ti' u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj a cu bin ts'abir ti' a mac a cu yacsic tu yor ti'. U Taj'or u Pixam C'uj mʌ' taqui' quire' mʌ' toy xic Jesús ich ca'anan.
\s1 Mʌ' quet yorob u winiquirob judío
\p 
\v 40 Ti' yʌn mac tu' yʌn Jesús caj yubob ya'aric baxuc aro' caj u ya'arajob:
\p ―Aro' jach jaj yʌjtseq'uir u t'ʌn C'uj a tij cu'yajex ya'ara' yʌn u tar.
\p 
\v 41 Chen yʌn mac jujuntur tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Raji' a jera' Cristo yʌjtaquir mac tu cotor.
\p Ti' yʌn mac jujuntur tan ya'aricob:
\p ―A Cristojo', mʌ' u bin tar ich u ru'umin Galilea.
\v 42 Quire' cu ya'aric ich u t'ʌn C'uj tu' ts'iba'an: “A Cristojo' a ca' bin taco' ti' cu bin rochbir ten u nʌ' ich u cajar Belén quire' David, raji' u ch'ic sucu'un Cristo. Ti' cu bin rochbir ten u na' Cristo quire' ti' rocha'b u ch'ic sucu'un ten u na'.”
\p 
\v 43 Rajen mʌ' quet yorob a pimob ti' Jesús.
\v 44 Yʌn mac u c'atob u chuquicob quir u mʌquicob. Chen mʌna' mac tu chucajob.
\s1 U jach ts'urirob u winiquirob judío mʌ' ju yacsicob tu yorob ti' Jesús
\p 
\v 45 Caj urob a policíajo' a cu beyajob ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob judío. Caj c'uchob ti' yʌnob u jach ts'urirob sacerdote yejer a fariseojo'. Caj c'ata'b ti'ob ten u jach ts'urirob:
\p ―Biquinin mʌ' ta chuquexi'?
\p 
\v 46 Caj u nuncob a policíajo' tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Mʌna' mac cu tsicbar baxuc a tar yʌn xibo'.
\p 
\v 47 A fariseojo' caj ya'arob:
\p ―U tus a'bar techex xan?
\v 48 Mʌ' ja wirej, mʌna' u ts'urirob u winiquirob judío tu yacsaj tu yor ti'. Baxuc a tenobo' u winiquirenob fariseo, mʌ' tin wacsajob tin worob ti'.
\v 49 Chen a pimob tu yacsob tu yorob tub much'a'anob. Robob jach chichob u jo'r. Mʌ' yerob a ba' ts'iba'an ich u t'ʌn C'uj, toc rʌc satob.
\p 
\v 50 Ti' yʌn Nicodemo a cu bin tsicbar yejer Jesús uch. Ac'bir caj binij. Raji' turiri' u ts'urir u winiquirob judío. Caj u ya'arajob ti' u yet winiquirob fariseo:
\p 
\v 51 ―Mʌ' c'ucha'an ij corex ic ts'iquex u muc'yaj mac wa mʌ' toy ij cu'yex u t'ʌn wa mʌ' tij quirex ba' u si'pir yʌn ti', quire' baxuc cu ya'aric u t'ʌn Moisés.
\p 
\v 52 Robob caj u nuncajob ti' tan ya'aricob;
\p ―A techo' irech a mac a cu tar ich u ru'umin Galilea. Xaquej a wirej tu' ts'iba'an ich u t'ʌn C'uj. Mʌ' ja bin a wirej, cu ya'aric u tar turiri' yʌjtseq'uir u t'ʌn C'uj ich u ru'umin Galilea.
\s1 A xquico' a nanij cu man tu c'asir
\p 
\v 53 Jujuntur u ts'urirob u winiquirob judío caj rʌc binob tu yatoch.
\c 8
\p 
\v 1 Chen a Jesúso' yejer u camsʌwinicob caj binob ich u jo'r wits u c'aba' Olivos.
\v 2 Caj sasij caj sutnʌj Jesús caj oc ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob judío. Caj u rʌc much'quintajob u bʌj ich Jesús. Caj curʌj Jesús caj u yʌnxchun u camsic a pimob.
\v 3 Caj c'uchob yʌjcamsʌyʌjirob u t'ʌn Moisés yejer a fariseojo'. Caj tarob u purej xquic a jach irir tan u man tu c'asir. Caj c'uchob caj u purajob ʌcʌtan tu yʌn Jesús.
\v 4 Robob caj ya'arob ti' Jesús:
\p ―In wʌjcamsʌyʌjirechob, caj in wirob a je' xquica' caj in jach chucob tu cu man ich u c'asir.
\v 5 Quire' Moisés tu toc araj uch ca' ic ch'inex u jo'r a xquico' a quic jach iriquex cu man tu c'asir. Are tenob ba' ca wa'aric a techo'?
\p 
\v 6 Baxuc caj ya'arob quire' u c'atob u tumticob yor Jesús soc u pʌyicob u si'pir soc yʌn ba'wir quir u taquicob u jo'r. Jesús caj p'uxrʌj caj u ts'ibtaj ich u noy ru'um yejer u yar u c'ʌb.
\v 7 Mʌ' ju ts'ocor u c'aticob ti' caj u tajquintaj u bʌj Jesús caj ya'araj:
\p ―Arej a mac a mʌna' u si'pir tu yʌnechex, arej ti' raji' cu yʌn bat'an ch'inic u jo'r yejer tunich a ray pay same'.
\p 
\v 8 Caj ca' p'uxrʌj Jesús u ts'ibtej ich noy ru'um.
\v 9 Caj ts'oc u yubicob ba' nunca'b ten Jesús caj rʌc joc'ob tan u binob. Jujuntur caj rʌc binob quire' caj u tucurajob u si'pirob. Caj u yʌnxchun u binob a mac jach uch ch'ijic, pachir caj rʌc binob a mʌ' uch ch'ijiqui'. P'atij Jesús yejer xquic ich a pimob chen u ts'urirob u winiquirob judío binob.
\v 10 Jesús caj u tajquintaj u bʌj a mac tarob u purob a xquico' rʌc binob chen xquic ti' yʌn. Rajen Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Xquic ―quen―. A mac a tu ta'cajob a jo'r sam mʌna', rʌc bin. Mʌna' mac tu ch'inaj a jo'r quire' yʌn a si'pir ―quij Jesús.
\p 
\v 11 A xquico' caj u ya'araj:
\p ―Mʌna' mac tu ch'inaj in jo'r, Jaj Ts'urir ―quij xquic.
\p Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Baxuc a teno', mʌ' in ts'aj a muc'yaj cax yʌn a si'pir. Xen ―quij―, mʌ' a yʌnyʌn acsic a si'pir.
\s1 Jesús u sasirir ich yoc'ocab
\p 
\v 12 Jesús cu ca' camsic a pimob ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob judío. Caj u ya'araj:
\p ―A teno' a quin camsic mac a ti' yʌnob ich yoc'ocab, iren quin yerc'ac'tic mac. Tu cotor mac a cu yacsic tu yor ten, mʌ' u binob ich yac'birir. Je' u binob tu sasirir quire' quin ts'ic ti'ob u cuxtar a ric'beno'.
\p 
\v 13 A fariseojo' caj ya'arob ti' Jesús:
\p ―A wʌc'ʌs bʌjiri' ca tsec'tic tech, rajen mʌ' in quibicob. Mʌna' yʌj'irirech soc ya'aric taj a ba' ca wa'aric.
\p 
\v 14 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti'ob tan ya'aric:
\p ―Cax wa ca tucriquex in wʌc'ʌs bʌjiri' tan in tsec'tic. Taj a ba' quin wac techex. In wer tub in tar, baxuc in wer tu' quin bin. A techexo' mʌ' a werex tub in tar, mʌ' a werex tu' quin bin.
\v 15 A techexo' seb ca quibiquex wa ju jer mac yʌn u si'pir. Mʌ' a qui' tucrex. A teno' ―quij Jesús―, mʌ' in tucric ba' ti' u jer mac.
\v 16 Wa yʌn ba' quin tucric, taj a ba' quin tucric. In wʌc'ʌs bʌjiri' mʌ' in tucric quire' p'eri' quin tucric yejer in Tet, a mac tu tuchi'tajen.
\v 17 Ti' ts'iba'an ich u t'ʌn C'uj ti' techex: “Tsoy a quibiquex u t'ʌn quire' ca'tur yʌj'irirob wa quet u t'ʌnob.”
\v 18 A teno' quin tsec'tic ti' in wʌc'ʌs bʌjiri'. In Teto' a mac tu tuchi'tajen, cu tsec'tic ti' ten xan.
\p 
\v 19 Robob caj u c'atob ti' tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Tu' yʌn a Tet a ca tsicbʌtic tenob?
\p Jesús caj u nuncaj ti'ob tan ya'aric:
\p ―A techexo' mʌ' a werenexi'. Mʌ' a werex in Tet xan. Wa baxuc a werenex baxuc a werex in Tet xan.
\p 
\v 20 Jesús tan u camsic a je' t'ʌna' ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob judío tu cu but'icob u taq'uin quir u sijic ti' u beyaj C'uj. Mʌna' mac c'ucha'an yorob u chuquicob u mʌquejob quire' mʌ' c'uchuc tu q'uinin u chuquicob u mʌquejob.
\s1 “A tu' quin bin a teno' mʌ' c'ucha'an a worex a tarexi'”
\p 
\v 21 Jesús caj u ca' araj ti'ob:
\p ―Tu' quin bin a teno', ca bin a cʌxtiquenex, chen mʌ' ja bin a wiriquenex ca bin a quiminex ti' a si'pirex quire' tu' quin bin a teno' mʌ' c'ucha'an a worexi' a tarex.
\p 
\v 22 Rajen u winiquirob judío caj u pacran arob, tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Bin u ca' quins u bʌj, tin t'ʌn quire' cu ya'aric: “Tu' quin bin mʌ' c'ucha'an a worex a tarexi'”, ―baxuc cu pacran aricob.
\p 
\v 23 Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Mʌ' p'eri'o'onex, rajen mʌ' p'eri' ic tucriquex ba', quire' a teno' tar in tar ich ca'anan, quire' a techexo' toc ti' yʌnechex ich yoc'ocab.
\v 24 Rajen quin wa'aric techex: Bin a ca' quiminex ti' a si'pirex, quire' mʌ' ja wacsex ta worex ten wa ten a mac cu bin u rucsic a si'pirex. Rajen ca quiminex ti' a si'pirex.
\p 
\v 25 Robob caj u c'atob ti' Jesús tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Maquechi'?
\p Jesús caj u nuncaj ti'ob tan ya'aricob:
\p ―A teno' tin toc araj techex uch maqueni'.
\v 26 Yʌn toy ya'ab quir in wa'aric techex baxuc quir in wa'aric techex ba' si'pir yʌn techex. A teno' quin chen aric techex a ba' caj u ya'araj ten in Tet a mac tu tuchi'tajen. In Tet a mac tu tuchi'tajen, taj u t'ʌn a ti'o'.
\p 
\v 27 Quire' mʌ' ju yacsob tu yor ti' Jesús quire' raji' Cristo a tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj, rajen mʌ' ju najtob wa tan u tsicbar ti' u Tet C'uj.
\v 28 Rajen Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Ca' bin a sinenex ich cruz quire' a teno' a mac tuchi'ta'ben ten C'uj, ra'iri' u q'uinin ca' bin a najtex a wʌjtaquirenex. Ra'iri' u q'uinin xan ca' bin a wetiquex, jari' tin wa'araj techex an ten bic tu ya'araj in Tet, a mac a tu tuchi'tajen.
\v 29 In Teto' mʌ' u p'ʌten quire' rajra' quin betic a ba' u c'at ―quij Jesús.
\p 
\v 30 Ti' toy cu camsic ti'ob, ya'ab mac caj u yacsajob tu yorob ti', quire' yerob yʌjtaquirob.
\s1 A mac a tu yacsaj tu yor ti' u t'ʌn C'uj yejer a mac a mʌ' tu yacsaj tu yor
\p 
\v 31 Rajen Jesús caj ya'araj ti' u winiquirob judío a tu yacsajob tu yorob ti':
\p ―Wa ja techexo' teni' ta toc acsex ta worex a ba' tin wa'araj techex a baxuc aro' in jach camsʌwiniquechex.
\v 32 A teno' tan in camsic techex a ba' taj, a je' t'ʌna' a ba' taji' cu bin u cha'bʌr techex ti' a ca ts'urintiquex.
\p 
\v 33 U winiquirob judío caj u nuncajob ti' tan ya'aricob:
\p ―A tenobob u pararenob in nunquir Abraham, mʌ' in ts'urinticob ba'. Bic tabar ca wa'aric a siptiquenex ti' ba'.
\p 
\v 34 Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Taj a ba' quin wac techex. Tu cotor a mac a cu man tu c'asir raji' cu ts'urintic u si'pirob.
\v 35 A mac a mʌnbir ten u ts'uriro' quir u beyaj ti', raji' mʌ' rajra' cu p'atʌr tu yatoch u ts'urir quire' cu bin ca' canbir ten u ts'urir. Chen a mac a jach u parar u ts'uriro', raji' u parar munt q'uin.
\v 36 A techexo' irechex a mac a mʌnbir ten ts'ur chen a teno' a mac tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj c'ucha'an in wor in cha'iquechex soc jach jaj cha'anechex.
\v 37 Bʌ'wir ca waquex u pararechex a nunquirex Abraham quire' techex a c'atex a quinsiquenex quire' c'as ca tucriquex ta pixamex. Rajen mʌ' ju yocar in t'ʌn ta pixamex.
\v 38 A teno' tin tsec'taj an ten bic in Tet tu cha'j in wiric. A techexo' ca betiquex an ten bic a tet quisin tu toc ts'aj u t'ʌnintechex.
\p 
\v 39 Robob caj u nuncob ti' tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Ic tetex raji' ic nunquir Abraham.
\p Caj ara'b ti'ob ten Jesús:
\p ―Wa ju pararechex a nunquirex Abraham ta quibex u t'ʌn C'uj xan an ten bic a nunquirex Abraham caj u quibaj u t'ʌn C'uj uch.
\v 40 Chen baje'rer a c'at a quinsiquenex quire' caj in wa'araj techex a ba' jach taji' a tin wu'yaj ich C'uj. A nunquirex Abraham mʌ' ju betaj baxuc a'rayo'.
\p Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Ca betiquex u beyaj a tetex quisin.
\p 
\v 41 Robob caj u nuncob ti' tan ya'aricob:
\p ―A tenob mʌ' u pararenob a yʌn u si'pir ―quij ya'aric u winiquirob judío―. Jari' yʌn tenob turiri' in tetob. Raji' in Tetob C'uj ―baxuc caj ya'araj u winiquirob judío ti' Jesús.
\p 
\v 42 Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Wa ja jach tetex C'uj je' a yajquintiquenex quire' a teno' taren ich C'uj. Mʌ' in bʌjiri' taquen quire' C'uj tu tuchi'tajen.
\v 43 Mʌ' ja najtiquex in t'ʌn quire' mʌ' a c'at a najtiquex in t'ʌn.
\v 44 A techexo' a tetex quisin. Mʌ' ja wirej, ta pixamex ca betiquex a ba' u c'at a tetex. Raji' yʌjquinsir mac uch tu yʌnxchun a winico' ich yoc'ocab uch. Mʌ' u c'at a ba' jach taji' quire' mʌna' u tajir tu pixam. Wa cu tus xan, cu tus quire' a cu tuso' u tet quisin, rajen cu camsic tus.
\v 45 Quire' taj a ba' quin wac techex, rajen mʌ' a c'atex a quibiquex in t'ʌn.
\v 46 Mʌ' c'ucha'an a worex a wiriquex wa yʌn in si'pir. In t'ʌn a tin wa'araj techex taj, rajen biquinin mʌ' ja quibiquex in t'ʌn?
\v 47 A maque', raji' C'uj yʌnin cu yubic u t'ʌn C'uj. Rajen a techexo' mʌ' C'uj yʌninechex. Rajen mʌ' a c'atex a wu'yiquex u t'ʌn.
\s1 U berer ti' yʌn Cristo uch mʌ' rochac Abraham ten u nʌ'
\p 
\v 48 Caj ya'arob u winiquirob judío ti' Jesús.
\p ―Taj a ba' quic tucriquex uch. U winiquirech samaria aca'an tech c'ac'as quisin ―baxuc tan u tus pac'ʌr u pach Jesús ten u winiquirob judío.
\p 
\v 49 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti'ob, tan ya'aric;
\p ―A teno' mʌ' aca'an ten c'ac'as quisini'. A teno' quin sʌjtic in Tet chen a techexo' mʌ' ja sʌjtiquenex.
\v 50 A teno' mʌ' jin cʌxtic soc u sʌjtiquen mac quire' in Tet u c'at yiric u sʌjtiquen tu cotor mac. A mac mʌ' u sʌjtiquen ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin. Je' u ya'ara' ten C'uj: Biquinin mʌ' ja sʌjtaj Jesús uch?
\v 51 Taj a ba' quin wac techex a mac a cu quibic in t'ʌn mʌ' ju bin quimin ―quij Jesús.
\p 
\v 52 U winiquirob judío caj ya'arob:
\p ―Baje'rer ij quer aca'an quisin tech. Quire' ic nunquir Abraham quimij uch. Baxuc yʌjtseq'uirob u t'ʌn quimob uch. Chen tech ca wa'aric: “A mac a cu quibic a ba' quin wa'aric ti' mʌ' ju bin quimin.”
\v 53 Biquinin a techo' ca tucric jach no'jech a beyaj? Ic nunquir Abraham a mac quimij uch, jach no'j beyaj. Baxuc yʌjtseq'uirob u t'ʌn C'uj caj quimob jach no'j beyajob uch. Mac ca tucric jach manan no'j a beyaj, tech wa?
\p 
\v 54 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti'ob, tan ya'aric:
\p ―Wa quin cʌxtic soc u sʌjtiquen mac jot aro'. Wa quin cʌxtic soc u sʌjtiquen mac, in Tet a mac ca tucriquex a C'uj techex, raji' cu ya'aric: “Jach caremech in pararech Jesús.”
\v 55 A techexo' mʌ' a werex C'uj. Chen a teno' in wer C'uj. Wa quin wa'aric mʌ' in wer C'uj, baxuc aro' tus in ca' an ten bic techex ca tusex. Chen a teno' in jach er C'uj quin wu'yic u t'ʌn.
\v 56 A tetex a nunquirex Abraham a ca tsicbʌtiquex qui'ji yor uch quire' yuba tabar in tar. Tu quibaj je' in tare' rajen tu jach qui'quintaj yor uch.
\p 
\v 57 Rajen u winiquirob judío caj ya'arob ti' Jesús:
\p ―A techo' mʌ' c'uchuc cincuenta yaxq'uinechi'. Tu' ta wiraj ic nunquir Abraham quire' mʌ' uch ch'ijiquechi'?
\p 
\v 58 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti'ob tan ya'aric:
\p ―Taj quin wac techex. Mʌ' toy rochac Abraham ten u nʌ' uch in toc berer uch ―quij Jesús.
\p 
\v 59 Rajen u winiquirob judío caj u chucob tunich quir u ch'inicob u jo'r Jesús. Jesús caj u ta'c u bʌj ich u rac'ob. A baywo' ca' joc' tancab ti' manij chumuc tu' yʌnob, caj bin.
\c 9
\s1 A mac ch'op u wicho' caj toc rocha'b ten u nʌ' uch, jawsa'b ten Jesús
\p 
\v 1 Tu cu man Jesús, ti' tu yiraj ch'op u wich toc berer caj rocha'b ten u na'.
\v 2 U camsʌwinicob caj u c'atajob ti' Jesús tan ya'aricob:
\p ―A wʌjcamsʌyʌjirenob ―quij―. Mac u si'pir quire' toc ch'op u wich caj rocha'b ten u na'? Wa ja je' xiba' yʌn u si'pir wa ju tet yejer u na', yʌn u si'pirob?
\p 
\v 3 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti'ob tan ya'aric:
\p ―Mʌ' u bʌjiri' u si'pir, mʌ' u si'pir u tet yejer u na' xan. Toc berer ch'opir u wich caj rocha'b ten u na' soc yesa' ten C'uj jach carem beyaj ti' a je' xiba'.
\v 4 Ti' toy cuxa'anen baje'rer te' ich yoc'ocaba'. Yʌn u q'uinin quir in beyaj ti' in Tet C'uj a mac tu tuchi'tajen. Ca' bin quimiquen ts'oc in beyaj tera' ich yoc'ocab.
\v 5 Mun q'uin ti' yʌnen ich yoc'ocab, quire' a teno' tuchi'taben ten C'uj, iren quib quir in wesiquex tech u jach jajir u t'ʌn C'uj.
\p 
\v 6 Caj ts'oc ya'aric aro' Jesús caj u tubaj ich u noy ru'um caj u jach'quintaj u noy ru'um caj u ch'aj u jach'ir u ru'umin caj u jic'taj tu boxer u wich a ch'op u wicho'.
\v 7 Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Ca' xiquech ca' a ja'xtej a wich tu cuch u yacʌr ya'arir pʌcha'an u c'aba' Siloé ―u c'at ya'aric aro' tu cuch u tar ya'arir.
\p A ch'op u wicho' caj binij u ja'xtej u wich ich u cuch ya'arir Siloé caj urij chʌca'an yiric u bej.
\v 8 Rajen u yet cajarob caj yirob. Baxuc a mac tu yirob uch a ch'op u wicho' caj u pacran arob tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Mʌ' wa raji' a cu cutar u c'atej u taq'uin uche'? ―baxuc u pacran aricob.
\p 
\v 9 Yʌn mac tu ya'arob:
\p ―Raji'.
\p Yʌn u jerob tu ya'arob:
\p ―Mʌ' raji'.
\p Mʌ' ja wirej, cu c'ʌs c'ʌ'oticob. Chen u bʌjiri' tu ya'araj:
\p ―Jach jaj raji' ten ―quij―, a ch'op in wich uche'.
\p 
\v 10 Rajen robob caj u c'atob ti', tan ya'aric:
\p ―Bic tabar caj jaw u ch'opir a wich baje'rer?
\p 
\v 11 A ch'op u wich ucho' caj u nuncaj ti'ob, tan ya'aric:
\p ―A ray xibo', Jesús u c'aba', caj u jach'quintaj u noy ru'um caj u jic'taj tu boxer in wich. Caj ya'araj ten: “Ca' xiquech, quij, ich tu cu yacʌr ya'arir u c'aba' Siloé.” Rajen binen in jax tin wich. Rajen baje'rer chʌca'an in wiric in ber ―quij a ch'op u wicho'.
\p 
\v 12 Robob caj u c'atob ti' a ch'op u wich ucho'.
\p ―Tu' yʌn a mac a ta tsicbʌtaj ucho'?
\p Caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Mʌ' in wer tu' yʌni'.
\s1 A fariseojo' cu c'aticob ti' bic jawsa'b u wich
\p 
\v 13 Caj bin purbir a mac jawsa'b u wich ʌcʌtan ich a fariseojo'.
\v 14 Ra' u q'uinin cu jesicob u bʌj u winiquirob judío caj u jach'quintaj u noy ru'um Jesús caj u jawsaj a ch'op u wich ucho'.
\v 15 A fariseojo' xan caj u c'atob ti' a xibo' bic jawsa'b u wich. Raji' caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Jesús ―quij―, caj u jic'taj tu boxer in wich a tu jach'quintaj u noy ru'um. Pachir caj binen in ja'x tin wich, rajen chʌca'an in wiric in ber baje'rer.
\p 
\v 16 Rajen caj ya'arob a ti' yʌn jun yarob a fariseojo':
\p ―A xibo' a ray ca tsicbar ti' mʌ' raji' C'uj yʌnin quire' raji' mʌ' u cʌnantic u q'uinin ic jesiquex ic bʌjex.
\p Chen u jerob caj ya'arob:
\p ―Bic tabar a mac a cu betic carem beyaj a mac yʌn u si'pir?
\p Rajen mʌ' p'eri' yorob a fariseojo'.
\v 17 Rajen robob caj u ca' c'atob ti' a ch'op u wich ucho'. Tech, ba' ca wac tech ti' a mac a tu jawsaj a wich?
\p A xibo' caj u nuncaj ti'ob, tan ya'aric:
\p ―A teno' quin wa'aric raji' yʌjtseq'uir u t'ʌn C'uj ―quij.
\p 
\v 18 U winiquirob judío mʌ' u c'at u quibicob a ba' ara'b ti'ob ten a ch'op u wich ucho'. Mʌ' ju quibob u t'ʌn hasta caj tarob u na' yejer u tet a mac jawsa'b u wich.
\v 19 Caj c'uchob u tet yejer u na' caj u c'atob ti'ob:
\p ―A je'ra' a pararex toc ch'op wa ju wich caj rocha'b ten u na' uch? Baxuc ca wa'aric uch? Bic tabar baje'rer quire' chʌca'an yiric u ber?
\p 
\v 20 U tet yejer u na' caj u nuncob ti'ob tan ya'aric:
\p ―In werob a jera' quire' in pararob toc berer ti' ch'op u wich caj rocha'b ten u na' uch.
\v 21 Chen a tenobo' mʌ' in werob bic tabar caj jaw u wich. Baxuc mʌ' in werob mac tu jawsaj u wich. C'atex a wu'yej ti' quire' ch'ijij, u bʌjiri' cu yac techex tu junan.
\p 
\v 22 Baxuc caj u nuncob u tet yej u na' quire' tu ch'ajob sajquir ti' u jach ts'urirob sacerdote. Mʌ' ja wirej, u jach ts'urirob sacerdote tu ts'ajob u t'ʌnin tan ya'aricob: “Toc jumpuri' mʌ' u yʌnyʌn ocar ich u chan najir tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob judío, a mac tu yubaj ya'aric ti' u rac'ob: A Jesúso', raji' yʌjtaquiro'onex.”
\v 23 Rajen u tet yejer u na' caj ya'arob: “C'atex a wu'yex ti' quire' ch'ijij. Je' yac techex bic caj jaw u wich.”
\p 
\v 24 U jach ts'urirob sacerdote caj u wʌc'ʌs pʌyob a ch'op u wich uch, caj ya'arob ti':
\p ―Ca' a wa'arej ti' C'uj: “Bayo' C'uj tech ta jawsaj in wich.” A mac a ca tsicbar ti', a tenobo' in werob yʌn u si'pir.
\p 
\v 25 Raji' caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―A teno' mʌ' in wer wa yʌn u si'pir. In chen er baje'rer quire' chʌca'an in wiric in ber. A ucho' mʌ' chʌca'an in wiric in ber ―quij.
\p 
\v 26 Robob caj u ca' c'atob ti':
\p ―Ba' tu betaj tech? Bic tabar caj u jawsaj a wich? ―quijob.
\p 
\v 27 Raji' caj u nuncaj ti'ob tan ya'aric:
\p ―Biquinin tin toc araj techex ca'ch? Chen techex mʌ' a c'atex a quibexi'. Biquinin a c'atex a ca' u'yiquex, je' wa ja binex tu pach quir a cʌniquex u t'ʌn?
\p 
\v 28 Robob caj u yʌnxchun u p'asticob ti' tan ya'aricob ti':
\p ―A techo' ca bin tu pach quir a cʌnic u t'ʌn a mac a yʌn u si'piro'. Chen a tenobo' quin binob tu pach ic nunquir Moisés quir in cʌnicob u t'ʌn Moisés uch.
\v 29 A tenobo' in werob C'uj cu tsicbar ti' Moisés uch. A ray ca tsicba ti' mʌ' in werob tub u tari' ―quijob u winiquirob judío.
\p 
\v 30 A xibo' caj u nuncaj ti'ob, tan ya'aric:
\p ―A techexo' ca jac'siquex in wor quire' ca waquex mʌ' a werex tub u tari'. Tu jawsaj in wich mʌ' wa ca wiriquex jaw in wich.
\v 31 Ij querex a C'uj mʌ' ju yubic u t'ʌn a mac a yʌn u si'pire'. A C'ujo' cu chen u'yic u t'ʌn a mac a cu sʌjtic C'uj, a mac a tan u betic a ba' u c'at C'ujo'. Ra' cu yubic C'uj.
\v 32 Mʌ' ja wirej, caj yʌnxbeta'b yoc'ocab taquij baje'rer, mʌ' ij cu'yimʌnex mac jawsa'b u wich ch'op a ju toc berer caj rocha'b ten u nʌ' ―raji', aric a ch'op u wicho'―.
\v 33 A quin tsicbʌtic ti', wa mʌ' tarij ich C'uj, mʌ' c'ucha'an yor u betic baxuc a jera' ―quij a ch'op wich ucho'.
\p 
\v 34 Robob caj u nuncob ti' tan ya'aric:
\p ―Bic ca bin a camsic tenob? Mʌ' toy u rochech a na', uch toc yʌn a si'pir tech uch ―baxuc caj ya'arob ti'.
\p Robob caj ya'arob ti' jumpuri':
\p ―Mʌ' a yʌnyʌn ocar ich chan naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob judío.
\s1 A mac a cu tus tucric yer C'uj, u berer a mac ch'op u wichob
\p 
\v 35 Jesús caj yubaj a mac ch'op u wich ucho', toc jumpuri' toc joc'sa'b ich chan naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob judío. Rajen Jesús caj tar u tsicbar ti' a xibo', ra' jaw u wicho'. Caj u yiraj caj u c'ataj ti':
\p ―Ca wacsic wa ta wor ti' u parar C'uj a mac a yʌn tu cotor u muc' C'uj?
\p 
\v 36 A xibo' a jaw u wicho' caj u nuncaj ti' tan ya'aric:
\p ―Maqui' in Jaj Ts'urir? In c'at in wacsic tin wor ti'.
\p 
\v 37 Jesús caj u nunca ti' tan ya'aric:
\p ―A techo' ta wirajen baje'rer. Raji'en a tan u tsicbar yejerech.
\p 
\v 38 A xibo' caj u nuncaj ti', tan ya'aric:
\p ―Quin wacsic tin wor tech, Jaj Ts'urir.
\p Caj xonrʌj tu' yʌn Jesús.
\v 39 Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―A teno' taren ich yoc'ocab soc u sasichʌjʌr u wich a mac ch'op u wiche'. A mac a cu ya'aric: “Sasij in wicho'”, cu bin tar ti', irej wa ch'op u wich.
\p 
\v 40 Ti' yʌn a fariseojo' tu' yʌn Jesús caj yubob a ba' caj u ya'araj Jesús. Rajen caj u c'atob ti':
\p ―Ca tucric wa ja tenob ch'opob in wichob ―baxuc caj ya'arob.
\p 
\v 41 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti'ob, tan ya'aric:
\p ―Wa ch'op a wichex mʌna' a si'pirex techex. Quire' ca waquex: “Sasir in wichob”, rajen yʌn a si'pirex techex quire' ca waquex sasir a wichex.
\c 10
\s1 Jesús cu camsic ti' a mac a taj u yʌjcʌnanyʌjirob tʌmʌn yuc
\p 
\v 1 Jesús caj ya'araj ti' a pimob:
\p ―Taj a ba' quin wac techex. Rajen u'yex, a mac a cu tar ya'cric tʌmʌn yuc, mʌ' ju yocar tu jor u pa'te' tu jap'nin quir u ya'cric. Cu chen nacatic u pa'te'ir quir u ya'cric.
\v 2 Chen a mac raji' u jach winquirir u tʌmʌn yuc cu jach ocar tu jor u pa'te'ir tu' yʌn yʌrʌc' tʌmʌn yuc.
\v 3 A mac a cu cʌnantic u jor u pa'te'ir tu' yʌn yʌrʌc' tʌmʌn yuc cu q'ue'ic u jor u pa'te'ir soc u yocar a taj yʌjcʌnanyʌjir tʌmʌn yuc. A tʌmʌn yuco' cu c'ʌ'otic u t'ʌn u winquirir. Cu t'ʌnic u yʌrʌc' tʌmʌn yuc quire' jujuntur yʌrʌc' tʌmʌn yuc cu t'ʌnic u c'aba' soc u pʌyic ich tancab ca' joc'acob ich u pa'te'ir.
\v 4 Caj ts'oc u joc'sic tu cotor u yʌrʌc' tʌmʌn yuc cu pʌyic u berob. U yʌrʌc' tʌmʌn yuc cu sayʌrob tu pach quire' cu c'ʌ'oticob u t'ʌn, rajen cu binob tu pach.
\v 5 U tʌmʌn yuc mʌ' u sayʌrob tu pach a mac a mʌ' u yocar tu jor u pa'te'ir quire' mʌ' ra' u winquirir. Cu puts'urob u tʌmʌn yuc quire' mʌ' u c'ʌ'oticob u t'ʌn.
\p 
\v 6 Jesús caj u ya'araj a je' t'ʌna' quir u camsic ti' a mac a mucha'an ti'o'. Chen mʌ' tu najtob a ba' u c'at ya'aric.
\s1 “Quin qui' cʌnantic a mac cu yacsic tu yor teno'”
\p 
\v 7 Jesús caj ya'araj ti' a pimob:
\p ―Taj quin wa'aric techex, a teno' yʌjcʌnanyʌjiren u jor u pa'te'ir tu' yʌn yʌrʌc' tʌmʌn yuc C'uj.
\v 8 A mac a ca tucriquex yʌjcʌnanyʌjirob, robob irob a mac a cu ya'cric tʌmʌn yuc quire' u c'at u taquic ti' ten a mac a cu sayʌrob tin pach. Mʌ' ju yubicob u t'ʌn u tus ʌjcʌnanyʌjirob tʌmʌn yuc.
\v 9 A teno' ―quij Jesús―, quin cʌnantic u jor u pa'te'ir tu' yʌn yʌrʌc' tʌmʌn yuc C'uj. A mac a cu yacsic tu yor ten quire' yerob quin bin in taquej. Robob waysa'b irob yʌrʌc' tʌmʌn yuc C'uj. Cu bin cʌnanbirob ten C'uj, cu bin jach qui'quinbir yorob ten C'uj.
\p 
\v 10 ’A mac a cu tar ya'cric tʌmʌn yuc, ra' u beyaj quir u ya'cric. Baxuc quir u quinsic. Baxuc quir u ch'esic xan. Chen a teno' taren in ts'ic ti'ob u cuxtarob munt q'uin soc jach manan u qui' tar yorob.
\v 11 An ten bic a mac yʌjcʌnanyijir tʌmʌn yuc a jach tsoyo' cu qui' cʌnantic u yʌrʌc' tʌmʌn yuc cax quinsbir ti' u yʌrʌc' tʌmʌn yuc. Baxuc a teno' quin qui' cʌnantic mac a cu yacsic tu yor ten cax quinsbiren quir in taquic ti'ob.
\v 12 Chen a mac u chen c'at u cʌnantic tʌmʌn yuc ca' bin yirej u tar bʌc' chi'bir u yʌrʌc' tʌmʌn yuc cu puts'ur quire' mʌ' raji' u winquirir. Rajen chi'bir yʌrʌc' tʌmʌn yuc ten bʌc' rʌc wacche' u binob yʌrʌc' tʌmʌn yuc.
\v 13 A mac a cu chen c'at u cʌnantic tʌmʌn yuc cu puts'ur quire' mʌ' u yajquintic tʌmʌn yuc.
\v 14 An ten bic a mac yʌjcʌnanyʌjir tʌmʌn yuc a jach tsoyo'. Cu qui' cʌnantic u tʌmʌn yuc. Baxuc a teno' quin qui' cʌnantic a mac a cu yacsic tu yor ten. In wer mac tu yacsaj tu yor ten. Baxuc xan robob yerob tu yacsajob tu yor ten.
\v 15 In pacran erob in bʌjob an ten bic in Tet yeren in pacran erob in bʌjob. In Tet yeren xan, baxuc ten in wer in Tet xan. Baxuc quin c'ubic in bʌj soc in quinsa' ti' a mac a cu sayʌr tin pach.
\v 16 Yʌn mac mʌ' u winiquirob judío cu bin u yacsicob tu yorob ten xan. Bin in ca' in pʌyejob xan. Robob cu bin u yubicob in t'ʌn xan soc p'eri'ob yejerechex u winiquirechex judío chen turiri' yʌjcʌnanyʌjir, raji'en.
\p 
\v 17 ’In Teto' cu yajquintiquen quire' tin c'ubaj in bʌj soc in quinsa' ti' a mac a cu sayʌrob tin pach. Pachir in ca' riq'uir.
\v 18 Mʌna' mac c'ucha'an yor u quinsiquen. In wʌc'ʌs bʌjiri' in c'at in cha'ic in quinsa'. C'ucha'an in wor in cha'ic in quinsa'. C'ucha'an in wor in wʌc'ʌs riq'uir quire' baxuc caj u ya'araj ten in Tet. Baxuc tu ts'aj u t'ʌnin ti' in Tet xan.
\p 
\v 19 Rajen mʌ' quet yorob a pimob a ba' caj u yubob ya'aric Jesús.
\v 20 Ya'ab mac tu ya'arob:
\p ―Aca'an ti' c'ac'as quisin.
\p U jerob cu ya'aricob:
\p ―Chochoc t'ʌn u ca' quire' mʌna' yor. Biquinin ca wu'yiquex u t'ʌn?
\p 
\v 21 U jerob u winiquirob judío caj ya'arob:
\p ―Raji' mʌ' u tsicbar baxuc wa aca'an c'ac'as quisin. Mʌ' ja wirej, a mac aca'an c'ac'as quisin mʌ' c'ucha'an yor u jawsic a mac ch'op u wicho' ―baxuc ya'arob.
\s1 U winiquirob judío u c'at quinsicob Jesús
\p 
\v 22 C'uchij tu q'uinin u qui'qui' janʌnob u winiquirob judío ich u cajar Jerusalén. Ra' u q'uinin u winiquirob judío cu c'ʌ'oticob caj ts'oc u qui' tsoyquinticob carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj uch soc ti' cu wʌc'ʌs c'ujinticob C'uj.
\v 23 Ra' u q'uinin que'er tan xet'ir. Ti' yʌn Jesús ca'ch tan u man tu jap'nin carem naj tu re'ja'an naj u c'aba' Salomón.
\v 24 U winiquirob judío caj u much'quintob u bʌj caj u bʌ'cristob Jesús caj ya'arob ti':
\p ―Arej tenob ber ca' bin ts'ocac a choquintic in worob. Mʌ' a mucric, toc arej tenob wa Cristojech a tuchi'ta'bech ten C'uj.
\p 
\v 25 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti'ob tan ya'aric:
\p ―Tin toc araj techex chen mʌ' ja quibiquex. A wiramʌnex xan tin betaj carem beyajob quire' tu yamtajen in Tet C'uj. Raji' cu yesic tar in tar ich C'uj.
\v 26 A techexo' mʌ' ja quibiquex in t'ʌn quire' mʌ' ten yʌninechex baxuc caj in wa'araj techex uch.
\v 27 Quire' a mac ten yʌnin ―quij Jesús―, a cu yubicob in t'ʌn quire' in wer maqui'. Robob cu sayʌrob tin pach.
\v 28 Quin ts'ic u cuxtarob munt q'uin mʌ' ju bin satʌrob mʌ' biq'uin. Mʌna' mac c'ucha'an yor u taquic ten quire' ten yʌnin.
\v 29 In Tet C'uj caj u ts'aj ti'ob ten soc ten yʌninob. In Teto' jach manan c'ucha'an yor ti' tu cotor ba'. Mʌna' mac c'ucha'an yor u taquic ti' in Tet quire' raji' yʌninob xan.
\p 
\v 30 Jesús caj ya'araj:
\p ―A teno' yejer in Tet turiri'enob.
\p 
\v 31 Rajen u winiquirob judío tu ca' chucob tunich u c'atob u ch'inicob u jo'r Jesús.
\v 32 Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob tan ya'aric:
\p ―A techexo' a wiramʌnex ya'ab carem in beyaj caj in betaj quire' tu yamtajen in Tet. Arex ten ba' tsoyir beyaj ta wirex in betic. Rajen a c'at a ch'iniquex in jo'r.
\p 
\v 33 U winiquirob judío caj u nuncob ti' tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Mʌ' jin bin in ch'inicob a jo'r quire' tsoy a beyaj. Quin bin in ch'inicob a jo'r quire' tan a p'astic C'uj. Mʌ' ja wirej, chen xibech ca tucric C'ujech.
\p 
\v 34 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti'ob tan ya'aric:
\p ―Ti' ts'iba'an tu cu ya'aric C'uj ti' techex: “Techex, quij C'uj, ca wesiquenex ti' mac C'ujen.”
\p Aro' ara'b ti' u juez u winiquirob judío uch ten C'uj.
\v 35 Baxuc caj ara'b ti' a mac ts'ab u beyajob ten C'uj uch. Rajen mʌ' ju bin ruc'sa'bir ich u t'ʌn C'uj tu ts'iba'an.
\v 36 A techexo' u winiquirechex judío ca waquex jach tsoyo' a mac ara'b ten C'uj ca wesiquenex ti' mac C'ujen. Rajen biquinin ca wa'ariquex quin p'astic C'uj quire' tin wa'araj u pararen C'uj. Mʌ' ja wirej, tu ts'aj in beyaj C'uj, rajen taren ich yoc'ocab.
\v 37 Wa ca tucriquex, mʌ' u beyaj C'uj quin betic mʌ' a yʌn acsiquex ta worex ten.
\v 38 Wa ca wiriquex ra' u beyaj C'uj quin betic, quibex aro', cax mʌ' a quibiquex in t'ʌn. Quire' wa ca quibiquex ra' u beyaj C'uj quin betic, baxuc a werex xan turi'en yejer C'uj.
\p 
\v 39 Rajen u ca' c'atob u chuquicob Jesús chen mʌ' c'ucha'an yorob u chuquicob chen Jesús puts'ij.
\p 
\v 40 Tu ca'ten ca' bin Jesús pichir ya'arir Jordán tu cu tar ic yum, ti' p'atij tu cu yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac Juan uch.
\v 41 Ti' toy yʌn Jesús pʌchir ya'arir Jordán caj tarob ya'ab mac quir u yirirob Jesús. A pimob caj u pacran arob:
\p ―Cax Juan mʌ' tu yesaj carem beyaj chen taj a ba' caj u ya'araj Juan ti' Jesús.
\p 
\v 42 Rajen ya'ab mac tu yacsob tu yorob ti' Jesús.
\c 11
\s1 Quimij Lázaro
\p 
\v 1 Ti' yʌn mac uch tu cʌnaj u yajir. Raji' u c'aba' Lázaro, ti' u tar uch ich u cajar Betania, ra' u wa'an u ru'umin Judea. Lázaro ti' cʌja'anob ich u cajar uch yejer u yits'inob María yejer Marta.
\v 2 María, raji' a tu jayaj a qui' u boco' tu yoc Jesús caj u tisaj yejer u tsotser u jo'r ca' tijic. A mac u cʌmʌn u yajir raji' u sucu'unob Lázaro.
\v 3 Rajen u yits'inob Lázaro caj tuchi'ta'b ca' xic pʌybir Jesús tan ya'aricob ti':
\p ―Jaj Ts'urir ―quij―, a mac a jach yaj a wiric baje'rer yajij ―baxuc caj ya'arob a mac tuchi'ta'b ten María yejer Marta.
\p 
\v 4 Jesús caj yuba caj ya'araj:
\p ―A tu cʌnaj u yajir, mʌ' quir u jach quimin chen quir u sʌjta' C'uj ten tu cotor mac. Cu bin quimij soc ten xan cu sʌjtiquenob tu cotor mac quire' u pararen C'uj a tuchi'ta'ben ten C'uj.
\p 
\v 5 Jesús tu yajquintaj Marta yejer u yits'in María yejer Lázaro,
\v 6 chen p'atij Jesús u jer ca'tur u q'uinin tu' yʌni' cax tu yubaj tu cʌnaj u yajir Lázaro.
\v 7 Pachir caj ya'araj ti' u camsʌwinicob:
\p ―Jeroj cuxex ca' wʌc'ʌs xico'on ich u ru'umin Judea ―quij Jesús.
\p 
\v 8 Chen u camsʌwinicob caj ya'arob:
\p ―A wʌjcamsʌyʌjirenob ―quij―, u winiquirob judío u c'at u ch'inicob a jo'r uch. Biquinin a c'at a ca' bin ti' taro'?
\p 
\v 9 Jesús caj u ya'araj ti'ob bic yira' u beyaj C'uj. Rajen caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―A C'ujo' tu ts'aj to'onex juntur u q'uinin doce horas. Mʌ' ja wirej, a mac a cu man chunq'uine', mʌ' ju cojar yoc, quire' ti' toy chunq'uini'.
\v 10 Chen wa cu yac'birchʌjʌr c'uchij tu q'uinin cu cojar yoc quire' mʌ' sasiri'.
\p Baxuc a jera' Jesús tu cha' ic najtic mʌ' ju bin quinsbir Jesús hasta cu c'uchur tu q'uinin a tu p'isa C'uj uch. Rajen mʌna' ba' u ber ti' Jesús ten mac.
\p 
\v 11 Pachir Jesús caj u ya'araj ti' u camsʌwinicob:
\p ―A Lázarojo' a jic jach yaj tan u wenʌn. Tar quin bino' quir in wʌsic quire' wenʌn u ca' ―quij Jesús.
\p 
\v 12 U camsʌwinicob caj ya'arob ti':
\p ―Jaj Ts'urir ―quij―, wa wenʌn u ca', je' u ch'ic yore'.
\p 
\v 13 Baxuc Jesús caj u ya'ara ti'ob quire' jach quimen Lázaro chen u camsʌwinicob cu tucricob jach wenʌn u ca' tan u je'sic u bʌj. Rajen cu bin u ch'ic yor.
\v 14 Rajen Jesús mʌ' tu mucraj caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Lázaro jach quimij.
\p 
\v 15 Caj ya'araj Jesús:
\p ―Qui' in wor quire' mʌ' ti' yʌnenob tu' yʌn Lázaro, soc a wacsiquex ta wor ten. Chen cuxex ij quirej.
\p 
\v 16 Rajen Tomás caj u ya'araj ti' u yet camsʌwinicob, raji' cu ya'aricob u yet camsʌwinicob Gemelo, mʌ' ja wirej, caj rocha'b ten u na' toc ca'tur:
\p ―Cuxex ca' quimico'onex yejer Jesús. Yer je' u quinsa'r Jesús.
\s1 Quire' a teno' yʌn u cuxtar mac munt q'uin
\p 
\v 17 Caj u bin Jesús yejer u camsʌwinicob caj c'uchob cuatro u q'uinin tub but'i u baquer ich u jap'nin tunich Lázaro.
\v 18 U cajar Lázaro, raji' Betania baytʌc ich u cajar Jerusalén. Ya'aric ca'tur kilómetro chumuc u nachir.
\v 19 Ya'ab u winiquirob judío caj binob tu' yʌn Marta yejer María quir u qui'quinta' yorob soc p'eri'ob ya'cticob u sucu'unob.
\v 20 Marta caj yuba tabar u c'uchur Jesús caj binij quir u nup'ic ich bej. Chen María ti' p'atij ich naj.
\v 21 Marta caj c'uchij ich Jesús caj ya'araj:
\p ―Jaj Ts'urir ―quij―, wa ti' yʌnech uch caj u cʌnaj u yajir in sucu'un mʌ' quimij uch je' a jawsique'.
\v 22 Quire' in wer C'uj cu ts'ic tech baje'rer a ba' ca c'atic ti' ―quij Marta.
\p 
\v 23 Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―A sucu'un je' u riq'uire' tu but'ij ich jap'nin tunich ―quij Jesús.
\p 
\v 24 Marta caj u ya'araj ti':
\p ―In wer in sucu'un je' u ca' cuxtare' ca' bin xuruc t'ʌn ca' bin cuxrac tu cotor mac.
\p 
\v 25 Jesús caj u ya'araj ti':
\p ―Quire' a teno' yʌn u cuxtar mac. Quire' a teno' yʌn u ca' cuxtar mac, a maque' cu yacsic tu yor ten quire' yer yʌjtaquiren a teno' cax cu bin quimin cu bin cuxtar munt q'uin.
\v 26 Tu cotor mac a cu cuxtar munt q'uin a mac a cu yacsic tu yor ten quire' yer yʌjtaquiren a teno'. Mʌ' ju bin satʌr mʌ' biq'uin. Ta quibaj aro' ―quij Jesús.
\p 
\v 27 Marta caj u ya'ara ti':
\p ―Quin quibic Jaj Ts'urir in wer a techo' Cristojech, u pararech C'uj a mac a cu bin tar ich yoc'ocab ―quij Marta.
\s1 Jesús oc'nʌjij
\p 
\v 28 Marta caj ts'oc ya'aric aro' caj bin u pʌyej u yits'in caj u muc u araj ti':
\p ―Ij cʌjcamsʌyʌjir c'uchij caj u tuchi'tajen ca' in pʌyech.
\p 
\v 29 Caj yuba ya'aric aro' María seb caj riq'uij caj bin irbir Jesús.
\v 30 Jesús mʌ' toy c'uchuc ich u cajar ti' yʌn tub u nup'a Marta ich bej ca'ch.
\v 31 Rajen u winiquirob judío a tarob u qui'quinticob yor a ti' yʌnob ich yatoch yejer ca'ch. Caj yirob seb u joc'ar María caj sayob tu pach quire' cu tucricob ti' cu bin tu' but' u baquer u sucu'un quir u yactic.
\p 
\v 32 Caj c'uchij María tu' yʌn Jesús caj xonrʌj tu' yʌn Jesús tan ya'aric ti':
\p ―Jaj Ts'urir ―quij―, wa ti' yʌnech uch caj u cʌnaj u yajir in sucu'un mʌ' quimij uch je' a jawsique' ―quij María.
\p 
\v 33 Jesús caj u yiraj yoc'ar María baxuc u winiquirob judío a sayob tu pach María yaj yubaj tu yor quire' mʌ' u c'at yiric u quimin mac.
\v 34 Jesús caj u c'ataj ti'ob:
\p ―Tub a but'ex u baquer Lázaro?
\p Caj ya'arob:
\p ―Jaj Ts'urir, cojen irej ―quij.
\p 
\v 35 Jesús caj oc'nʌjij.
\v 36 A mac a ti' yʌnob caj u pacran arob:
\p ―Iric, cu yajquintic Lázaro.
\p 
\v 37 Ti' yʌn mac caj u ya'arob:
\p ―Aro' raji' a tu jawsaj u wich a ch'opo' uch. Mʌ' wa raji' c'ucha'an yor yamta'bir Lázaro soc mʌ' u quimij?
\s1 Ric'sa'b Lázaro ten Jesús quir u cuxtar
\p 
\v 38 Jesús caj c'uchij tu' but'a'an u baquer Lázaro yʌn u jap'nin tunich caj u tucraj tu yor quire' mʌ' u c'at yiric quimin mac. Tu' but'ij yʌn u mac u jor.
\v 39 Jesús caj ya'araj:
\p ―Ruc'sex ―quij―, u mac u jor tunich.
\p Marta, a yits'in ixba Lázaro caj u ya'araj ti':
\p ―Jaj Ts'urir ―quij―, tu'jij tin t'ʌn quire' toc yʌn cuatro q'uin caj but'ij.
\p 
\v 40 Jesús caj u ya'araj ti':
\p ―Mʌ' wa tin wa'araj tech wa ca wacsic ta wor ca bin a wirej jach manan u muc' C'uj? ―quij Jesús.
\p 
\v 41 Caj u ruc'sob u tunichir u mac u jor tu' but'a'an u baquer Lázaro. Jesús caj u pʌctaj ich ca'anan caj u ya'araj:
\p ―In Tet C'uj ―quij―, quin wa'aric tech: “Bayo'” quire' rajra' ca wu'yic in t'ʌn.
\v 42 In wer rajra' ca wu'yic in t'ʌn. Baxuc quin wac ti' tech quire' ti' yʌn mac tera' soc yubic ba' caj in wa'araj tech soc yacsicob tu yorob tech ta tuchi'tajen.
\p 
\v 43 Caj ts'oc ya'aric aro' Jesús caj u c'am t'ʌnaj:
\p ―Lázaro ―quen―, joq'uen ti' taro' ―quij Jesús.
\p 
\v 44 A quimeno' ca' joq'uij toc sʌsʌ c'ʌxa'an u c'ʌb yejer noc', baxuc u yoc xan. Baxuc u wich tapa'an yejer panyu. Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob a mac ti' yʌnob:
\p ―Jitex u noc' soc u bin ―quij Jesús.
\s1 Cu tucricob bic tabar cu bin u chuquicob Jesús
\r (Mt. 26.1‑5; Mr. 14.1‑2; Lc. 22.1‑2)
\p 
\v 45 Rajen ya'ab u winiquirob judío a ti' yʌnob yejer María tu yacsob tu yorob ti' Jesús quire' yerob yʌjtaquirob quire' tu yirob Jesús u ric'sic Lázaro.
\v 46 A mac mʌ' tu yacsajob tu yorob quire' mʌ' u c'at yiricob ba' cu betic Jesús. Rajen caj binob ich a fariseojo' caj u tsicbʌtajob a ba' caj u betaj Jesús.
\v 47 Rajen u ts'urirob sacerdote yejer a fariseojo' caj u much'quintajob u bʌj u yet ts'urirob u winiquirob judío, caj ya'arob:
\p ―Ba' quic bin ic betejex ti' a xibo' a tar yʌno' quire' tan u yesic carem u beyajob?
\v 48 Quire' wa quic aric: “Tsire'ej”, tu cotor mac cu bin u yacsicob tu yorob ti' quire' yerob yʌjtaquirob. A baywo' cu bin acsa'bir ten a pimob quir ic ts'urintiquex, rajen u rey ich u cajar Roma cu bin u ts'ictar yejero'onex. Cu bin tuchi'tic a soldadojo' ca' tacob u quinsico'onex ca' tacob u rʌc joc'sico'onex.
\p 
\v 49 Chen turiri' u yet ts'urirob u c'aba' Caifás, raji' a je' yaxq'uina' c'uchij tu q'uinin u yocar u jer u jach ts'urir sacerdote, raji' Caifás. Raji' caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Mʌna' ba' a werex a techexo'.
\v 50 Mʌ' wa ca najtiquex wa tsoy cu quimin turiri' mac ti' tu cotoro'onex soc tu cotor mac mʌ' u bin quinsbir ten u winiquirob romano.
\p 
\v 51 A Caifáso' mʌ' u bʌjiri' tu ya'araj a jera' quire' raji' u jach ts'urir sacerdote quire' c'uchij tu q'uinin u yocar u jer u jach ts'urir sacerdote.
\v 52 Mʌ' chen ti' to'onex, quij Caifás, cu bin quinsbir Jesús. Cu bin quinsbir u parar C'uj ti' tu cotor a mac C'uj yʌnin a ti' yʌnob ich yoc'ocab soc u p'eri'quintico'onex a mac a C'uj yʌnino'.
\v 53 Rajen u ts'urirob sacerdote seb caj u tucrajob u c'at u quinsicob Jesús.
\p 
\v 54 Rajen Jesús mʌ' ju yes u bʌj ti' u winiquirob judío. Tu junan caj binij yejer u camsʌwinicob ich u ru'umin Judea, caj bin ich tʌcay ru'um. Caj c'uchij ich u cajar Efraín. Ti' p'atij yejer u camsʌwinicob.
\p 
\v 55 Tabar u c'uchur tu q'uinin u qui'qui' janʌnob u winiquirob judío. Ra' u q'uinin pascua, ra' u q'uinin cu c'ʌ'oticob tu potmasta'b ten yʌjmasirob u t'ʌn C'uj uch soc mʌ' u quimin u parar a yʌn rocha'b ten u na'. Ya'ab winiquirob caj rʌc binob ich u cajar Jerusalén cax mʌ' c'uchuc tu q'uinin pascua soc u nup'sic a ba' cu ya'aric ich u t'ʌn Moisés soc tsoy yiricob C'uj.
\v 56-57 Caj c'uchob u winiquirob judío ich u cajar Jerusalén. Caj yubob ya'aricob a ba' ara'b ti'ob ten u jach ts'urirob sacerdote yejer a fariseojo': “Wa mac cu yiric tu' yʌn Jesús ca' tac ya'arej tu' tu yiraj Jesús soc u bin chucbirob quir u ma'cʌr.” Rajen tan u manob cʌxta'bir Jesús. Tu cotor mac ti' yʌn ich carem naj tan u pacran c'aticob tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Ba' ca tucric je' wa ju tar Jesús ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin u qui'qui' janʌn? ―baxuc tan u pacran tsicbarob ti' Jesús.
\c 12
\s1 A xquico' cu jic'tic ts'ac tu yoc Jesús
\r (Mt. 26.6‑13; Mr. 14.3‑9)
\p 
\v 1 Yʌn seis u q'uinin quir u c'uchur tu q'uinin pascua. Caj binob Jesús yejer u camsʌwinicob ich u cajar Betania tu cʌja'an Lázaro a tu ric'saj Jesús tu quimirir.
\v 2 Marta caj u pʌyaj Jesús yejer u camsʌwinicob quir u qui' janʌnob. Ti' yʌn Lázaro yejer u jer macob tan u janʌnob yejer ich u pojche'ob. Marta cu tar purbir yoch ti'ob.
\v 3 María, u yits'in Marta, tu ch'aj tu' yʌn Jesús chumuc kilo a qui' u boque' u c'aba' nardo. Jach co'oj a nardojo' caj u rʌc jic'taj tu yoc Jesús, María caj u tisaj yejer u wʌc'ʌs tsotser u jo'r. Tu cotor u japnin yatoch tu rʌc bac'aj u boc nardo.
\v 4 Ti' yʌn Judas Iscariote u yet janʌn Jesús, raji' u parar Simón Iscariote. Raji' turiri' ich u camsʌwinicob Jesús chen raji', Judas, cu wʌc'ʌs bin u c'ubic Jesús ca' quinsac. Raji' caj ya'araj:
\p 
\v 5 ―Wa tu canaj a je' qui' u boc a tu jic'taj tu yoc Jesús, a tu chen jaraj u taq'uin ca'ch tres cientos denarios ―u c'at ya'aric u taq'uin a mac a cu jaric turiri' yaxq'uin tu cu beyaj―. Jach tsoy ca' u jʌsej ti' a mac otsire' ―baxuc caj ya'araj Judas.
\p 
\v 6 Judas mʌ' u jach tucric a mac otsir tu chen araj aro' quire' Judas cu cʌnantic u taq'uin u yet camsʌwinicob Jesús. Mʌ' ja wirej, a Judaso', cu chʌc a'cric taq'uin tu cu ts'abʌr u cʌnantej ti' ten u yet camsʌwinicob Jesús.
\v 7 Jesús caj ya'araj ti' Judas:
\p ―Tsire'ej mʌ' a wa'aric aro' quire' tu cʌnantaj a jeroj soc u c'uchur tu q'uinin in quimin.
\v 8 Rajra' ti' yʌn otsir tu' yʌnechex. Chen a teno' mʌ' rajra' ti' yʌnen tu' yʌnechex ―quij Jesús.
\s1 U ts'urirob sacerdote cu tucricob u quinsej Jesús
\p 
\v 9 Jach pim a winiquirob judío a tu much'quintajob u bʌj ich u cajar Jerusalén caj yubob c'uchij Jesús yejer u camsʌwinicob ich u cajar Betania. Rajen binob u yirejob Jesús. Mʌ' chen c'uchob quir u yiricob Jesús quir yiric Lázaro xan a mac ric'sa'b tu' quimen ten Jesús.
\v 10-11 Caj tarob ich u cajar Betania mʌ' toy u yacsajob tu yorob ti' Jesús. Caj joc'ob tu cajar Betania tu yacsob tu yorob ti' Jesús quire' yerob yʌjtaquirob quire' tu yirob Lázaro raji' ric'sa'b ten Jesús tu' quimen. Rajen u jach ts'urirob sacerdote tu p'eri'quintob yorob u tucricob u quinsicob Lázaro xan.
\s1 Jesús cʌpa'an ich u pach chan tsimin tan u yocar ich u cajar Jerusalén
\r (Mt. 21.1‑11; Mr. 11.1‑11; Lc. 19.28‑40)
\p 
\v 12 Caj sasij a pimob tan u much'quinticob u bʌj ich u cajar Jerusalén quire' c'uchij tu q'uinin u qui'qui' janʌnob u winiquirob judío. Caj yubob tan u c'uchur Jesús ich u cajar Jerusalén.
\v 13 Rajen caj joc'ob u janch'ʌtejob u re' pajo' caj joc'ob tancab ich u cajar Jerusalén. U mʌchmʌnob u re' pajo' quir u binob u nup'icob Jesús ich bej. C'am tan u t'ʌnob tu cu tarob ich bej. Caj ya'arob:
\p ―Je' cu tar ij cʌjtaquirex jach qui' ij corex quire' baje'rer tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj. Ca' qui'ac ij corex. Raji' cu bin yocar quir ic reyintiquex a tenobo' u pararenob ic nunquirex Israel. Ca' ij carex ti' C'uj: “Jach caremech C'uj.”
\p 
\v 14 Ti' yʌn chan tsimin taro'. Jesús caj naquij quir u cʌptar tu pach an ten bic ts'iba'an ich u t'ʌn C'uj uch tan ya'aric:
\q1 
\v 15 A techexo', a xquico' a mac cʌja'an ich u cajar Jerusalén, u jer u c'aba' Sión, mʌ' a ch'iquex sajaquir, je' u tar a mac ca' bin a reyintiquex. Je' u tar cʌpʌcbar tu pach chan tsimin.
\m Baxuc cu ya'ara' ti' Jesús uch.
\p 
\v 16 U camsʌwinicob Jesús, mʌ' ju najtobi' caj yirob Jesús u captar tu pach chan tsimin quir u sʌjta' ten tu cotor mac. Caj wʌc'ʌs binij Jesús ich ca'anan caj c'aj ti'ob a ba' ts'ibta'b ti' Jesús uch.
\p 
\v 17 A pimob a tarob ich bej quir u nup'icob Jesús quire' tu yubob ya'aric: “Raji' tu t'ʌnaj ca' joc'ac Lázaro tu but' u baquer.
\v 18 Raji' tu ric'saj Lázaro tu' quimen.”
\v 19 Rajen a fariseojo' caj u pacran arob:
\p ―Iriquex mʌ' c'ucha'an ij corex ti' quire' tu cotor mac tan u binob tu pach quir u cʌnicob u t'ʌn ―baxuc caj u pacran arob.
\s1 A mac a cu t'ʌn griego u c'at u tsicbarob yejer Jesús
\p 
\v 20 Ti' yʌnob u winiquirob griego a rajra' cu tarob cu c'uchur tu q'uinin u qui'qui' janʌnob u winiquirob judío quir u c'ujinticob C'uj, irob u winiquirob judío. Caj tarob u sijejob ba' ti' C'uj xan.
\v 21 Robob caj tarob u tsicbarob yejer Felipe. Raji' u camsʌwinic Jesús a cu tar tu cajar Betsaida a ti' yʌn tu ru'umin Galilea, caj u chich arajob ti':
\p ―Jach ts'urir, quen, in c'atob in wiricob Jesús ―quij.
\p 
\v 22 Rajen Felipe caj bin ich Andrés caj ya'araj ti'. Rajen ca'turo' u camsʌwinicob Jesús caj binob ich Jesús caj ya'arob ti'.
\v 23 Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―C'uchij tin q'uin a teno' a tu tuchi'ten C'uj soc u caremquintiquen C'uj, a teno' irenechex.
\v 24 Taj a ba' quin wac techex, u yijir u wich trigo cu ts'abʌr u wich wa cu pʌc'ʌr ich ru'um. Wa pʌc'a'an cu nets'ajic u wich trigo. Wa mʌ' pʌc'a'an chen tu junan yʌn. Baxuc ten ―quij Jesús―, wa quin quimin, ya'ab mac cu bin u yacsicob tu yorob ten quir u tar tin pach ―quij Jesús―.
\v 25 Baxuc yejer techex. A mac mʌ' u c'at u c'ubic u bʌj ti' ten soc u quinsa' irej ten, cu bin ts'abir u muc'yaj munt q'uin. Chen a mac u c'at u c'ubic u bʌj ti' ten soc u quinsa', raji' cu bin u cuxtar munt q'uin.
\v 26 Tu cotor mac u c'at u yamtiquen ca' tacob tin pach. Baxuco' cu bin c'uchur ich ca'anan tu' yʌnen quire' a mac a tu yamtajen cu bin qui' acsa'bir ten C'uj.
\s1 Yʌn in quinsa'
\p 
\v 27 Jesús caj ya'araj:
\p ―Yaj in wu'yic tin wor baje'rer. Mʌ' c'ucha'an in wor in wac ti' in Tet C'uj: “Yʌmtej ten, Tet”, quire' taren ich yoc'ocab quir in muc'yaj a ba' cu bin tar ten. Rajen taren quir in muc'yaj.
\p 
\v 28 Jesús caj u t'ʌnaj C'uj tan ya'aric:
\p ―Baxuc in c'at ca' u sʌj techob C'uj.
\p Jeroj tune', caj yubob u t'ʌn ca'anan. C'uj caj u nuncaj, ti' u tar u t'ʌn ich ca'anan:
\p ―Tan in toc sʌjta're', je' in ca' sʌjta're' ―quij C'uj―, ra' u q'uinin ca' bin quinsaquech.
\p 
\v 29 A mac a ti' yʌnob a tan u ch'ictarob caj yubob u t'ʌn c'am a tar u tar ich ca'anan. Robob caj u pacran arajob tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Ba' pecnʌjij sam, a ti' ij cu'yajex?
\p U jer caj ya'arob:
\p ―Yʌjmasir u t'ʌn C'uj, raji' t'ʌnʌjij. Raji' tin wu'yajob, tin t'ʌn.
\p 
\v 30 Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―In Tet, C'uj, caj u t'ʌnajen, mʌ' chen jari' ti' ten, ti' techex xan ca' a wu'yex soc a werex in Tet, C'uj, cu yubic in t'ʌn.
\v 31 Baje'rer ―quij Jesús―, c'uchij tu q'uinin cu bin jʌsbir mac a yʌn u si'pire' quire' mʌ' biq'uin u c'at yacsicob tu yor ten. Baje'rer ―quij Jesús―, c'uchij tu q'uinin xan cu bin ruc'sa'bir u beyaj a quisino' quire' raji' cu ts'urinticob ich yoc'ocab.
\v 32 Quire' a teno' quin bin quinsbir ich cruz. A baywo' tu cotor mac cu bin tar tu' yʌnen quir u yacsicob tu yorob ten cax u winiquirob judío cax mʌ' u winiquirob judío.
\p 
\v 33 Baxuco' ca' u chaj u najticob ti' cu bin quimin ich cruz.
\v 34 Rajen a pimob caj u nuncob tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Tij cu'yajex a ba' ts'iba'an ich u t'ʌn C'uj ti' a Cristojo' cu ya'aric: “Munt q'uin cu bin u cuxtar a Cristojo'.” Wa Cristojech biquinin ca wa'aric: “Bin in ca' quinsa' ich cruz?” A techo' ca wa'aric: “Iren techex”, quire' baxuc ca wa'aric.
\p 
\v 35 Jesús caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Irej a mac a cu ximbar ich bej, cu jach p'isic u bʌj soc mʌ' u yac'birchʌjʌr tu bej wa tabar u bin q'uin. Quire' wa cu yac'birchʌjʌr mʌ' yer tu cu bin. Aro' baxuc ten, tabar in bin, a mac cu camsiquechex. Rajen toc acsex ta wor ten baje'rer. Ti' toy yʌn u q'uinin quir a wacsiquex ta worex soc a bin tacbirex munt q'uin.
\v 36 Ti' toj yʌnen tu' yʌnechex, toc acsex ta worex ten. Quire' a werex a wʌjtaquirenex a teno' soc a werex jach jaj u pararintechex C'uj. Caj ts'oc ya'aric aro' caj binij Jesús. Mʌ' u ca' u tsicbar ti'ob.
\s1 Ya'ab u winiquirob judío mʌ' c'ucha'an yorobob yacsicob tu yor ti Jesús
\p 
\v 37 Cax ya'ab tu yesaj carem beyaj Jesús ti'ob, mʌ' tu yacsob tu yorob ti'.
\v 38 Baxuc caj u nup'saj a ba' ara'b ten yʌjtseq'uir u t'ʌn C'uj Isaías uch. Quire' Isaías tu ts'ibtaj uch:
\q1 Jaj Ts'urir, quij Isaías, a mac a tin tsec'taj a t'ʌn ti' uch, mʌ' tu yacsob tu yorob ti'. Cax ta yamtaj ti'ob, mʌ' tu sʌjtech Jaj Ts'urir, quij Isaías. A techo' yʌn tu cotor a muc'.
\p 
\v 39 Rajen mʌ' c'ucha'an yor u winiquirob judío u yacsicob tu yor ti'. Tu ca' ten Isaías tu ts'ibtaj uch tan ya'aric:
\q1 
\v 40 Ac'birquinta'b u wich ten C'uj u winiquirob judío, bayiri' caj chichquinta'b u jo'r soc mʌ' u yiricob ba' soc mʌ' u najtic ba' xan, soc quir u c'axicob yorob, soc u to'carob ten C'uj.
\m 
\v 41 Baxuc caj ya'araj Isaías uch quire' u c'at ca' ij quirex Cristo, raji' yʌn tu cotor u muc'. Rajen ya'araj aro'.
\p 
\v 42 Cax ya'ab u winiquirob judío mʌ' ju yacsob tu yorob ti' Jesús. Chʌc yʌn u ts'urirob u winiquirob judío tu yacsajob tu yorob ti' Jesús. Tu muc u acsajob tu yorob quire' cu sʌjticob a fariseo cu bin joc'sabirob ich carem naj soc mʌ' u yʌnyʌn tar.
\v 43 Mʌ' ja wirej, cu tucricob soc tsoy irir ten u rac'ob chen mʌ' u tucricob soc tsoy irirob ten C'uj, rajen mʌ' tu toc arob ti' u rac'ob wa tu yacsob tu yorob.
\s1 A mac mʌ' u yacsicob tu yorob ti' Jesús cu bin ts'abir u muc'yajob ten C'uj
\p 
\v 44 Jesús caj u c'am araj ti' a pimo' tan ya'aric:
\p ―Tu cotor mac a cu yacsicob tu yorob ti' in t'ʌn, mʌ' chen ten cu yacsic tu yor ti' in t'ʌn. Baxuc cu yacsicob tu yor ti' u t'ʌn in Tet C'uj a mac tu tuchi'tajen.
\v 45 Tu cotor mac u yirmʌnen baxuc xan yirmʌn in Tet, a mac tu tuchi'tajen.
\v 46 A teno' ―quij Jesús―, iren quib quir in yerc'ac'tic techex a mac ti' yʌn ich yoc'ocab. Tu cotor mac a cu yacsicob tu yorob ten mʌ' u mʌn tu yac'birirob quire' yerob C'uj.
\v 47 A mac cu yubicob in t'ʌn wa mʌ' ju yacsic tu yor ti' in t'ʌn mʌ' taren quir in taquic u jo'r mac baje'rer. Quire' mʌ' taren quir in taquic u jo'r mac quire' taren quir in taquic mac.
\v 48 A maque' a mʌ' u sʌjtiquen a mʌ' ju yacsic tu yor ti' in t'ʌn ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin u xur t'ʌn cu bin ts'abir u muc'yaj in t'ʌn a tin wa'araj ti'. Raji' cu bin u ta'quic u jo'r quire' mʌ' tu quibaj in t'ʌn. Rajen cu bin ts'abir u muc'yaj quire' mʌ' tu quibaj in t'ʌn ―quij―.
\v 49 A teno' mʌ' tin chen araj techex in bʌjiri' in t'ʌn. In Tet C'uj a mac tu tuchi'tajen tu ya'araj ba' yʌn in wac techex. Baxuc a ba' yʌn in camsiquechex xan.
\v 50 In wer a ba' caj u ya'araj ten in Tet, ra' quin tsec'tic techex soc yʌn techex a cuxtarex munt q'uin. Ra'iri'e' a tu ya'araj ten in Tet, quin wac techex, quet bayiri' quin wac techex.
\c 13
\s1 Jesús cu p'o'ic u yoc u camsʌwinicob
\p 
\v 1 Tabar u c'uchur tu q'uinin u qui'qui' janʌnob u winiquirob judío u q'uinin pascua. Jesús yer c'uchij tu q'uinin ti' cu wʌc'ʌs bin ich u Tet ca'anan. Jesús caj u yajquintaj a mac ts'a'b ti' ten u Tet C'uj. Jach manan caj u yajquintaj a ts'a'b ten u Tet.
\v 2-4 A quisino' toc aca'an ti' Judas Iscariote. U tet Judas, Simón u c'aba'. Rajen u c'at u c'ubic Jesús soc u chucur. Jesús yer ts'a'b ti' u beyaj ten u Tet C'uj quir u cʌnantic tu cotor ba'. An ten bic caj tuchi'ta'b ich yoc'ocab yer xan je' u ca' bin ich ca'anan ich u Tet C'uj. Ti' toy cu janʌnob oq'uin tu q'uinin pascua. Cax Jesús tarij ich C'uj caj riq'uij caj u pitaj u ca' yarir u noc' caj u ch'aj u noc' tu cu tisic ba' caj u wit'c'ʌxtaj tu nʌc', irej c'urew a nanij cu p'o'ic yoc a mac acsa'b ich naj.
\v 5 Jesús caj u pe'aj ya'arir ich palancan quir u p'o'ic yocob u camsʌwinicob a cura'anob tu janʌnob. Caj u tisaj u yocob yejer a noc'o' a tu wit'c'ʌxtaj tu nʌc'.
\p 
\v 6 Jesús caj c'uchij ich Simón Pedro quir u p'o'ic u yocob caj ya'araj:
\p ―Jaj Ts'urir, mʌ' jin najtic. Biquinin ca p'o'ic in woc? ―quij.
\p 
\v 7 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti', tan ya'aric:
\p ―A ba' quin betic baje'rer mʌ' ja najtic chen pachir ca bin a najtic.
\p 
\v 8 Pedro caj ya'araj:
\p ―Mʌ' in cha'ic a p'o'ic in woc, mʌ' biq'uin.
\p Jesús caj u nuncaj ti', tan ya'aric:
\p ―Wa mʌ' jin p'o'ic a woc, mʌ' ten yʌninechi'.
\p 
\v 9 Simón Pedro caj ya'araj:
\p ―Jaj Ts'urir, quen, mʌ' chen in woc ca p'o'ic, p'o'ej in c'ʌb xan yejer in jo'r.
\p 
\v 10 Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―A mac ts'oc u yichir mʌ' ba'wir cu p'obar tu cotor chen u yoc cu p'obar chen ti' u yoc. Baxuco' toc p'o'a'anechex. Mʌ' ja wirej, toc ruc'sa'an a si'pirex chen ti' yʌn turiri' tu yʌnechex mʌ' ruc'sa'an u si'piri'.
\p 
\v 11 Quire' Jesús yer Judas cu bin c'ubic, rajen tu ya'araj: “Turiri' tu' yʌnechex mʌ' ruc'sa'an u si'piri'.”
\p 
\v 12 Caj ts'oc u p'o'ic yoc u camsʌwinic, Jesús tu ca' buquintaj u ca'yarir u noc'. Caj wʌc'ʌs cura tu po'che'ir u janʌn caj u c'ataj ti'ob:
\p ―A wer wa biquinin caj in p'o'aj a woquex?
\v 13 Quire' techex ca t'ʌniquenex in wʌjcamsayʌjirechex, baxuc ca t'ʌniquenex Jaj Ts'urir. Tsoy ca t'ʌniquenex quire' taj ten tin camsiquechex quire' taj a Jaj Ts'urirenex xan.
\v 14 A teno' a Jaj Ts'urirenex, baxuc a yʌjcamsʌyʌjirenechex tan in p'o'ic a woquex. Baxuc techex soc mʌ' a tucriquex jach no'jechex, ca' a yamtex a wet acsa'orirex.
\v 15 A techexo' ta wirex ba' tin betaj, baxuc techex, rajra' ca' a betex, an ten bic ten tin betaj.
\v 16 Taj a ba' quin wa'aric techex, mʌ' tsoy wa ju c'urew cu tucric jach neno'j u beyaj ―quij Jesús―, rajen mʌ' u bin u betic an ten bic u jach ts'urir. Mʌ' tsoy wa mac tuchi'ta'b cu tucric jach neno'j u beyaj. Rajen bin u betic an ten bic a mac tuchi'tej.
\v 17 Wa ca najtiquex a je' quin camsiquechex ca bin a cʌniquenex. Rajen cu bin u qui' tar a worex.
\p 
\v 18 ’Mʌ' tan in tsicbar ti' tu cotorechex. In wer mac tin tetajechex quir in camsiquechex. Chen ti' yʌn turiri' ich techex a mac tin tetaj, aro' mʌ' quir u yamtiquen. A teno' tin chen tetaj quir in nup'sic a ba' ts'iba'an ich u t'ʌn C'uj tu cu ya'aric ich u t'ʌn C'uj uch: “A mac p'eri' in janʌn yejeren a mac in wet man. Raji' cu bin u c'ubiquen.” Ra' cu tsicbar ti' ten.
\v 19 Mʌ' toy c'uchuc tu q'uinin u c'ubiqueni' quin toc aric techex soc a najtiquex soc ca' bin jach c'uchuc tu q'uinin u c'ubiquen ca' bin a qui' acsex ta worex ten. Quire' a werex yʌjtaquirenechex.
\v 20 A mac a cu yacsic a mac tin tuchi'taj, irej wa cu yacsiquen. A mac a cu yacsiquen, irej wa cu yacsic a mac a tu tuchi'tajene'.
\s1 Jesús cu ya'aric Judas cu bin u c'ubic
\r (Mt. 26.20‑25; Mr. 14.17‑21; Lc. 22.21‑23)
\p 
\v 21 Caj ts'oc ya'aric aro' Jesús yaj cu yubic caj ya'araj ti' u camsʌwinicob:
\p ―Taj a ba' quin wac techex, turiri' ich techex cu bin u c'ubiquen.
\p 
\v 22 Rajen u camsʌwinicob caj u yʌnxchun u pacran pʌcticob u bʌj quire' mʌ' yerob mac tan u tsicbari' ti'.
\v 23 Ti' yʌnen, quij Juan, raji' Jesús cu jach yajquintic jach bʌytʌc cura'an janʌn yejer Jesús.
\v 24 Simón Pedro caj yesaj ti' Juan ca' u c'atej ti' Jesús wa mac tan u tsicbar ti'.
\v 25 Ti' yʌn Juan bʌytʌc tu' yʌn Jesús, rajen caj u c'ataj:
\p ―Mac aro'? Jaj Ts'urir ―quij.
\p 
\v 26 Rajen Jesús caj u nuncaj ti', tan ya'aric:
\p ―A mac a quin ts'ic ti' yoch pan a ts'oc in chuquic, raji' cu bin u c'ubiquen.
\p Caj ts'oc u chuquic yoch pan caj u ts'aj ti' Judas, raji' u tet Judas Simón Iscariote.
\v 27 Caj ts'oc u ts'abʌr yoch pan Judas, caj oc quisin ti' Judas. Rajen Jesús caj u ya'araj:
\p ―A ba' ca bin a betej baje'rer toc sebquintej, betej baje'rer.
\p 
\v 28 U camsʌwinicob a mac yet janʌnob ich u pojche'ir mʌ' yerob biquinin caj ya'araj aro' ti' Judas.
\v 29 Quire' Judas ra' u beyaj quir u cʌnantic u taq'uin u yet camsʌwinicob, rajen caj u sosoc tucrajob Jesús tan ya'aric:
\p ―Joq'uen mʌnej a ba' ij c'at quir ij qui'qui' janʌnex.
\p Chen u jer caj u sosoc tucrajob ara'b ten Jesús ti' Judas ca' u jʌsej taq'uin ti' a mac mʌna'.
\v 30 Caj ts'oc u jantic yoch pan Judas sep caj joq'uij, jach ac'bir.
\s1 Jesús tu ya'araj u jer u t'ʌn ric'ben
\p 
\v 31 Caj ts'oc u bin Judas, Jesús caj u ya'araj ti' u camsʌwinicob:
\p ―Baje'rer c'uchij tu q'uinin cu bin u sʌjtiquen tu cotor mac. A teno' tu tuchi' ten C'uj a mac irenechex. Cu bin sʌjta'bir C'uj xan quire' a ba' quin bin in betej.
\v 32 Quire' a ba' quin bin in betej cu bin sʌjta'bir C'uj ten mac. Baxuc a C'ujo' cu bin u yiric jach caremen a teno'. Baje'rer c'uchij tu q'uinin cu yiric caremen a teno'.
\v 33 In chan pararechex, tabar in bin, ca' bin a cʌxtiquenex an ten bic caj in wa'araj ti'ob u winiquirob judío. Baxuc xan quin wa'aric techex tu' quin bin a teno', mʌ' toy c'ucha'an a wor a tarex tu' quin bin.
\v 34 Quin toc aric techex u jer in t'ʌn ric'ben. Quin wac techex: Yajquintex a pacran bʌjex. An ten bic quin yajquintic techex.
\v 35 Wa baxuco' tu cotor cu bin u yerob in camsʌwiniquechex wa ca pacran yajquintex a bʌjex.
\s1 Jesús cu ya'aric ti' Pedro: Je' a wa'aric mʌ' a c'ʌ'otene'
\r (Mt. 26.31‑35; Mr. 14.27‑31; Lc. 22.31‑34)
\p 
\v 36 Simón Pedro caj u c'ataj ti' Jesús, tan ya'aric:
\p ―Jaj Ts'urir ―quij―, tub u wich a bin?
\p Jesús caj u nuncaj ti':
\p ―A tu' quin bin a teno' mʌ' c'ucha'an a wor a tar baje'rer. Chen pachir je' a tare' ―quij Jesús.
\p 
\v 37 Pedro, caj u ya'araj:
\p ―Jaj Ts'urir ―quij―, biquinin ca wa'aric mʌ' c'ucha'an in wor in tar ta pach baje'rer? ―quij Pedro―. Cax quimiquen ti' tech jach tsoy tin t'ʌn.
\p 
\v 38 Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―A techo' Pedro mʌ' a c'at a quimini', taj quin wac tech mʌ' toy c'aynʌc a caxo' mʌna' u nup u tenin ca' bin a wa'arej mʌ' a c'ʌ'oteni'. Tabar in bin, ca' bin a cʌxtiquenex a teno'.
\c 14
\s1 A teno' p'eri'en yejer in Tet C'uj, quij Jesús
\p 
\v 1 Jesús caj ya'araj ti' u camsʌwinicob:
\p ―Mʌ' a xac' a tucriquex ba', acsex ta wor ti' C'uj. Baxuc ten acsex ta worex ten xan.
\v 2 Tar quin bino' ich in Tet C'uj. Wa mʌ' taj ca'ch mʌ' in wac techex. Tar quin bino' quir in tsoyquintic quir a wocarex quir a cʌjtarex.
\v 3 Cu ts'ocar in tsoyquintique', je' in ca' tare' quir in pʌyiquechex soc rajra' ti' yʌnechex tu' yʌnen.
\v 4 A tu' quin bin a teno' a toc erex bic tabar a tarex.
\p 
\v 5 Tomás caj u ya'araj ti':
\p ―Jaj Ts'urir ―quij―, mʌ' in werob tu' ca bin. Bic in weticob bic tabar in tar tu' yʌnech?
\p 
\v 6 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti', tan ya'aric:
\p ―Quire' a teno' ca' bin c'uchuquechex tu' yʌn in Tet C'uj. Quire' a teno' ca' bin a wetiquex a ba' taj. A teno' quin ts'ic a cuxtarex ric'ben. Chen a mac a cu yacsic tu yor ten cu bin u c'uchur tu' yʌn in Tet C'uj. A mac mʌ' u yacsic tu yor in t'ʌn mʌ' c'ucha'an yor u yer C'uj.
\v 7 Ra' u q'uinin mʌ' a werenexi', rajen mʌ' a werex in Teti'. Baje'rer a chʌc erex in Tet xan quire' tan a cʌnic a werenex xan.
\p 
\v 8 Rajen Felipe caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Jaj Ts'urir ―quij―, cha' in wiricob ic Tet C'ujex a baxuco' ti'ti' tenob.
\p 
\v 9 Jesús caj ya'araj:
\p ―Mun q'uin ti' yʌnen yejerechex? Mʌ' toy a weren, Felipe? A mac yirmʌnen baxuc yirmʌn in Tet C'uj xan. Biquinin ca wac ten: “Cha' in wiricob ic Tetex C'uj”?
\v 10 Mʌ' wa ta wacsex ta worex ra'iri'enob yejer in Tet C'uj? A ba' quin wa'aric techex mʌ' in t'ʌni'. A quin wa'aric techexo' u t'ʌn in Tet C'uj. Mʌ' ja wirej, in Tet ti' cʌja'an tin pixam raji' cu betic a carem beyajo'.
\v 11 Acsex ta worex ten ra'iri'enob yejer in Tet C'uj. Wa mʌ' c'ucha'an a wor a wu'yic a ba' quin wa'aric techex, rajen acsex ta worex ti' a ba' quin betic.
\v 12 Taj a ba' quin wac techex. Acsex ta worex wa quin yamtiquechex soc quet bayiri' carem a beyajex xan an ten bic ten carem in beyaj. Chen jach manan ca bin a betiquex quire' ca' bin xiquen ich in Tet C'uj.
\v 13 Quire' ta wacsex ta worex ten, rajen c'ucha'an a worex a c'atic ba' ti' C'uj. Rajen a teno' quin bin in ts'ic tu cotor a ba' ca c'atiquex ti' in Tet. Soc a baxuco' cu bin ya'aricob mac jach carem in Tet C'uj quire' ten tin yamtajechex ―quij Jesús―. Mʌ' ja wirej, u pararen C'uj.
\v 14 Quire' ca wacsiquex ta worex ten, rajen ca bin a c'atiquex ba' ten, rajen quin ts'ic techex xan.
\s1 Je' in tuchi'tic techex u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj
\p 
\v 15 Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Wa ca yajquintiquenex je' a quibiquex tu cotor in t'ʌn.
\v 16 Wa ca quibiquex in t'ʌn je' in t'ʌnic in Tet C'uj soc u ts'ic techex u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj quir u yamtiquechex. Rajra' ti' yʌn yejerechex. Raji' cu cʌnantic in t'ʌn xan a ba' jach taje'.
\v 17 A mac ti' yʌn ich yoc'ocab mʌ' c'uch'a'an yorob u c'ʌmic u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj quire' mʌ' u yacsicob tu yorob ti' wa ti' yʌn quire' mʌ' yerob bic tabar cu beyaj. Quire' ca' bin tac u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj, je' a wetiquexe' quire' a wet binex yejer. Baxuc cu bin u cʌjtar ta pixamex.
\v 18 Mʌ' jin bin in p'ʌtiquechex, je' in ca' tar soc ti' yʌnen yejerechex tu ca' ten.
\v 19 A mac a ti' yʌnob ich yoc'ocab, mʌ' ya'ab u q'uinin cu bin yiriquenob. Chen techex rajra' ca bin a wiriquenex quire' ca bin a wiriquex in beyaj. Quire' a teno' quin bin in cuxtar, rajen ca bin a c'ʌmiquex ric'ben cuxtar techex.
\v 20 Quire' ca' bin tac u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj quir u cʌjtar ta pixamex je' a c'ʌ'otiquex a teno' ra'iri'en yejer in Tet C'uj. Je' a c'ʌ'otiquex ti' yʌnen yejerechex ra'iri'en yejerechex quire' ti' yʌnen ta pixamex.
\v 21 A mac cu quibic in t'ʌn a tu yubaj raji' cu yajquintiquen. A mac cu yajquintiquen raji' yajbir ten in Tet C'uj. Baxuc ten quin yajquintic xan. Je' in tar ti' soc u jach c'ʌ'otiquenob.
\p 
\v 22 Judas mʌ' ra' Iscariote caj ya'araj ti' Jesús:
\p ―Jaj Ts'urir ―quij―, biquinin mʌ' a wesic a bʌj ti' tu cotor mac a ti' yʌn ich yoc'ocab?
\p 
\v 23 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti', tan ya'aric ti':
\p ―A mac a cu yajquintiquene' cu quibic a ba' quin wac ti'. Raji' yajbir ten in Tet C'uj. Quin tarob yejer in Tet quir in cʌjtarob tu pixamo'.
\v 24 A mac a mʌ' u yajquintiquen, raji' mʌ' u quibic a ba' quin wa'aric ti'. Mʌ' ten in t'ʌn a quin wa'aric techexo'. Raji' u t'ʌn in Tet a mac tu tuchi'tajen.
\p 
\v 25 ’Quin wa'aric techex aro' ti' toy yʌnen yejerechex.
\v 26 Quire' tin c'ataj ti' in Tet ca' u tuchi'tej techex u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj quir u yamtiquechex. Je' u camsiquechex tu cotor ba'. Baxuc je' u c'asic techex tu cotor a ba' caj in wa'araj techex uch.
\p 
\v 27 ’Mʌ' toy xiquen, je' in chichquintic a worex. Mʌ' in chichquintic a worex an ten bic mac cu chichquintic u yor u rac'ob a ti' yʌn ich yoc'ocabe'. Quin bin in ts'ic techex u qui'ir in wor soc rajra' qui' a worex. Rajen mʌ' a xa'xac' tucurex, baxuc mʌ' a ch'iquex sajaquirex.
\v 28 Quire' tin wa'araj techex bin in ca'. Quire' tin wa'araj techex je' in ca' tar in wiriquechex. Wa ca yajquintiquenex cu qui' tar a worex quire' wʌc'ʌs bin in ca' ich in Tet C'uj. In Teto' jach manan no'j, a teno' mʌ' nejach no'jeni'.
\v 29 Quire' quin wac techex aro' ti' toy yʌnen yejerechex quire' mʌ' toy xiquen. Baxuco' ca' bin xiquen je' a quibiquex a ba' tin wa'araj techexo'.
\p 
\v 30 ’Mʌ' ya'ab u q'uinin quir in tsicbar ya'ab techex quire' tabar u c'uchur a quisino' quir u cʌxtiquen. Raji' cu cʌnantic tu cotor mac ich yoc'ocab a mac mʌ' yer C'ujo'. Mʌ' ju c'uchur yor u betic mʌ' c'ʌs ba' ten.
\v 31 A teno' quin chen betic an ten bic tu ya'araj ten in Tet. Baxuc soc yer mac quin yajquintic in Tet. Jeroj riq'uenex cuxex ―quij Jesús.
\c 15
\s1 A teno' iren u yaq'uir u wich uva
\p 
\v 1 Jesús caj ya'araj ti' u camsʌwinicob:
\p ―A teno' ―quij―, iren u yaq'uir u wich uva. In Tet C'uj irej a mac cu cʌnantic u yaq'uir u wich uva.
\v 2 Tu cotor mac cu tar tin wicnʌn irob u xa'yar yaq'uir uva. A mac a cu tar tin wicnʌn a mʌ' u betic a ba' u c'at in Tet C'uj, raji' irej u xa'yar yaq'uir uva a mʌ' u ts'ic u wiche'. Wa ju xa'yar yaq'uir a mʌ' u ts'ic u wich a mac cu cʌnantic u yaq'uir uva cu janc'ubtic u xa'yar yaq'uir. Baxuco' in Tet C'uj cu bin u betej ti' a mac a mʌ' u betic a ba' u c'at C'uj. Chen a mac cu tar tin wicnʌn a cu betic a ba' u c'at C'uj cu bin yamta'bir ten C'uj soc u man tu tsoyir. Raji' irej u xa'yar yaq'uir uva cu racʌr a ba' mʌ' tsoye', ten a mac a cu cʌnantic soc u nets'ic u wich.
\v 3 Mʌ' ja wirej, in Tet C'uj tu toc ruc'saj a c'asirex a ta betajex quire' ta wacsajex ta worex in t'ʌn a tin wa'araj techex.
\v 4 P'atenex tin wicnʌn soc in p'atʌr ta pixamex. C'aj techex wa ju xa'yar yaq'uir wa mʌ' ti' yʌn ich u jach aq'uir, mʌ' c'ucha'an yor u ts'ic u wichi'. Rajen, wa ca p'atʌrex tin wicnʌn soc in p'atʌr ta pixamex baxuco' c'ucha'an a worex a betic a ba' u c'at C'uj. Quire' wa mʌ' a p'atʌrex tin wicnʌn mʌ' c'ucha'an a worex a betic a ba' u c'at C'uj.
\p 
\v 5 ’A teno', iren u jach aq'uir uva, a techexo' irechex u xa'yar yaq'uir uva. A mac a cu p'atar tin wicnʌn quin p'atar xan tu pixam raji'ob cu ts'ic u wich, cu beticob a ba' u c'at C'uj. A wʌc'ʌs bʌjiri'ex mʌ' c'ucha'an a worex ti' mʌna' ba', quire' yʌn in yamtiquechex.
\v 6 A mac a mʌ' u c'at u quibic in t'ʌn, raji' mʌ' u c'at u p'atʌr tin wicnʌn. Raji' irej u xa'yar yaq'uir uva a mʌ' u ts'ic u wich. Rajen cu janch'ʌctic. U xa'yar yaq'uir uva a tu janch'ʌctaj cu tijir. Pachir cu tar u maric quir u toquic ich c'ac'.
\p 
\v 7 ’Wa ca p'atʌrex tin wicnʌn, baxuc wa cu p'atʌr in t'ʌn ta pixamex, c'ucha'an a worex a c'atiquex tu cotor ba' a c'atex ti' C'uj. Je' u ts'ic techex.
\v 8 Wa rajra' ca betiquex a jach tsoyo' in Tet C'uj cu bin sʌjta'bir C'uj ten tu cotor mac. Baxuco' ca wesiquex in jach camsawiniquechex.
\v 9 An ten bic in Tet cu yajquintiquen, baxuc techex quin yajquintiquechex. P'atenex soc in yajquintiquechex.
\v 10 Wa ca quibiquex tu cotor a ba' quin wac techex. A baywo' quin yajquintic techex an ten bic in Tet C'uj cu yajquintiquen quire' tin quibaj tu cotor a ba' caj u ya'araj ten.
\p 
\v 11 ’Rajen quin wa'aric techex aro' soc rajra' qui'ex a worex an ten bic ten qui' in wor. A baywo' jach manan qui'ex a worex.
\v 12 A je' in t'ʌna' tan in wac techex ca' a pacran yajquintiquex a bʌjex an ten bic ten caj in yajquin techex.
\v 13 A mac a cu c'ubic u bʌj quir u quinsa' ti' a mac a cu jach yajquintic, raji' jach manan cu yajquintic. Baxuc quin bin in betej a teno', rajen yʌn cʌniquenex.
\v 14 Techex jach manan quin yajquintiquechex wa ca betiquex a ba' tin wa'ara techex baje'rer.
\v 15 Baje'rer ra'iri'o'onex quire' tin cha' a najtiquex tu cotor a ba' in wu'ymʌn ich in Tet C'uj. A mac a cu beyaj mʌ' ara'b ten u ts'urire' tu cotor ba' cu tucric u betic. Chen ten tin toc araj techex rajen baje'rer mʌ' in c'urewechex quire' ra'iri'o'onex.
\v 16 A techexo' mʌ' ta tetajenex chen ten tin tetajechex. An ten bic u yaq'uir uva ts'a'b u beyaj ten C'uj quir u wichʌncʌr. A teno' tin ts'aj techex a beyajex soc a wesic u beyaj C'uj ta pixamex. U yaq'uir uva yʌn u q'uinin quir u wichʌncʌr. Chen mʌ' baxuc techex quire' techex rajra' c'ucha'an a worex a wesiquex u beyaj C'uj ta pixamex. Rajra' ca bin a betiquex aro' quire' ta wacsex ta worex ten. Rajen a ba' ca c'atiquex ti' in Tet C'uj je' u ts'ic techex.
\v 17 A je' in t'ʌna' tan in wac techex: ca' a pacran yajquintex a bʌjex.
\s1 U camsʌwinicob cu bin p'actabir ten a mac ti' yʌn ich yoc'ocab
\p 
\v 18 Jesús caj ya'araj ti' u camsʌwinicob:
\p ―Wa mac cu p'actiquechex mʌ' a p'ʌtiquex in t'ʌn, c'aj techex ten tu yʌn p'acten a teno'.
\v 19 Wa techex irechex a mac ti' yʌn yoc'ocab cu yajquintiquechexob quire' irechexob a mac ti' yʌn yoc'ocab. Chen mʌ' irechex a mac ti' yʌnob ich yoc'ocab quire' ten tin tetajechex ich a mac a mʌ' ju yacsob tu yorob in t'ʌn. Rajen cu bin u p'actiquechex a mac ti' yʌnob yoc'ocab.
\v 20 C'aj techex a ba' caj in wa'ara techex: “A mac a cu beyaj ti' u jer, mʌ' no'j u beyaj. Chen u ts'urir a mac a cu beyaj, raji' jach no'j u beyaj.” Robob caj u chucob in pach, baxuc techex xan cu bin u chuquicob a pachex. Robob wa tu quibajob in t'ʌn, baxuc techex cu bin u quibicob a t'ʌnex xan.
\v 21 Baxuc tu cotor aro', cu bin u beticob ti' techex quire' mʌ' tu yacsob tu yorob in t'ʌn quire' mʌ' yerob mac tu tuchi'tajen.
\p 
\v 22 ’Wa mʌ' taren in tsicbar ti'ob uch, mʌ' chʌca'an yiricob u si'pirob. Quire' taren, rajen mʌ' c'ucha'an yor ya'aricob mʌna' u si'pirob.
\v 23 Chen a mac a cu p'actiquen baxuc cu p'actic in Tet xan.
\v 24 Wa mʌ' tin wesob ti' carem beyaj an ten bic mʌna' mac yiramʌn uch, mʌ' chʌca'an yiricob u si'pirob cax tu yirob a ba' tin betaj caj u p'actajenob yejer in Tet.
\v 25 Chen robob caj u nup'saj tu' ts'iba'an ich u t'ʌn C'uj uch: “Tu chen p'actajenob quire' baxuc u c'atob u bʌjiri' cu p'acticquenob.” Baxuc ts'ibta'b ten uch yʌjtseq'uirob u t'ʌn C'uj uch.
\p 
\v 26 ’Ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin cu bin tar u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj a mac quin tuchi'tic soc u yamtiquechex. Taj a ba' cu bin yac techex quire' ti' u tar ich u Tet C'uj. Raji' cu bin u tsec'tiquen ―quij Jesús―.
\v 27 Techex xan ca bin a tsec'tiquenex ti'ob quire' techex ti' yʌnechex yejeren caj u yʌnxchun in beyaj hasta baje'rer.
\c 16
\p 
\v 1 ’Quin toc aric techex a jera' soc mʌ' a p'ʌtiquex in t'ʌn pachir quire' a werex mac cu p'actiquex.
\v 2 Robob cu bin u joc'siquechex tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob judío. Je' u c'uchur tu q'uinin xan je' u quinsiquechex xan quire' cu tus tucricob wa quet u beyaj C'uj a cu beticob.
\v 3 Baxuc cu bin u beticob techex quire' mʌ' yerob in Tet C'uj. Baxuc ten xan mʌ' yerenobi'.
\v 4 Mʌ' ja wirej, quin toc aric techex aro' baje'rer soc ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin cu chuquicob a pachex ca bin a c'ʌ'otiquex a ba' caj in toc araj techexe'.
\s1 U Taj'or u Pixam C'uj cu bin u tsec'tic ti' to'onex Jesús
\p ’Caj in yʌn tetajechex uch mʌ' jin toc araj techex quire' ti' toy yʌnen yejerechex. Mʌ' ju bin u tar ti' techex aro' hasta ca' bin xiquen.
\v 5 Jesús caj ya'araj ti' u camsʌwinicob. Baje'rer bin in ca' ich in Tet C'uj a mac tu tuchi'tajen. Mʌna' turiri' techex a c'atmʌnex ten biquinin ca bin.
\v 6 Jach yaj tan a wu'yiquex quire' tucur a ca'ex quire' tin wa'araj techex bin in ca' ich in Tet.
\v 7 Quire' taj quin wac techex. Jach tsoy ti' techex ca' xiquen ich in Tet C'uj. Quire' wa mʌ' jin bin mʌ' ju tar u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj. Chen wa ca' bin xiquen je' in tuchi'tic techex u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj.
\v 8 Ca' bin tac u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj je' u yesic soc chʌca'an yiric tu cotor mac ich yoc'ocab yʌn u si'pirob. Baxuc xan, je' u yesic mac soc chʌca'an yiricob bic tabar u cuxtaro', a jach tajo'. Baxuc xan je' u yesic soc chʌca'an yiric cu bin u jʌsbir ti'ob.
\v 9 Je' u yesic soc chʌca'an yiric yʌn u si'pirob quire' mʌ' tu toc acsajob tu yorob ten quire' ten quin taquicob.
\v 10 Je' u yesic mac a cuxtaro' a jach tajo' an ten bic caj cuxrajen ich yoc'ocab quire' mʌ' c'ucha'an yorob yiriquenob quire' ca' bin ts'ocac in beyaj bin in ca' ca'anan.
\v 11 Je' u yesic soc chʌca'an yiric C'uj cu bin jʌsbirob quire' toc jʌsa'anob ten C'uj quir u binob muc'yajob munt q'uinob.
\p 
\v 12 ’Yʌn toy ya'ab quir in camsiquechex chen mʌ' c'ucha'an a worex a najtiquex baje'rer. Quire' mʌ' toy c'uchuc tu q'uinin quir a najtiquexi'.
\v 13 Ca' bin tac u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj cu bin u camsiquechex tu cotor a ba' jach tajo'. Mʌ' ju bin u tsicbar techex u wʌc'ʌs bʌjiri' u t'ʌn. Ra' cu bin u tsicbar techex a ba' ara'b ten in Tet C'uj. Je' u tsicbar ti' techex a ba' cu bin tar ich yoc'ocab.
\v 14 Je' u tsicbar techex soc a sʌjtiquenex quire' ra' u beyaj u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj quir u tsec'tic ti' techex ti' ten soc a werex u jach tajiren a teno'.
\v 15 Tu cotor a ba' yʌn ti' in Teto' tu cotor ten yʌnin. Rajen tin wa'araj techex u beyaj u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj ra' quir u tsec'tic ti' techex ti' ten soc a werex u jach tajiren a teno'.
\s1 Ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin je' u qui' tar a worex, quij Jesús
\p 
\v 16 Jesús caj ya'araj:
\p ―Chen sasame' ca bin a wiriquenex. Chen mʌ' ya'ab u q'uinin mʌ' ja bin a wiriquenex. Pachire' je' a ca' iriquenex. Cu ts'ocar aro' quin ca' bin ich in Tet C'uj ―quij Jesús.
\p 
\v 17 Jun yarob u camsʌwinicob caj u pacran aricob:
\p ―Ba' u c'at ya'aric aro'?: “Chen sasame' ca bin a wiriquenex. Chen mʌ' ya'ab u q'uinin mʌ' ja bin a wiriquenex. Pachire' je' a ca' iriquenex. Cu ts'ocar aro' quin ca' bin ich in Tet C'uj”, quij Jesús.
\v 18 Ba' u c'at ya'aric: Sansame'? Mʌ' ic najtic a ba' cu ya'aric ―baxuc cu pacran a'aricob u camsʌwinicob Jesús.
\p 
\v 19 Jesús caj u najtaj u c'atob u c'atic a ba' u c'at ya'aric, a ba' ara'b ti'ob same'. Rajen Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―In wer a ba' ca pacran ariquexe'. Chen sasame' ca bin a wiriquenex. Chen mʌ' ya'ab u q'uinin mʌ' ja bin a wiriquenex. Pachire' je' a ca' iriquenexe'. Cu ts'ocar aro' quin ca' bin ich in Tet C'uj ―quij Jesús―.
\v 20 Taj a ba' quin wa'aric techex. Ca bin a woc'arex, ca bin a tucurex. Chen a pimob cu bin u qui' tar u yorob. Sansame' ca chen tucurex. Pachire' cu qui' tarex a worex jach jaj.
\v 21 Ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin a xquico' cu bin u rochic chan och. Tucur u ca' quire' muc'yaj u ca', chen ca' bin ts'ocac u rochic chan och, cu tubur ti' u muc'yaj a tu yubaj. Chen pachir qui' yor quire' tu rochaj chan och.
\v 22 Baxuc techex xan baje'rer tucur a ca'ex, irej a xquico'. Cu man mʌ' ya'ab u q'uinin je' a ca' iriquenex. Baxuc cu bin u qui'tar a worex xan. Mʌna' mac cu bin u ruc'sic u qui'ir a worex.
\p 
\v 23 ’Ca' bin c'uchuc a ray q'uino' mʌ' ja bin a c'atic ba' ten. Taj a ba' quin wac techex. Ca' bin a t'ʌnex C'uj chich a wor ca' bin a t'ʌnejex. Je' u ts'ic techex tu cotor ba' quire' ta c'ʌnex in c'aba'.
\v 24 Mʌ' toy a tumtex chen baje'rer a yʌnx chun techex a c'atiquex ti' in Tet. Tan a c'ʌniquex in c'aba' tu ca t'ʌniquex C'uj.
\s1 Toc c'ucha'an in wor ti' tu cotor ba' ich yoc'ocab, quij Jesús
\p 
\v 25 ’A teno' ―quij Jesús―, tin c'ʌs mucraj a ba' tin wa'araj techex uch. Je' u c'uchur tu q'uinin mʌ' in mucric techex quin bin in toc aric techex in Tet C'uj.
\v 26 Je' u c'uchur tu q'uinin ca' bin xiquen ich in Tet C'uj a ray u q'uinino'. A bʌjiri'ex ta junanex ca bin a c'atex ba' ti' in Tet C'uj quire' ta wacsex ta worex ten. Mʌ' ba'wir quin c'atic ti' in Tet C'uj ti' techex.
\v 27 Quire' u bʌjiri' in Tet cu yajquintiquechex. Cu yajquintiquechex quire' ta yajquintenex quire' techex ta quibex ti' in tar ich C'uj.
\v 28 Raji' taj, a teno' taren ich C'uj tera' ich yoc'ocab. Rajen baje'rer quin p'ʌtic yoc'ocab quire' wʌc'ʌs bin in ca' ich in Tet C'uj.
\p 
\v 29 U camsʌwinicob caj ya'arob ti':
\p ―Baje'rer tan a tsicbar soc in najticob a ba' ca wa'aric. Mʌ' tan a c'ʌs mucric a ba' ta wa'araj tenob tu ca p'eri'quintic a ba' ca camsic ti' tenob uch.
\v 30 A tenobo', in werob tu cotor ba' a wer. Quire' a wer yʌn ba' quin c'aticob tech cax mʌ' toy in c'atob ti' tech a toc er. Rajen mʌ' ba'wir mac quir u c'atic tech ba'. Rajen quin quibicob tu tuchi'tech C'uj.
\p 
\v 31 Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―A wacsmʌnex ta worex chen yʌn toy a c'atex.
\v 32 Tabar u c'uchur tu q'uinin ca bin a p'ʌtiquenex tantanxer ca' bin xiquechex. Chen tin junan ca bin p'ʌtenex. Chen mʌ' tin junani' quire' ti' yʌn in nup, raji' in Tet C'uj.
\v 33 Quin wa'aric techex tu cotor aro' soc mʌ' a ch'iquex sajaquirex quire' ta wacsex ta worex ten. Ti' toy cuxa'anechex ich yoc'ocab, je' a muc'yajex. Chen mʌ' a ch'iquex sajaquirex quire' a teno' ts'oc in toc ruc'sic u muc' u ts'urir a mac ti' yʌnob ich yoc'ocab. Baxuc techex ca bin a ruc'siquex u muc' u ts'urir a ti' yʌn ich yoc'ocabe'.
\c 17
\s1 Jesús cu t'ʌnic C'uj ti' u camsʌwinicob
\p 
\v 1 Jesús caj ts'oc u ya'aric aro' caj u nacsaj u wich ca'anan quir u t'ʌnic C'uj. Caj ya'araj:
\p ―Tet ―quij―, c'uchij tin q'uin esej ti'ob a winico' jach caremen a teno' quire' a pararen soc c'ucha'an in wor in wesic ti' a winico' jach caremech xan.
\v 2 Quire' ta ts'aj in cʌnantej tu cotor mac a ti' yʌn ich yoc'ocab cax a mun ti' yʌn soc c'ucha'an in wor in ts'ic ti'ob u cuxtar muntq'uin a mac ta ts'aja ten.
\v 3 In Tet jach C'ujech quire' mʌna' u jer baxuquech. A teno' Jesucristojen a mac a ta tuchi'taj ich yoc'ocab. Tu cotor mac u yerech, baxuc u yeren xan. Je' u c'ʌmicob u cuxtar munt q'uin.
\p 
\v 4 ’Ts'oc in wesic ti' tu cotor mac a ti' yʌn ich yoc'ocab jach caremech a techo'. Quire' tin ts'ocsaj in beyaj a ta ts'aja ten baje'rer.
\v 5 Baje'rer Tet ―quij Jesús―, esej ti' tu cotor mac jach caremen a teno' ʌcʌtanech an ten bic ti' yʌnen uch yejerech cax mʌna' toy ru'um uch.
\p 
\v 6 ’A teno', tin wesaj ti'ob bicyʌra'ech ti' a mac ta tetaj ich yoc'ocab quir a ts'ic ten. Tech yʌnin ca' ta ts'ajob ten caj u quibob a t'ʌn.
\v 7 Tu cotor ba' a ta ts'aja ten u tar ti' tech in Tetech.
\v 8 A teno' tin toc araj ti'ob a t'ʌn, a ta wa'araj ten. Robob caj u c'ʌmajob a t'ʌn quire' yerob taj, ti' in tar tub yʌnech. Caj u yacsajob tu yorob tech ta tuchi'tajen.
\p 
\v 9 ’A teno' ―quij Jesús―, quin c'atic tech ca' a yamtejob. Mʌ' jin c'atic tech quir a yamtic tu cotor mac ich yoc'ocab. Chen ca' a yamtej a mac a pararob a mac a ta tetaj ca' u yacsejob tu yor ten.
\v 10 Tu cotor mac tech yʌnin, ten yʌnin xan. Tu cotor a mac ten yʌnin tech yʌnin xan. P'eri' to'on yʌnin quire' a ba' cu bin u beticob quin bin sʌjta'bir.
\p 
\v 11 ’Baje'rer tar in ca' ich tech tu ca'ten. Mʌ' jin p'atʌr ich yoc'ocab. Chen robob cu bin u p'atʌrob ich yoc'ocab tu junanob. In Tet ʌcʌtan tech a mʌna' u si'piro' quin c'atic tech ca' a cʌnantej tu cotor mac a ta ts'aj ten uch. Soc c'ucha'an yorob ti' wa ba' cu tar u tumtic yorob. Quin c'atic tech ca' a cʌnantej ti'ob soc p'eri' u tucurob an ten bic tenob quire' p'eri' in tucurob xan.
\v 12 Ti' toy yʌnen yejerob ich yoc'ocab a mac a ta ts'aja ten tin cʌnantajob tin camsaj ti'ob a ba' a c'at. Tin cʌnantaj soc mʌ' u satʌrob. Chen ti' toy cu sayʌrob tin pach a mac a ta ts'aja ten. Chen turiri' satij. Quire' ti' ts'iba'an ich u t'ʌn C'uj cu bin satʌr.
\p 
\v 13 ’Quire' tar in ca' ta wicnʌn, Tet. Chen tan in t'ʌniquech ti'ob, ti' toy yʌnen yejerob tera' ich yoc'ocab. Soc cu yubicob soc cu chichquinta'r yorob quire' in t'ʌn.
\v 14 Tin wa'araj ti'ob a t'ʌn. Baje'rer robob caj p'actabir ten mac. Quire' mʌ' p'eri'ob u tucurob yejer a mac ti' yʌn yoc'ocab. Quire' baxuc ten ―quij Jesús―, mʌ' p'eri' in tucur yejer a mac ti' yʌn ich yoc'ocab.
\v 15 Mʌ' tan in c'atic tech ca' a joc'sicob ich yoc'ocab. Tan in c'atic tech ca' a cʌnantob ti' a quisino' soc mʌ' u p'ʌticob u t'ʌn C'uj.
\v 16 Quire' mʌ' p'eri' u tucurob yejer a mac ti' yʌn ich yoc'ocab quire' baxuc ten ―quij Jesús―, mʌ' p'eri' in tucur yejer a ti' yʌn ich yoc'ocab.
\v 17 Tsoyquintej yorob yejer a t'ʌn quire' a t'ʌn a techo', raji' taj.
\v 18 An ten bic ta tuchi'tajen ich a mac a ti' yʌnob yoc'ocab quir in wa'aric a t'ʌn. Baxuc ti'ob quin tuchi'tic ich yoc'ocab quir u ya'aricob a t'ʌn yoc'ocab.
\v 19 Quire' tan in c'ubic in bʌj quir in betic a ba' a c'at quire' quin yajquinticob xan soc jach jaj tech yʌninob tu cotorob. C'ucha'an yorob u beticob aro' quire' baxuc tin betaj ten xan.
\p 
\v 20 ’Mʌ' chen ti'ob quin c'atic tech, quin c'atic tech ti'ob a mac a cu bin u yacsic tu yor pachir ca' bin yubej u tsec'ticob a t'ʌn.
\v 21 Quin t'ʌniquech ti'ob, Tet, soc p'eri'ob u tucurob an ten bic tech yejeren, Tet, p'eri'enob in tucurob. Soc tu cotor mac cu bin u yacsicob tu yorob tech ta tuchi'tajen.
\v 22 A teno' tin ts'aja ti'ob u tsoyir u pixamob an ten bic ta ts'ajten u tsoyir in pixam soc p'eri' u tucurob an ten bic tenob p'eri' in tucurob xan ―quij Jesús―.
\v 23 A teno' ti' yʌnen tu pixamob, a techo' ti' yʌnech tin pixam xan soc raji'ob jach jaj p'eri'ob u tucurob soc tu cotor mac yerob tech ta tuchi'tajen soc yerob xan tech ta yajquintaj a mac a cu yacsicob tu yorob in t'ʌn an ten bic ten ca yajquintiquen, Tet.
\p 
\v 24 ’Tet ―quij Jesús―, in c'at u tarob a mac a ta ts'aja ten tu' quin bin a teno' soc munt q'uin ti' yʌnob yejerenob. Soc yiricob a teno' u sasiriren a ta ts'aja ten quire' ta yajquinten cax mʌna' toy yoc'ocab uch.
\v 25 In Tetech, C'uj, taj a wor a techo'. A mac a ti' yʌn ich yoc'ocab mʌ' yerech chen ten in werech. In camsʌwinicob yerob tech ta tuchi'tajen.
\v 26 Tin camsaj ti'ob soc yerechob. Ti' toy jach ya'ab u q'uinin bin in camsic ti'ob soc yerechob a techo' jach manan. Soc u yajquintiquechob an ten bic ca yajquintiquen soc ti' quin cʌjtar ich u pixamob, ―baxuc caj u t'ʌnaj C'uj Jesús.
\c 18
\s1 Jesús caj chuquij ten u ts'urirob u winiquirob judío
\r (Mt. 26.47‑56; Mr. 14.43‑50; Lc. 22.47‑53)
\p 
\v 1 Caj ts'oc u t'ʌnic C'uj Jesús caj joc' yejer u camsʌwinicob. Caj u ch'ʌctaj pʌchij chan ja' u c'aba' Cedrón. Ti' c'uchij tu' yʌn u chan corir u pʌc'ar Olivo. Ti' mani yejer u camsʌwinicob yaran u che'er Olivo.
\v 2 Judas a cu bin u c'ubic Jesús yer tu yʌn u chan corir quire' ti' nanij Jesús cu bin yejer u camsʌwinicob.
\v 3 Ti' c'uchij Judas yejer ya'ab soldados yejer policía a cu beyajob ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob judío. Robob tuchi'ta'b ten u jach ts'urirob sacerdote yejer a fariseojo'. Caj tarob u mʌchmʌnob tʌjte' yejer u quib yejer u mascab xan.
\v 4 Jesús yer tu cotor ba' a ba' cu bin tar ti' rajen raji' nats'ij ich a pimo' a cu tarob caj u c'ataj ti'ob:
\p ―Mac tan a cʌxtiquex?
\p 
\v 5 Caj u nuncob tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Tan in cʌxticob Jesús a cu tar ich u cajar Nazaret.
\p Jesús caj u nuncaj ti'ob tan ya'aric:
\p ―Raji'en.
\p Ti' yʌn Judas xan yejer a mac tarob tan u c'ubic Jesús ti' a pimob.
\v 6 Caj ts'oc u ya'aric Jesús: “Raji'en”, caj cuncun pachnʌjob a mac a cu tarob u chuquicob Jesús ca'ch. Sep caj rubob ich ru'um.
\v 7 Jesús caj u ca' c'ataj ti'ob:
\p ―Mac tan a cʌxtiquex?
\p Caj u nuncajob:
\p ―Jesús a cu tar ich u cajar Nazaret tan in cʌxticob.
\p 
\v 8 Jesús caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Tin wa'araj techex, raji'en a ta wu'yajex in wa'aric techex. Rajen robob in camsʌwinicob tsire'ej u binob a ti'ob quire' chen ten ca cʌxtiquenex.
\p 
\v 9 Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob baxuco' soc u nup'sic a ba' caj u ya'araj ti' C'uj caj u t'ʌnaj sam caj ya'araj: “A mun ta ts'aja tene' mʌ' ju bin sa'tʌr”, baxuc caj u ya'araj Jesús ti' C'uj uch.
\p 
\v 10 Simón Pedro u ch'a'mʌn u mascab caj u jarar tu pix u mascab caj u ch'ʌcaj u xiquin, raji' u c'urew u jach ts'urir sacerdote. Raji' u c'aba' u c'urew Malco. Caj u racch'ʌctaj u xiquin ich u no'oj.
\v 11 Jesús caj u ya'araj ti' Pedro:
\p ―Wʌc'ʌs jupej a mascab tu pix. Wa baxuc ca betic mʌ' in bin in muc'yaj an ten bic in Tet u c'at in muc'yaj.
\s1 Jesús cu bin purbir ʌcʌtan u jach ts'urir sacerdote u c'aba' Anás
\r (Mt. 26.57‑58; Mr. 14.53‑54; Lc. 22.54)
\p 
\v 12 Rajen u capitán yejer u soldado yejer policía a cu beyajob ti' sacerdote caj u chucob Jesús caj u c'ʌxob u c'ʌbob, quir u binob u purej.
\v 13 Caj yʌn ch'ic binob u purob ich u jach ts'urir sacerdote, u c'aba' Anás. Anás, raji' tu yʌcantaj Caifás. U ja'an Caifás, raji' u jach ts'urir sacerdote, ra' u yaxq'uinin caj quinsa'b Jesús.
\v 14 Mʌ' u jer Caifás, ra'iri' a tu ya'araj:
\p ―Jach tsoy ca' quimic turiri' mac ti' tu cotoro'onex quire' cax mʌ' tu cotoro'onex quij quiminex ―quij.
\s1 Pedro cu ya'aric mʌ' u c'ʌ'otic Jesús
\r (Mt. 26.69‑70; Mr. 14.66‑68; Lc. 22.55‑57)
\p 
\v 15 Simón Pedro, quij Juan, caj binenob tu pach Jesús quire' u jach ts'urir u c'ʌ'oren, quij Juan. Tar binen ich u japnin tu re'a'an naj a yatocho' u jach ts'urir sacerdote tu yʌn Jesús xan.
\v 16 Tar p'at Pedro tancab bʌytʌc tu' yʌn u mac u jor yatoch u jach ts'urir sacerdote. Quire' u c'ʌ'omʌnenob, rajen binen in wa'arej ti' a mac a cu cʌnantic u jor yatoch soc u yacsa' Pedro. Rajen cha'b yocar Pedro tu japnin yatoch tu re'a'an.
\v 17 Rajen a mac cu cʌnantic u jor naj, raji' xquic, caj u c'ataj ti' Pedro:
\p ―Mʌ' wa tech u camsʌwiniquech a je' xiba'?
\p Pedro caj u nuncaj tan ya'aric:
\p ―Mʌ' teni' ―quij Pedro.
\p 
\v 18 Ti' ch'ica'anob u c'urewob u jach ts'urir sacerdote yejer u policía u jach ts'urir sacerdote. Tu nuts'ob u q'uich quire' que'er. U c'ac' a tu t'ʌbajob raji' u chuquir. Tu cu q'uichob ti' ch'ica'an Pedro xan, tan u q'uich xan yejerob.
\s1 Yʌn toc u jo'r Jesús ten u jach ts'urir sacerdote
\r (Mt. 26.59‑66; Mr. 14.55‑64; Lc. 22.66‑71)
\p 
\v 19 U jach ts'urir sacerdote caj u yʌnxchun u c'atic ti' Jesús:
\p ―Mun yʌn a camsʌwinic tech? Ba' ta camsaj ti'ob xan?
\p 
\v 20 Jesús caj u ya'araj:
\p ―Ten ―quij Jesús―, mʌ' jin mucraj ich tu cotor mac caj in camsaj ti'ob ich ʌcʌtan tu cotor mac. Rajra' quin camsicob ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj tu cu much'quinticob u bʌj u winiquirob judío. Baxuc ich chan naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob judío, rajra' tin camsajob. Mʌ' jin muc u camsaji'.
\v 21 Biquinin ca c'atic ten? ―quij Jesús―. C'atej a wu'yej ti'ob a mac tu yubob in camsicob. Robob yerob a ba' caj in wa'araj ti'ob.
\p 
\v 22 Jesús caj ts'oc u ya'aric aro', ti' yʌn turiri' policía a cu beyaj ich carem naj caj u tac' jʌtstaj Jesús, caj ya'araj ti' Jesús:
\p ―Biquinin ca nunquic baxuco' ti' u jach ts'urir sacerdote?
\p 
\v 23 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti' tan ya'aric:
\p ―Wa c'as tin wa'araj, arej ten. Tu' yʌn c'as tin wa'araj? Quire' mʌ' c'as tin wa'araj. Biquinin ca tac' jʌtstiquen?
\p 
\v 24 Anás tu tuchi'taj Jesús ich Caifás toc c'ʌxa'an. Raji' u jach ts'urir sacerdote a tan tu yocar u ts'urir sacerdote.
\s1 Pedro cu ma'quintic mʌ' ju c'ʌ'otej Jesús
\r (Mt. 26.71‑75; Mr. 14.69‑72; Lc. 22.58‑62)
\p 
\v 25 Ti' toy yʌn Pedro, ti' ch'ica'an q'uich. A mac yet q'uich caj u c'ataj ti':
\p ―Mʌ' wa tech u camsʌwiniquech a je' xiba'?
\p Pedro caj u ca' ma'quintaj:
\p ―Mʌ' teni' ―quij.
\p 
\v 26 Ti' yʌn u c'urew u jach ts'urir sacerdote. Raji' u bʌjob a mac ch'ac u xiquin ten Pedro. Caj u c'ataj ti':
\p ―Mʌ' wa tin wirech yejer a ra xibo' ich u chan corir u pʌc'ar Olivo?
\p 
\v 27 Pedro caj u ca' ma'quintaj:
\p ―Mʌ' ten ta wirajeni'.
\p Sasame' caj c'aynʌj cax.
\s1 Jesús ʌcʌtan ich Pilato
\r (Mt. 27.1‑2, 11‑14; Mr. 15.1‑5; Lc. 23.1‑5)
\p 
\v 28 Caj joc'sa'b Jesús ich Caifás caj bin purbirob ich u palacio gobernador soc ca' to'cac u jo'r. U c'aba' u palacio gobernador pretorio, u cuchir tu cu naj ta'quic u jo'r mac. Chen tabar u sastar. U jach ts'urir sacerdote yejer u rac'ob mʌ' ju yocarob ich palacio. Mʌ' ja wirej, ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin pascua mʌ' u xac'ticob u bʌj yejer a mʌ' u winiquirob judío. Mʌ' toy u jantob yoch u q'uinin pascua. Wa cu yocarobe' mʌ' u cha'bʌr u janticob quire' baxuc u winiquirob judío nanij cu beticob.
\v 29 Rajen Pilato caj joc' tu' yʌnob, caj u c'ataj ti'ob:
\p ―Ba' si'pir yʌn ti' quir a tar a puric tenex?
\p 
\v 30 Caj u nuncajob tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Wa mʌna' u si'pir uch mʌ' jin tarob in c'ubicob tech.
\p 
\v 31 Pilato caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Toc ch'a'ej techex a wʌc'ʌs bʌjiri'e'. Ta'quej u jo'r an ten bic ts'iba'an ich a t'ʌn techex.
\p U jach ts'urir sacerdote caj u nuncaj ti':
\p ―U t'ʌn u winiquir romano cu ya'aric mʌ' c'ucha'an in worob in quinsicob mac quire' ra' a beyaj tech.
\p 
\v 32 Baxuc cu bin u tar ti' Jesús an ten bic caj u ya'araj uch. Cu bin quinsbir ich cruz ten u winiquirob romano.
\v 33 Rajen Pilato caj ca' oquij tu cuchir tu nanij u ta'quic u jo'r mac. Pilato caj u ya'araj ti' Jesús:
\p ―In c'at in wu'yej wa tech u reyech u winiquirob judío?
\p 
\v 34 Jesús caj u ya'araj:
\p ―Baxuc wa ca tucric tech wa yʌn mac tu ya'araj tech ti' ten?
\p 
\v 35 Pilato caj u nuncaj, tan ya'aric:
\p ―Bic in wetic aro' mʌ' u winiquir judíojen. A wet winiquirob judío yejer u jach ts'urirob sacerdote a mac tu c'ubech ti' ten. Ba' ta betaj tech ti'ob?
\p 
\v 36 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti' tan ya'aric:
\p ―A teno' mʌ' in reyintic a tera' ich yoc'ocab. Wa tin reyintic a tera', in camsʌwinicob uch je' u yamtiquenob soc mʌ' u chuquiquenob uch u policía a cu beyajob ich carem naj yejer soldado. Rajen uch mʌ' jin tar ʌcʌtan tech uch soc a ta'quicob in jo'r.
\p 
\v 37 Pilato caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Jaj a techo' ca wa'aric reyech ―quij.
\p Jesús caj u nuncaj ti':
\p ―A teno' reyen, rajen taren ich yoc'ocab caj u rochen in nʌ' soc in tsec'tic u t'ʌn C'uj a ba' jach taj. Tu cotor mac a ju c'at u cʌxtic a ba' jach taj cu yubic in t'ʌn.
\p 
\v 38 Pilato caj u ya'araj:
\p ―Bic yerob mac ba'quiri' taj?
\s1 Jesús ara'b ca' quinsa'c
\r (Mt. 27.15‑31; Mr. 15.6‑20; Lc. 23.13‑25)
\p Pilato caj ts'oc u ya'aric aro' caj wʌc'ʌs joc' tu' yʌn u jach ts'urirob sacerdote. Caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Mʌ' jin wiraj wa yʌn u si'pir.
\v 39 Quire' techex nanij quin cha'ic a teno' a mac mʌca'an cu c'uchur tu q'uinin pascua. A c'atex wa jin cha'ic a reyex techex u winiquirex judío?
\p 
\v 40 Tu cotorob caj c'am awʌt'nʌjob tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Mʌ' a cha'ic aro', cha'ej Barrabás.
\p A Barrabáso' raji' cu ya'cric ba'.
\c 19
\p 
\v 1 Pilato caj ya'araj u jats'ʌr Jesús. Rajen u soldado Pilato caj u ch'ajob Jesús caj u jʌts'ajob u pach Jesús.
\v 2 A soldadojo' caj u jit'ajob q'ui'ix caj u tʌcʌjob caj u p'o'quintaj Jesús. Caj u tʌcob u buquintej Jesús u c'ʌrʌb noc'. Raji' u noc' chʌc irej cu buquintic a reyo'.
\v 3 Caj u tus t'ʌnajob irej wa rey tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Ca' cuxraquech ya'ab u q'uinin u reyech u winiquirob judío ―baxuc nanij cu t'anic jach rey. Rajra' tan u tac' jʌts'ticob Jesús.
\p 
\v 4 Pilato caj ca' joq'uij ich tancab tu' yʌnob u winiquirob judío caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Irex, tin joc'saj a je' xiba' ʌcʌtan techex soc a werex mʌna' turiri' u si'pir tin wiraj ti'.
\p 
\v 5 Caj joc'sab Jesús ʌcʌtan ti'ob. Jesús ti' toy u p'o'quinmʌn q'ui'ix. Baxuc u noc' ti' toy u buquinmʌn a chʌc noc'o'. Pilato caj u ya'araj ti' u winiquirob judío:
\p ―Ire'ex a je' xiba'.
\p 
\v 6 Rajen caj yirob Jesús u jach ts'urirob sacerdote yejer u policía a cu beyajob ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob u winiquirob judío. Caj u yʌnxchun u c'am aricob ti' Pilato:
\p ―Bʌjej ich cruz, bʌjej ich cruz.
\p Rajen Pilato caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Ch'a'ex ca' a bʌjex ich cruz a bʌjiri'ex quire' a teno' mʌ' in wiric wa yʌn u si'pir.
\p 
\v 7 U winiquirob judío caj u nuncob ti' tan ya'aric:
\p ―A tenob yʌn in t'ʌnob. Aj in t'ʌnob cu ya'aric ca' in quinsob wa cu tucric u bʌjiri' raji' u parar C'uj.
\p 
\v 8 Pilato caj u toc ch'aj sajquir uch a ba' cu bin tar ti' Jesús. Caj ts'oc u yubic a ba' caj u ya'arob ti', tu jach ch'aj sajaquir Pilato quire' yerob u parar C'uj, u winiquirob judío.
\v 9 Pilato caj ca' oquij ich palacio yejer Jesús caj u c'ataj ti' Jesús:
\p ―Tub a tar? ―quij.
\p Jesús mʌ' c'ʌs ba' tu nuncaj ti'.
\p 
\v 10 Rajen Pilato caj u ya'araj ti' Jesús:
\p ―A techo' mʌ' ja nunquic ten quire' a teno' a ts'urirenex. Wa jin c'at in cha'iquech ca' xiquech. A teno' c'ucha'an in wor in wa'aric ca' in quinsech ich cruz xan.
\p 
\v 11 Jesús caj u ya'araj ti':
\p ―Mʌ' c'ucha'an a wor a betic baxuc aro' ti' ten wa C'uj mʌ' ju c'at, a ti' yʌn ich ca'anano'. Rajen u jach ts'urirob sacerdote a mac tu c'ubajenob ti' tech, jach manan yʌn u si'pirob.
\p 
\v 12 Rajen Pilato u c'at u cha'ic Jesús ca' xic chen u winiquirob judío caj u c'am arob:
\p ―Wa ca cha'ic u bin mʌ' tan a qui' beyaj ti' a rey César quire' tu cotor mac a ju c'at yocar rey cu p'actic u rey César.
\p 
\v 13 Pilato caj ts'oc yubic ya'aric a pimo' caj u ya'araj ti' u soldado ca' u yacsej Jesús tu re'a'an naj. Ich chumuc tu' re'a'an naj ti' yʌn u cutan gobernador raji' beta'b ti' tunich. Raji' quir u cutar soc ya'aric wa cu cha'bʌr wa yʌn u quinsa'r wa ber cu ts'ocar u to'car u jo'r. U cutan gobernador pʌcha'an u c'aba' ich u t'ʌn hebreo Gabata. Rajen Pilato caj oc u cutar ti' taro'.
\v 14 Caj c'uchij c'ac'chunq'uin caj oc Pilato quir u cutar ich u cutan gobernador. Raji' u jach q'uinin pascua. Caj curʌj Pilato caj ya'araj ti' u winiquirob judío:
\p ―Iriquex a je' reyexa'.
\p 
\v 15 U winiquirob judío caj u c'am arajob, tan ya'aricob:
\p ―Sinej ich cruz ca' quimic. Sinej ich cruz ca' quimic.
\p Chen Pilato caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Cax wa ja reyex quin sinic ich cruz ca' quimic?
\p U jach ts'urirob sacerdote caj u ya'arob:
\p ―Raji' mʌ' ic reyex aro'. Chen raji' ic reyex César.
\p 
\v 16 Rajen Pilato caj u quibaj a ba' u c'atob caj u c'ubaj ti'ob u soldado ca' u bʌjej ich cruz. Rajen a soldadojo' caj u pʌyob Jesús.
\s1 Bʌja'an Jesús ich cruz
\r (Mt. 27.32‑44; Mr. 15.21‑32; Lc. 23.26‑43)
\p 
\v 17 Rajen u soldado caj u ts'ʌraj u pach Jesús, rajen tu c'ochaj u cruz. Caj bin tu cuchir a cu ya'aric u baquer u jo'r mac. Ich u t'ʌn hebreo pʌcha'an u c'aba' Gólgota.
\v 18 Ti' tu bʌjob ich cruz, yet bajac ca'tur mac, u tiri' bʌja'an xan tu ts'ic, u tiri' bʌja'an xan tu no'oj Jesús. Chumuc yʌn Jesús.
\v 19 Pilato caj u ts'ibtaj ich yoc'o che' jun xot' caj u ts'ibta, baxuc tan ya'aric: “A je' Jesús a cu tar ich u cajar Nazaret, raji' u rey u winiquirob judío.” Raji' bʌja'an ich yoc'or u jo'r Jesús ich u cruz.
\v 20 Ya'ab u winiquirob judío cu xaquicob tu' ts'iba'an quire' ti' bajij Jesús ich bʌytʌc tu cu yocarob ich u cajar Jerusalén. A ba' caj u ts'ibtaj Pilato ich u t'ʌn hebreo yejer ich u t'ʌn griego yejer ich u t'ʌn latino.
\v 21 U jach ts'urirob sacerdote caj ts'oc yiricob a ba' ts'iba'an ich cruz Jesús caj bin ya'aricob ti' Pilato:
\p ―C'axej a ba' caj a ts'ibtaj soc mʌ' ya'aric: “Raji' u rey u winiquirob judío.” Chen ca' a ts'ibtej: “Raji' cu ya'aric u reyen u winiquirob judío.”
\p 
\v 22 Pilato caj u nuncaj ti'ob tan ya'aric:
\p ―An bic caj in ts'ibtaj toc tsire'ej, a teno', mʌ' in c'axic ―quij Pilato.
\p 
\v 23 A mac a tu bʌjob Jesús cuatrojob soldado. Caj ts'oc u bʌjicob Jesús tu ch'ajob u noc'. Jujuntur tu ch'aj turiri', c'ʌs p'atij turiri'. Raji' u ca' yarir u noc' Jesús quire' toc coch caj sʌcta'b u tan u noq'uir, mʌna' u ber u chuyur.
\v 24 Rajen u soldado cu pacran aricob:
\p ―Cax mʌ' ic jʌtic. Ca' ij cʌrʌc'tej chan tunich, ca' ij quirej mac cu bin ch'ic u ca' yarir u noc'.
\p A baxuco' caj u nup'saj tu' ts'iba'an u t'ʌn C'uj uch caj u ya'araj: “Mʌ' u bin u jʌticob u ca' yarir in noc'. Cu chen binob yʌrʌc'ticob chan tunich soc yiricob mac cu bin u toc ch'ic in noc'”, quij. Baxuc ya'aric yʌjtseq'uir u t'ʌn C'uj uch. Rajen baxuc caj u betob u winiquirob soldado.
\p 
\v 25 Ti' ch'ica'an u nʌ' Jesús tu' bʌja'an ich cruz Jesús. Ti' yʌn u bʌj u nʌ' Jesús u c'aba' María xan. U c'aba' u mam Cleofas. Baxuc ti' yʌn María Magdalena.
\v 26 Ti' yʌn Juan bʌytʌc tu' bʌja'an Jesús, a mac jach yajbir ten Jesús. Ti' yʌn tu' yʌn u nʌ' Jesús. Rajen Jesús caj yiraj ti' yʌnob u nʌ' yejer Juan, caj ya'araj Jesús ti' u nʌ':
\p ―Nʌ', quen, raji' Juan, ch'a'ej tech soc irej a parar.
\p 
\v 27 Jesús caj u ya'araj ti' Juan:
\p ―Raji' in nʌ', ch'a'ej tech soc irej a nʌ' tech.
\p Rajen Juan tu yacsaj tu yatoch soc ti' cu cʌjtar ich yatoch Juan.
\s1 Quimij Jesús
\r (Mt. 27.45‑56; Mr. 15.33‑41; Lc. 23.44‑49)
\p 
\v 28 Caj ts'oc u toc aric ti' Juan aro', Jesús yer yʌn u rʌc nup'sic a ba' ts'iba'an ich u t'ʌn C'uj uch, rajen caj u ya'araj:
\p ―Uc'chʌjen ―quij Jesús.
\p 
\v 29 Ti' yʌn ich ruch chup u c'ab uva, pʌj. Rajen caj u ts'ʌmaj u noq'uir ich u c'ab uva a pʌjo' quir u ts'u'ts'ic ya'arir a noc'o' irej tʌmʌn. Caj u tʌcaj ich jʌrʌr u c'aba' hisopo caj u tich'itej u chi' Jesús ca' u ts'u'ts'aj.
\v 30 Jesús caj u ts'u'ts'aj u c'ab uva a pʌjo' caj ts'oc aro' caj u ya'araj:
\p ―Tin ts'ocsaj in beyaj ―quij Jesús.
\p Caj u chinquintaj u jo'r quire' quimij.
\s1 Caj rom u ch'ʌra'tir Jesús ten soldado
\p 
\v 31 Quire' a samano' u q'uinin quir u jesicob u bʌj u winiquirob judío, rajen u ts'urirob sacerdote. Mʌ' u c'atob yiricob u p'atʌrob u baquer ich cruz. Mʌ' ja wirej, ti' u winiquirob judío jach no'j yiricob u q'uinin saman tu cu bin u jesicob u bʌj. Rajen caj u c'atajob ti' Pilato soc u wʌticob u baquerob a mac a bʌja'anob ich cruz xan, u chac bʌq'uerob soc seb cu quiminob soc c'ucha'an yorob u yemsicob u baquer ich cruz.
\v 32 Rajen caj c'uchob soldado caj u rʌc wʌtob u chac bʌq'uer a turiri' u yet bʌja'an winico'. Caj c'uchob tu' yʌn u jer yet bʌja'an winiquir caj u wʌtob u chac bʌq'uer.
\v 33 Caj nats' tu' yʌn Jesús caj yirob quimij, rajen mʌ' tu wʌtob u chac bʌq'uer Jesús.
\p 
\v 34 Chen turiri' soldado tu ramaj u ch'ara'tir Jesús yejer ransa ca'ch. Sasame' caj joc' u q'uiq'uer yet jocac u ya'arir u bʌq'uer.
\v 35 A teno', quij Juan, caj in wiraj bic caj quimij Jesús. Rajen taj a ba' quin wa'aric soc baxuc a werex xan.
\v 36 A ba' u ber ti' Jesús ich cruz ten soldado, ra' quir u nup'sic a ba' ts'iba'an ich u t'ʌn C'uj uch, tu cu ya'aric: “Mʌ' ju bin wʌtbir u baquer, mʌ' turiri'”, baxuc caj ya'araj u t'ʌn C'uj uch.
\v 37 Baxuc ti' ts'iba'an u jer ich u t'ʌn C'uj uch, tan ya'aric: “Robob cu bin u yiricob ti' tu' rom in ch'ʌra'tir”, baxuc ts'iba'an ich u t'ʌn C'uj xan.
\s1 But' Jesús ich japnin tunich
\r (Mt. 27.57‑61; Mr. 15.42‑47; Lc. 23.50‑56)
\p 
\v 38 Pachir José a cu tar ich u cajar Arimatea, raji' tu muc u acsaj tu yor ti' Jesús quire' cu sʌjtic u jach ts'urirob u winiquirob judío, mʌ' ju ya'araj ti' u rac'ob wa tu yacsaj tu yor. Caj yiraj quimij Jesús caj bin ich Pilato quir u c'atic wa tsoy u ch'ic u baquer Jesús quir u but'ic ich japnin tunich. Pilato caj u ya'araj ti' ca' yens u baquer ich cruz quir u ch'ic u but' u baquer ich japnin tunich. Caj bin u ch'ic.
\v 39 Yet binac Nicodemo, raji' a mac bin tsicbar yejer Jesús oq'uin uch. Bin u yamtej José. Nicodemo tu mʌnaj u ts'ac mirra, xaca'an yejer u ts'ac áloes quir u jic'tic tu bʌq'uer Jesús, treinta kilos yʌn.
\v 40 Robob caj u cuchob u baquer Jesús, José yejer Nicodemo. Caj u sʌsʌjc'ʌstajob u baquer Jesús yejer sʌc noc'. Tu cu sʌsʌjc'ʌsticob u baquer Jesús, ti' cu puricob u ts'ac mirra yejer u ts'ac áloes soc mʌ' netu' u boc quire' baxuc nanij cu beticob u winiquirob judío tu cu bin u but'ic u baquer u rac'ob ich japnin tunich.
\v 41 Tu' tu sinob Jesús ich cruz uch bʌytʌc ti' u chan corir u pʌc'ar u che'er Olivos. Tu' yʌn u che'er Olivos ti' yʌn u mucnaj japnin tunich a beta'b ten mac. Mʌna' mac u but'mʌn u baquer quire' ric'ben.
\v 42 Tabar u q'uinin quir u jerar u winiquirob judío quire' tabar u bin q'uin. Quire' bʌytʌc ti' yʌn u japnin tunich, rajen c'ucha'an yorob u but'icob u baquer Jesús.
\c 20
\s1 Jesús caj riq'uij quir u ca' cuxtar
\r (Mt. 28.1‑10; Mr. 16.1‑8; Lc. 24.1‑12)
\p 
\v 1 Ra' u q'uinin cu yʌnxchun semana ti' toy ac'bir caj c'uchij María Magdalena tu' but' u baquer Jesús. Caj u yiraj toc bʌc'ʌsa'an u tunichirir u mac u jor a tu tu but'aj u baquer Jesús.
\v 2 María Magdalena caj u c'ʌnaj u yacab caj bin tu' yʌn Juan u yajbir ten Jesús yejer Simón Pedro. Caj ya'araj:
\p ―Tu cuchob u baquer ic Jaj Ts'urirex, mʌ' ij quer tu tu purob u baqueri'.
\p 
\v 3 Rajen Pedro yejer Juan caj joc'ob caj binob tu' but'a'an u baquer Jesús.
\v 4 Quet caj u c'ʌnob yacab. Chen Juan jach chich yacab raji' yʌn bat'an c'uchij tu but' u baquer Jesús. Chen Pedro sen yacab, pachir caj c'uchij.
\v 5 A Juano' caj u tac ch'ena'btaj tu japnin caj u yiraj u sʌc noc' tu top u baquer Jesús uch. Ti' jana'an ich ru'um. Juan mʌ' oc tu japnin tunich.
\v 6 Caj c'uchij Simón Pedro seb caj oquij tu japnin tu but' u baquer Jesús uch. Raji' caj u yiraj ti' jana'an u sʌc noq'uir tu top u baquer Jesús uch. U beri' jenric.
\v 7 Baxuc tu yiraj u panyujir tu top u wich Jesús uch. Toc ca' ts'a'an, u tiri' jana'an.
\v 8 Pachir caj oquij Juan a yʌn c'uch sasame' tu but' u baquer Jesús. Caj u yira ti' toc jana'an u noq'uir caj u quibaj riq'uij Jesús tu' quimen an ten bic caj u ya'araj Jesús.
\v 9 A ucho' mʌ' ju najtob tu ts'iba'an u t'ʌn C'uj uch wa yʌn u riq'uir Jesús tu quimirir. Ra'iri' u q'uinin caj u najtajob.
\v 10 Rajen Pedro yejer Juan yej u yet camsʌwinicob caj wʌc'ʌs sutnʌjob tu yatochob.
\s1 Jesús cu yesic u bʌj ti' María Magdelena
\r (Mr. 16.9‑11)
\p 
\v 11 María caj ca' urij tu but' u baquer Jesús uch. Caj bin Pedro yejer Juan ti' p'at María. Oc'ar u ca'. Ti' toy cu yoc'ar caj u tac ch'enaptaj yirej u japnin tu but' u baquer Jesús uch.
\v 12 María caj yiraj yʌjmasirob u t'ʌn C'uj ca'tur, jach sʌc u noc'ob ti' cura'anob tu chaquinta'b u baquer Jesús uch. Turiri' tu jo'rir, turiri' tu yoquir tu chaquinta'b u baquer Jesús uch.
\v 13 Caj c'ata'b ti' ten yʌjmasirob u t'ʌn C'uj:
\p ―Xquic ―quen―, biquinin tan a woc'ar?
\p Raji' caj u nuncaj tan ya'aric:
\p ―Quire' tu cuchob u baquer in Jaj Ts'urir, mʌ' in wer tuj tu purob u baquer in Jaj Ts'urir.
\p 
\v 14 María caj ts'oc ya'aric aro' caj u sut u bʌj caj u yiraj ti' yʌn Jesús chen mʌ' yer wa Jesúsi'.
\v 15 Jesús caj ya'araj ti' María:
\p ―Xquic ―quij―, biquinin tan a woc'ar? Mac tan a cʌxtiqui'?
\p María yer raji' a cu cʌnantic u chan corir tub u pʌc'mʌn u che'er Olivo. Rajen caj u ya'araj ti':
\p ―Tech wa ta ch'ajaj u baquer in Jaj Ts'urir, arej ten tub a puraj ca' xiquen in ch'a'ej.
\p 
\v 16 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti':
\p ―María ―quij.
\p Rajen María caj u sut u bʌj caj u ya'araj ti' ich u t'ʌn hebreo:
\p ―Raboni ―quij ya'araj. Raji' u c'at ya'aric: A wʌjcamsʌyʌjiren, quij Juan.
\p 
\v 17 Jesús caj u ya'araj ti':
\p ―Mʌ' a yʌn su'siquen quire' mʌ' xiquen tu' yʌn in Tet ich ca'anan. Ca' xiquech a wa'arej ti'ob in camsʌwinicob a irej in wits'inob. Arej ti'ob: tar quin bin ich in Tet. Baxuc tech, raji' a Tet xan. Ti' quin bin ich C'uj baxuc tech, raji' a C'uj xan. Baxuc yʌn a wac ti' in camsʌwinicob.
\p 
\v 18 Rajen María Magdalena caj bin ich u camsʌwinicob Jesús caj u ya'araj:
\p ―A teno' ―quij―, tin wiraj ic Jaj Ts'urirex.
\p Caj u ya'araj ti'ob tu cotor a ba' ara'b ti' ten Jaj Ts'ur.
\s1 Jesús cu yesic u bʌj ti' u camsʌwinicob
\r (Mt. 28.16‑20; Mr. 16.14‑18; Lc. 24.36‑49)
\p 
\v 19 Ra'iri' u q'uinin, oq'uin ti' toy u q'uinin cu yʌnxchun semana. U camsʌwinicob ti' u much'quinmʌnob u bʌj ich yatoch. U qui' mʌcmʌnob u jor quire' cu sʌjticob u jach ts'urirob u winiquirob judío. Seb caj yubob ti' c'uchij Jesús tu' yʌnob. Caj ch'icrʌj Jesús chumuc tu' yʌnob caj u rʌc t'ʌnaj tan ya'aric:
\p ―Taren in qui'quint a worex ―quij Jesús.
\p 
\v 20 Caj ts'oc ya'aric aro' ti'ob caj yes u c'ʌb tuj bajij yejer u ch'ʌ'ra'tir tuj rom. Rajen yerob ic Jaj Ts'urirex. Rajen jach qui' yorob.
\v 21 Jesús tu ca' araj ti'ob:
\p ―Qui'quintex a worex. An ten bic in Tet caj u tuchi'tajen ich yoc'ocab. Baxuc techex quin tuchi'tiquechex quir a beyajex ti' ten.
\p 
\v 22 Caj ts'oc ya'aric aro' caj u yustaj u camsʌwinicob caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Baje'rer a wet binaquex u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj.
\v 23 A mac cu c'axicob yor c'ucha'an a worex a wa'ariquex ti'ob: “Jawsa'b u si'pirob.” Chen a mac mʌ' u c'axicob yor c'ucha'an a wor a wa'ariquex ti'ob: “Mʌ' jawsa'an u si'pirobi'.”
\s1 Tomás mʌ' ju quibaj wa riq'uij Jesús
\p 
\v 24 Tomás mʌ' ti' yʌn ca'chi' yejer u yet camsʌwinicob caj c'uchij Jesús. Raji' turiri' ich a doce u camsʌwinicob Jesús. Raji' a toc ca'tur caj rocha'b ten u nʌ' uch.
\v 25 Caj c'uchij Tomás. U yet camsʌwinicob caj u ya'arob:
\p ―Tin wirob ic Jaj Ts'urirex.
\p Chen Tomás caj u nuncaj tan ya'aric:
\p ―Wa mʌ' in wiric u c'ʌb tu bajij yejer clavo. Wa mʌ' in jupic u yar in c'ʌb tu jorir clavo tuj bajij u c'ʌb, baxuc wa mʌ' in jupic in c'ʌb tuj rom u ch'ʌra'tir, mʌ' in quibic wa riq'uir Jesús ―quij Tomás.
\p 
\v 26 Caj c'uchij u jer semana u camsʌwinicob ti' cu much'quinticob u bʌj. A ray u q'uinino' ti' yʌn Tomás yejerob ich yatoch. Qui' mʌcmʌnob u jor. Seb caj yubob ti' yʌn Jesús yejerob caj ch'irʌj Jesús chumuc tu' yʌnob. Caj ya'araj:
\p ―Taren in qui'quintic a worex ―quij Jesús.
\p 
\v 27 Jesús caj ya'araj ti' Tomás:
\p ―Cojen jupej yar a c'ʌb tuj bʌja'an in c'ʌb iric in c'ʌb. Tich'ej yar a c'ʌb ca' a jupej tuj rom in ch'ʌra'tir. Mʌ' a tucric wa mʌ' taji' quire' riq'uen tuj quimen. Quibej riq'uen ich in quimirir.
\p 
\v 28 Rajen Tomás caj u nuncaj caj ya'araj:
\p ―In Jaj Ts'urirech ―quij―, in C'ujech xan ―quij Tomás.
\p 
\v 29 Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Tomás ―quij―, a techo' mʌ' ja quibaj hasta caj a wiraj riq'uen ti' in quimirir. Chen jach manan qui' yorob a mac a cu quibicob riq'uen ti' in quimirir cax mʌ' ju yirajenob.
\s1 Biquinin Juan caj u ts'ibtaj a je' ju'una'
\p 
\v 30 Ti' toy ya'ab carem beyajob tu yesaj Jesús ti' u camsʌwinicob Jesús. Chen mʌ' ts'ibta'b ich a je' ju'una'.
\v 31 Chen caj u ts'ibtaj a je' t'ʌna' soc a quibiquex a Jesúso', raji' Cristo a teta'b ten C'uj quir u taquico'onex, u parar C'uj. Wa baxuc ca quibico' toc yʌn a cuxtar munt q'uin.
\c 21
\s1 Jesús cu yesic u bʌj ti' u camsʌwinicob a sietejo'
\p 
\v 1 Jesús caj u ca' esa'r u bʌj ti' u camsʌwinicob. Caj u yesaj u bʌj ich chi' c'ac'nab u c'aba' Tiberias. Baxuc a jera' caj u yesaj u bʌj ti' u camsʌwinicob.
\v 2 Ti' tu much'quintajob u bʌj Simón Pedro yejer Tomás a toc ca'tur caj rocha'b ten u nʌ'. Ti' yʌn Natanael ti' u tar ich u cajar Cana ich u ru'umin Galilea. Ti' yʌn xan ca'turob u camsʌwinicob Jesús raji' u tetob Zebedeo. Ti' yʌn xan u jer ca'turob u camsʌwinicob.
\v 3 Simón Pedro caj u ya'araj ti' u yet camsʌwinicob:
\p ―Bin in ca' chuc cʌy yejer chim.
\p Robob caj ya'arob:
\p ―Baxuc a tenob tar in ca'ob yejerech.
\p Caj rʌc ocob ich chem caj binob u chuquejob cʌy. U burur ac'bir tu puricob u chimin, mʌ' ju chucobi'.
\v 4 Caj sasij ti' ch'ica'an Jesús ich chi' c'ac'nab chen u camsʌwinicob mʌ' yerob wa raji' Jesúsi'.
\p 
\v 5 Jesús caj u c'ataj ti'ob:
\p ―Chichanechex, mʌ' wa ta chuquex u cʌyir?
\p Caj u nuncajob:
\p ―Mʌna' ―quij.
\p 
\v 6 Jesús caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Purej u chimin tu no'oj chem. Je' a chuquiquex a cʌyo'.
\p Baxuc caj u betajob caj u purajob u chimin caj u jarajob u chimin jach chup u cʌyir. Rajen mʌ' ju c'uchur u yorob u jaricob ich c'ac'nab.
\v 7 A Juano', raji' a yajbir ten Jesús. Raji' u camsʌwinic xan, caj ya'araj ti' Pedro:
\p ―Raji' ic Jaj Ts'urirex.
\p Simón Pedro caj u yubaj ya'aric, “Raji' ic Jaj Ts'urirex”, caj u buquintaj u noc' quire' chʌcpiten ca'ch caj u puraj u bʌj ich ja' quir u c'uchur ich chi' c'ac'nab tu' yʌn Jesús.
\v 8 Caj tarob u camsʌwinicob yejer chem, tan u payticob u chimin cʌy quire' jach chup u cʌyir. Mʌ' nach yʌn ti' u chi'c'ac'nab chen cien metros.
\v 9 Caj joc'ob ich chem caj c'uchob ich chi'c'ac'nab. Caj yirob nuts'a'an c'ac'. Ti' yʌn u chuquir, ti' yʌn cʌy, tan u c'ac'tic yoc'or yejer waj.
\v 10 Jesús caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Ch'ayex cʌy jach ya'ab a tan ta chuquiquex.
\p 
\v 11 Rajen binij Simón Pedro ich chem. Caj u jitaj u chimin chup yejer cʌy. Jach carem u cʌyir caj u xacaj caj u yiraj ciento cincuenta y tres u cʌyir. Cax chup u chimin mʌ' ju jatʌr.
\v 12 Rajen caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ―Cojenex ta jananex ―quij.
\p Mʌna' u camsʌwinicob caj u ya'araj: “Maquech”, quire' baje'rer yerob raji' u Jaj Ts'urirob.
\v 13 Jesús caj u chucaj waj caj u ts'aj ti'ob u camsʌwinicob. Baxuc caj u ts'aj ti'ob yoch cʌy xan. Caj u rʌc jantajob.
\p 
\v 14 A jera' mʌna' u nup u tenin tu yesa u bʌj ti'ob u camsʌwinicob a caj ts'oc u riq'uir ti' u quimirir.
\s1 Jesús cu tsicbar yejer Simón Pedro
\p 
\v 15 Caj ts'oc u janʌnob Jesús caj u c'ata ti' Simón Pedro:
\p ―Simón, u pararech Jonás. A nupob cu yajquintiquen, chen tech wa jach manan ca yajquintiquen?
\p Pedro caj u nuncaj:
\p ―Tech, Jaj Ts'urir, a wer quin yajquintiquech.
\p Jesús caj u ya'araj ti':
\p ―Cʌnen, jansej ti' ten tu cotor mac a tu yacsob tu yorob ti' ten soc cu bin u chichquinticob tu pixamob an ten bic yʌjcʌnʌnyʌjir tʌmʌn yuc cu jansic u chan ar tʌmʌn yuc.
\p 
\v 16 Jesús caj u ca' c'ataj ti':
\p ―Simón, u pararech Jonás, jach qui' wa ca yajquintiquen?
\p Pedro caj u nuncaj:
\p ―Tech, Jaj Ts'urir, a wer in qui' yajquintiquech.
\p Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Cʌnen, jansej ti' ten tu cotor mac a tu yacsob tu yorob ti' ten soc cu bin u chichquinticob tu pixamob an ten bic yʌjcʌnʌnyʌjir tʌmʌn yuc cu jansic u chan ar tʌmʌn yuc.
\p 
\v 17 Mʌna' u nup caj c'ata'b ten Jesús ti':
\p ―Simón, u pararech Jonás, ca jach qui' wa ca yajquintiquen?
\p Pedro caj tucurnʌjij quire' tu yubaj mʌna' u nup u tenin caj c'ata'b ti': “Ca yajquintiquen wa?” Caj u ya'araj:
\p ―Tech, Jaj Ts'urir, tu cotor a wer. A wer quin yajquintiquech.
\p Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Cʌnen, jansej ti' ten tu cotor mac a tu yacsob tu yor ti' ten soc cu bin u chichquinticob tu pixamob an ten bic yʌjcʌnʌnyʌjir tʌmʌn yuc cu jansic u chan ar tʌmʌn yuc.
\p 
\v 18 Jesús caj ya'araj:
\p ―Taj a ba' quin wac tech. Chen chichanech uch ta qui' buquintaj a noc' caj bin tub a c'at. Ca' bin ch'ijiquech cu bin u c'ʌxicob a c'ʌb yejer a winquirir ich che' quir u quinsiquech.
\p 
\v 19 Caj u ya'araj ti' aro' quir u camsic bic tabar cu bin quimin soc mac cu bin u yiricob jach carem a C'ujo'. Jesús caj ya'araj ti':
\p ―Cojen tin pach ―quij.
\s1 U camsʌwinic a yajbir ten Jesús
\p 
\v 20 Pedro caj u sut u bʌj caj u yiraj tan u tar Juan tu pach a mac yajbir ten Jesús, ra'iri' a ti' yʌn ich Jesús caj u jantob yoch u q'uinin pascua, caj u c'ataj uch ti': “Jaj Ts'urir, quij, mac cu bin u c'ubiquech?” quij.
\v 21 Pedro caj u yiraj Juan caj u c'ataj ti' Jesús:
\p ―Jaj Ts'urir ―quij―, ba' cu bin tar ti' a ray in nupo'?
\p 
\v 22 Jesús caj u nuncaj ti', tan ya'aric:
\p ―Wa jin c'at ca' p'atac Juan hasta quin ca' ur, mʌ' ba'wir ca tucric ti'. Tech yʌn a tar tin pach ―quij.
\p 
\v 23 Rajen caj bin u sosoc arej ich mac a tu yacsob tu yorob, tan ya'aric:
\p ―A Juano' mʌ' ju bin quimin ―quij.
\p Chen Jesús mʌ' ju ya'araj: “Mʌ' ju bin quimin.” Tu chen araj: “Wa jin c'at ca' p'atac Juan hasta quin wu'ur mʌ' ba'wir ca tucric ti'.”
\p 
\v 24 Tu cotor a ba' ts'iba'an a tera', raji' caj u yiraj Juan, baxuc caj u yubaj a raji' u camsʌwinic Jesús. Rajen ij querex taj a ba' cu ya'aric.
\p 
\v 25 Ti' toy yʌn ya'ab ba' caj u betaj Jesús. Wa toc ts'iba'an jujuntur ich u ju'unin jach p'ecʌch ya'ab u ju'unin cu bin ts'ibta'bir. Chen a ts'iba'an a tera' ti'ti' soc ij querex bic tabar ic taquic ic bʌjex.
